{"type":"message","id":"1002651d","parentId":"77029732","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:04:44.882Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-10 14:04:44 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a [msg:om_x100b52bd50b674a0c448fa73b971d2a]\n\nA new session was started via /new or /reset. Run your Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Friday, April 10th, 2026 — 2:04 PM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-10 06:04 UTC"}],"timestamp":1775801084879}}
{"type":"message","id":"9496e15f","parentId":"1002651d","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:04:49.998Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me run the session startup sequence - read the required files before responding.\n\nAccording to AGENTS.md, I need to:\n1. Read SOUL.md - already in project context\n2. Read USER.md - already in project context\n3. Read memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md (today and yesterday) - need to check\n4. Read MEMORY.md - already in project context\n\nLet me check today's memory file first.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zidsxykni1ki_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/2026-04-10.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zidsxykni1ki_2","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/2026-04-09.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":622,"output":172,"cacheRead":32251,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33045,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775801084884,"responseId":"chatcmpl-4705eb20-1f39-4b45-928c-fc6b29e00014"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5f8c033c","parentId":"9496e15f","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:04:50.011Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_zidsxykni1ki_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# memory/2026-04-10.md\n\n## 今天发生了什么\n\n- 用户把我的名字更新为\"瞎子\"（更新了 IDENTITY.md）\n- 用户发来飞书妙记链接《Harness工程导论》，要求我学习并创建\n- 通过浏览器读取了妙记内容（需要用户已登录状态），成功解析并创建了学习笔记文档\n- 今天（14:00）：用户要求在 GitHub 上学习 harness engineering\n  - 搜索并爬取了 Intense-Visions/harness-engineering 项目（monorepo 结构、49 skills、12 personas）\n  - 爬取了 celesteanders 的 Harness Engineering Best Practices gist（Anthropic + OpenAI 社区总结）\n  - 将 GitHub 社区最佳实践整合进 HARNESS_ENGINEERING.md\n\n## 学习内容\n\n完成了《Harness工程导论》（李志琦老师）学习，创建了 HARNESS_ENGINEERING.md\n\n核心内容：\n- Harness 工程四层架构：约束层 → 信息层 → 验证层 → 修正层\n- 与提示工程、上下文工程的关系\n- 三个实践案例（Anthropic 实验、产品报价系统、OpenAI Codex CLI）\n- 用四层框架诊断 AI 系统的方法\n\nGitHub 新增内容（整合到 HARNESS_ENGINEERING.md 第七章）：\n- 架构原则：多代理职责分离、保持单体、上下文重置\n- 状态管理：JSON 持久化、仓库为真实来源、AGENTS.md 地图而非百科\n- 会话协议：定向→设置→验证基线→单任务→实现→测试→更新状态\n- 反馈循环：自动化验证反压、UI 自动化、sprint 合同\n- 上下文管理：稀缺资源、战略性子代理、确定性核心文件加载\n- 安全沙箱：OS 级隔离、文件系统限制、命令允许列表\n- 代码质量：机械强制不变量、持续清理债务、代理可读性优先\n- 恢复能力：Git 安全网、预期失败、计划定期重新生成\n\n## 待处理\n\n无\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775801090010}}
