{"type":"message","id":"9d776b07","parentId":"161dd1b5","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:05:52.684Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me create the AGENTS.md file.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_b4gkf2lua74x_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Harness Agent 配置\n\n## 模型\n- default: miaoda/miaoda-model-auto\n\n## 运行时\n- workspace: /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/agents/harness\n- 每次启动读取 SOUL.md\n\n## 工具\n- 全工具可用（搜索、读写文件、浏览器、飞书资源等）\n\n## 知识库\n- 启动时加载 `/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/HARNESS_ENGINEERING.md` 作为参考上下文\n","file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/agents/harness/AGENTS.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":98,"output":166,"cacheRead":38971,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39235,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775801146483,"responseId":"chatcmpl-ebefe7df-d039-4b8c-b27c-f336f511131c"}}
