{"type":"message","id":"f7f3d4f8","parentId":"ed810a16","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:06:03.415Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_sj7uga1uu43h_1","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/2026-04-10.md."}],"details":{"diff":"    ...\n  8 - 今天（14:00）：用户要求在 GitHub 上学习 harness engineering\n  9   - 搜索并爬取了 Intense-Visions/harness-engineering 项目（monorepo 结构、49 skills、12 personas）\n 10   - 爬取了 celesteanders 的 Harness Engineering Best Practices gist（Anthropic + OpenAI 社区总结）\n 11   - 将 GitHub 社区最佳实践整合进 HARNESS_ENGINEERING.md\n+12 - 今天（14:04）：用户要求学习 Harness 并创建对应的智能体\n+13   - 创建了 `agents/harness/SOUL.md`（智能体身份：控，驾驭工程专家）\n+14   - 创建了 `agents/harness/AGENTS.md`（配置）\n+15   - 以 HARNESS_ENGINEERING.md 为知识库核心\n 12 \n 13 ## 学习内容\n 14 \n 15 完成了《Harness工程导论》（李志琦老师）学习，创建了 HARNESS_ENGINEERING.md\n    ...","firstChangedLine":12},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775801163414}}
{"type":"message","id":"492b4272","parentId":"f7f3d4f8","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:06:12.963Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, now let me give the user a summary of what was created.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"搞定了 🦞\n\n给你创建了一个 Harness 智能体 **「控」**，放在 `agents/harness/` 目录下：\n\n- **SOUL.md** — 身份定义：驾驭工程专家，用四层框架（约束→信息→验证→修正）帮你诊断和设计 AI 系统\n- **AGENTS.md** — 配置，以完整的 HARNESS_ENGINEERING.md 为知识库\n\n---\n\n**简单说 Harness 是什么：**\n\n> **Agent = Model + Harness**\n> \n> 模型是\"大脑\"，Harness 是\"操作系统\"——给大模型配上缰绳、马鞍、护目镜，让它的力量被稳定、可控地释放。\n\n核心四层：\n- **约束层**：规定它能做什么、不能做什么（角色、格式、安全边界）\n- **信息层**：给它刚好够用的上下文（RAG、知识库、会话管理）\n- **验证层**：输出前做质量检验（格式、事实、安全）\n- **修正层**：错了怎么补救（重试、降级、转人工）\n\n想用它搞点什么？比如诊断你现有的 AI 项目，或者基于 Harness 框架设计一个新系统？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":354,"output":249,"cacheRead":39419,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40022,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775801163415,"responseId":"chatcmpl-11b77386-5971-4f99-b410-5af35e312e7a"}}
