{"type":"message","id":"8b44d5f7","parentId":"a3b30a34","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:06:31.371Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking the same thing again - \"学习什么事harness，并创建对应的智能体\". This is likely because they sent the message before my previous response arrived, or they're re-sending. I already did this - I created the harness agent. Let me just acknowledge this and let them know it's already done.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 嘿，这个任务刚已经搞定了呀 🦞\n\n今天 14:04 你就发过同样的需求，我给你：\n\n1. **创建了 Harness 智能体「控」** — 放在 `agents/harness/`\n   - `SOUL.md` — 身份与能力定义（驾驭工程专家）\n   - `AGENTS.md` — 配置，以 `HARNESS_ENGINEERING.md` 为知识库\n\n2. **给你总结了什么 Harness**：\n   > **Agent = Model + Harness**\n   > 模型是大脑，Harness 是操作系统——给大模型配上缰绳，让它的力量稳定可控地释放。\n   > \n   > 四层架构：**约束层 → 信息层 → 验证层 → 修正层**\n\n有什么具体想深入的方向？比如：\n- 用 Harness 四层诊断你现在做的 AI 项目？\n- 基于 Harness 框架设计一个新系统的架构？\n- 还是有其他想干的？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":6290,"output":266,"cacheRead":33595,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40151,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775801174856,"responseId":"chatcmpl-ba2ac900-c836-41fd-bcbf-0285be4a4d3a"}}
