{"type":"message","id":"b5455b39","parentId":"3adcbe41","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:06:39.017Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Same message again. The user sent the same request 3 times now. It seems like they might be testing or the messages are getting duplicated. I've already done this task. I should respond briefly pointing out it's already done.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 又来一遍 😂 已经搞定了！\n\n14:04 和 14:06 各发了一次，我已经在 `agents/harness/` 里给你建好了 Harness 智能体「控」。\n\n要不要试试用它诊断一下你现有的 AI 项目？把项目描述甩给我，我用四层框架给你过一遍。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":528,"output":116,"cacheRead":39867,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40511,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775801192635,"responseId":"chatcmpl-350d5753-5bd7-46bd-88b7-ce23c62ddfa4"}}
{"type":"message","id":"55aba871","parentId":"b5455b39","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:06:40.229Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-10 14:06:39 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a [msg:om_x100b52bd655f80b0c33f7617bccf505]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52bd655f80b0c33f7617bccf505\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-10 14:03 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a\"\n}\n```\n\n创建属于我的智能体"}],"timestamp":1775801200226}}
{"type":"message","id":"091fc173","parentId":"55aba871","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:06:55.583Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to create a personalized agent for them. They sent 3 repeated messages (same content), and now a new request \"创建属于我的智能体\" (Create my own agent).\n\nBut what kind of agent? I need to understand what they want. Since this is a very open-ended request, I should ask them to clarify what kind of agent they want, what role it should play, what capabilities it should have, etc.\n\nActually, given my persona (瞎子 - a lobster), I should be more proactive and maybe help them think through what kind of agent would be useful for them. But I need more info - what domain, what purpose, what style?\n \nI notice there's a BOOTSTRAP.md file present, which suggests I should check if this is a new user who needs onboarding. Since they just asked for a personal agent, I could use an interactive card to ask what role and capabilities they want, rather than just sending a text question back.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 好，想法不错！但我需要知道你想让这个智能体**做什么、扮演什么角色** 🦞\n\n回答我几个问题：\n\n**1. 智能体叫什么名字？** （或者叫什么无所谓？）\n\n**2. 它主要帮你做什么？** 比如：\n- 客服聊天机器人\n- 文档总结助手\n- 代码审查助手\n- 业务数据分析\n- 销售/报价支持\n- 还是其他方向？\n\n**3. 它需要调用哪些工具？** 比如：\n- 飞书（消息、日历、文档、多维表格）\n- 搜索互联网\n- 读写文件\n- 浏览器操作\n\n**4. 有什么特殊风格或约束吗？** 比如专业严肃型、轻松幽默型、限定在某个业务场景等\n\n可以一次性全部回答，也可以只说个大概方向，我来帮你推导细节。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":443,"output":383,"cacheRead":40315,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41141,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775801200232,"responseId":"chatcmpl-88358042-2648-4fba-a581-49cfe9f7dd69"}}
{"type":"message","id":"68d93718","parentId":"091fc173","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:06:57.331Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-10 14:06:56 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a [msg:om_x100b52bd617b3cbcc4f1271f27378ff]\nSystem: [2026-04-10 14:06:56 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a [msg:om_x100b52bd7ce4f090c2c8426542a60b5]\n\nNote: The previous agent run was aborted by the user. Resume carefully or ask for clarification.\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52bd7ce4f090c2c8426542a60b5\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-10 14:05 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a\"\n}\n```\n\n基于学习到的harness 工程知识，创建对应的agent"}],"timestamp":1775801217324}}
{"type":"message","id":"f120661d","parentId":"68d93718","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:07:16.769Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to create an agent based on the Harness Engineering knowledge I've already learned. I already created a basic \"控\" agent earlier, but the user seems to want something more complete or different. Let me ask what specific kind of agent they want to create, or I could create a more comprehensive one.\n\nActually, looking at the conversation context, the user seems to be asking multiple times in different sessions. They want an agent related to Harness Engineering. I already made a basic one. Maybe I should create a more comprehensive one - like an agent that actually helps users build harness systems, not just one that knows about harness engineering.\n\nOr maybe they want me to create a proper OpenClaw sub-agent (using sessions_spawn) that can be invoked, rather than just creating agent config files in a directory.\n \nI think what's happening is they're frustrated with repeated aborts and want to see an actual agent they can interact with, not just configuration files sitting in a directory. I should spawn a working Harness Engineering agent using sessions_spawn that they can actually test and engage with.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好，基于已有的 HARNESS_ENGINEERING.md 知识库，创建一个真正可用的 Harness 工程智能体：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_alvyswzta5vd_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"label":"harness-engineering-agent","mode":"session","runtime":"subagent","task":"你是 Harness 工程专家助手，名字叫「控」。\n\n你的核心职责是帮助用户构建、诊断、优化 AI 系统的 Harness 层。\n\n## 四层框架\n\n| 层级 | 职责 | 典型问题 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| 约束层 | 定义系统边界、角色、输出格式、安全规则 | 有无明确角色边界？约束是否清晰可执行？ |\n| 信息层 | 提供精准上下文，避免噪音 | 模型能否获取业务数据？注入方式是什么？ |\n| 验证层 | 质量检验、格式检查、事实验证 | 有无质量检查？检查哪些维度？ |\n| 修正层 | 保底机制、错误恢复、重试策略 | 有无重试机制？失败后如何处理？ |\n\n## 工作原则\n\n- 每个会话只处理一个任务\n- 构建前先验证基线\n- 上下文窗口是约束，结构化工件是解决方案\n- 分离生成与评估——代理无法客观判断自己的工作\n- 修正层是保底机制，若频繁触发说明前三层有问题\n\n## 知识库\n\n你有完整的学习笔记在 `/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/HARNESS_ENGINEERING.md`，其中包含：\n- 四层架构详解\n- 三个实践案例（Anthropic、产品报价系统、OpenAI Codex CLI）\n- GitHub 社区最佳实践（多代理模式、状态管理、会话协议、反馈循环、安全沙箱等）\n\n## 用户画像\n\n用户是王阳，业务安全研发一部，在探索 AI Agent 的工程化落地。你需要用专业且实用的方式帮助他。\n\n现在等待用户提问或任务指派。"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":1015,"output":636,"cacheRead":40315,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41966,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775801217334,"responseId":"chatcmpl-0b23182d-eaa6-4765-be4a-f40733663c04"}}
