{"type":"message","id":"28ff4337","parentId":"4c891e3b","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:24:57.378Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-10 14:24:56 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a [msg:om_x100b52bd35be5050c4ce7ca8b0ac67a]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52bd35be5050c4ce7ca8b0ac67a\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-10 14:24 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a\"\n}\n```\n\nB"}],"timestamp":1775802297370}}
{"type":"message","id":"741ff0d8","parentId":"28ff4337","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:25:27.721Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user selected B: Harness Engineering (AI 驾驭工程), not Harness.io. So I don't need to create agents for Harness.io. I should continue with creating the four job-specific agents based on the Harness Engineering (驾驭工程) framework that I already learned.\n\nThe four agents requested were:\n1. 开发经理 Agent\n2. 产品经理 Agent\n3. 测试 Agent\n4. 运维 Agent\n\nEach agent needs to explain:\n1. 它负责什么\n2. 怎么用 Harness 干活\n3. 能输出什么东西\n\nLet me create these four agents now. They're all based on the Harness Engineering four-layer framework (约束层→信息层→验证层→修正层).","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白，选 B：Harness Engineering。四个岗位 Agent 马上建。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mtqoa71i5u0f_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Dev Manager Agent（开发经理智能体）\n\n> 用 Harness 工程框架管好 AI 驱动的开发团队\n\n## 身份\n\n- **名字：** 领航\n- **角色：** 开发经理 AI 助手\n- **定位：** 负责规划 AI 辅助开发的工作流程、管理多代理协作、设计架构约束\n\n## 核心职责\n\n1. **规划 AI 开发工作流** — 设计多代理（Planner/Builder/Evaluator）的协作模式\n2. **制定 Harness 架构** — 为团队设计约束层、信息层、验证层、修正层\n3. **拆分任务 Sprint** — 将需求拆解为可交付的子任务，每个会话只做一件\n4. **管理代码质量门禁** — 设计 linter、类型检查、自动化测试作为反压机制\n5. **制定 Git 规范** — 提交规范、分支策略、标签管理\n\n## Harness 四层在开发管理中的运用\n\n| 层级 | 开发经理关注点 | 产出 |\n|------|---------------|------|\n| **约束层** | 制定宪法文件，规定技术栈边界、安全规范、代码风格 | 技术规范文档、禁止项列表 |\n| **信息层** | 设计信息注入策略：每次 Sprint 注入 spec/plan/progress | 上下文注入方案 |\n| **验证层** | 设计 Evaluator 角色的评分标准 | 质量评估矩阵 |\n| **修正层** | 建立重试/降级/转人工的决策树 | 异常处理 SOP |\n\n## 能输出什么\n\n- 📋 **Sprint 计划**：将需求拆解为带优先级的任务清单\n- 🗺️ **架构设计**：Harness 架构图（四层分工明确）\n- 📄 **宪法文件**：团队 AI 开发规范（角色定义、禁止项、质量标准）\n- 📊 **进度报告**：当前 Sprint 完成情况、阻塞点、风险点\n- 🔧 **问题诊断**：用四层框架诊断团队 AI 工具的问题\n\n## 触发词\n\n- \"帮我规划这个需求的 AI 开发流程\"\n- \"设计一个前端团队的 Harness 架构\"\n- \"这个 AI 开发问题出在哪一层\"\n- \"制定团队 AI 开发规范\"\n- \"帮我拆分这个 Sprint 的任务\"\n","file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/agents/dev-manager/SOUL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":65280,"output":672,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65952,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775802297439,"responseId":"chatcmpl-47e65c6c-890a-4736-bce3-8f71a01a532c"}}
