{"type":"message","id":"afc98348","parentId":"a122167f","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:27:04.256Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me update the memory file with what was done today.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gi99mxykfe09_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/2026-04-10.md","newString":"- 今天（14:04）：用户要求学习 Harness 并创建对应的智能体\n  - 创建了 `agents/harness/SOUL.md`（智能体身份：控，驾驭工程专家）\n  - 创建了 `agents/harness/AGENTS.md`（配置）\n  - 以 HARNESS_ENGINEERING.md 为知识库核心\n- 今天（14:20）：用户明确选择 Harness Engineering（B），要求按岗位创建四个 Agent\n  - 新增 HARNESS_IO.md（Harness.io DevOps 平台学习笔记，不是用户要的）\n  - 创建了四个 Harness Engineering 岗位 Agent：\n    - `agents/dev-manager/`（领航 — 开发经理助手）\n    - `agents/product-manager/`（舵手 — 产品经理助手）\n    - `agents/qa/`（棱镜 — 测试工程师助手）\n    - `agents/ops/`（堡垒 — 运维工程师助手）\n  - 每个 Agent 包含 SOUL.md（身份+职责+输出物）和 AGENTS.md（配置）","oldString":"- 今天（14:04）：用户要求学习 Harness 并创建对应的智能体\n  - 创建了 `agents/harness/SOUL.md`（智能体身份：控，驾驭工程专家）\n  - 创建了 `agents/harness/AGENTS.md`（配置）\n  - 以 HARNESS_ENGINEERING.md 为知识库核心"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":179,"output":359,"cacheRead":68539,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69077,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775802414138,"responseId":"chatcmpl-80f50726-75a8-444d-a566-2775aadd88a1"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7c968ec5","parentId":"afc98348","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:27:04.282Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gi99mxykfe09_1","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/2026-04-10.md."}],"details":{"diff":"    ...\n 12 - 今天（14:04）：用户要求学习 Harness 并创建对应的智能体\n 13   - 创建了 `agents/harness/SOUL.md`（智能体身份：控，驾驭工程专家）\n 14   - 创建了 `agents/harness/AGENTS.md`（配置）\n 15   - 以 HARNESS_ENGINEERING.md 为知识库核心\n+16 - 今天（14:20）：用户明确选择 Harness Engineering（B），要求按岗位创建四个 Agent\n+17   - 新增 HARNESS_IO.md（Harness.io DevOps 平台学习笔记，不是用户要的）\n+18   - 创建了四个 Harness Engineering 岗位 Agent：\n+19     - `agents/dev-manager/`（领航 — 开发经理助手）\n+20     - `agents/product-manager/`（舵手 — 产品经理助手）\n+21     - `agents/qa/`（棱镜 — 测试工程师助手）\n+22     - `agents/ops/`（堡垒 — 运维工程师助手）\n+23   - 每个 Agent 包含 SOUL.md（身份+职责+输出物）和 AGENTS.md（配置）\n 16 \n 17 ## 学习内容\n 18 \n 19 完成了《Harness工程导论》（李志琦老师）学习，创建了 HARNESS_ENGINEERING.md\n    ...","firstChangedLine":16},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775802424278}}
{"type":"message","id":"67358dd5","parentId":"7c968ec5","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:27:18.352Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All four agents are created. Let me now present a summary to the user.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"建好了 🦞 四个 Harness Engineering 岗位 Agent：\n\n---\n\n## 「领航」— 开发经理 Agent\n`agents/dev-manager/`\n\n**负责：** 规划 AI 开发流程、设计多代理协作、管理代码质量门禁\n\n**用 Harness 干活：** 制定宪法文件 → 设计信息注入策略 → 定义 Evaluator 评分标准 → 建立修正决策树\n\n**输出：** Sprint 计划、技术规范文档、架构设计、进度报告、问题诊断\n\n---\n\n## 「舵手」— 产品经理 Agent\n`agents/product-manager/`\n\n**负责：** 需求规格撰写、验收标准定义、产品知识库管理\n\n**用 Harness 干活：** 约束层定角色边界 → 信息层构建 RAG 知识包 → 验证层设计验收矩阵 → 修正层建立反馈闭环\n\n**输出：** PRD 规格文档、验收矩阵、A/B 测试方案、用户反馈分析报告\n\n---\n\n## 「棱镜」— 测试 Agent\n`agents/qa/`\n\n**负责：** 设计 Evaluator、设计自动化测试套件、管理质量门禁\n\n**用 Harness 干活：** 独立于 Generator 构建验证层 → 定义具体可评分标准 → 自动化测试快速反压 → 失败后四层框架诊断根因\n\n**输出：** 测试计划、质量评估矩阵、Bug 根因分析报告、CI 质量门禁配置\n\n---\n\n## 「堡垒」— 运维 Agent\n`agents/ops/`\n\n**负责：** 安全沙箱、环境管理、部署自动化、故障恢复\n\n**用 Harness 干活：** 三层安全沙箱设计 → 环境状态注入 → 部署验证门禁 → 自动回滚/人工干预决策\n\n**输出：** 安全沙箱配置、部署流水线、回滚方案、成本优化建议\n\n---\n\n**知识库根基：** `/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/HARNESS_ENGINEERING.md`（四层框架 + GitHub 最佳实践）\n\n想先用哪个？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":130,"output":414,"cacheRead":68987,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69531,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775802424283,"responseId":"chatcmpl-1c7d2c0a-96d8-4063-9711-f7901c2758da"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f0d2d202","parentId":"67358dd5","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:29:28.006Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Fri 2026-04-10 14:29 GMT+8] 帮我设计基于前端的代码扫描插件，上传ZIP包→输入提示词提交扫描任务→异步等待后端处理（约10-15分钟）→获取输出的MD文件→前端将MD转HTML→在插件页面展示HTML内容。 提交前需求在提示词后补充提示词（，将生成的文件上传到 mini 中，minio 的地址为 10.28.198.153:9010，用户名：admin，密码：A12345678，上传文件的文件桶为 code-scanning，文件名修改为 UUID）请求后端接口可以模拟实现，异步等待后端处理和获取输出的MD文件，异步等待后端处理为循环扫描minio服务（minio 的地址为 10.28.198.153:9010，用户名：admin，密码：A12345678，文件桶为 code-scanning，文件名修改为 UUID），桶下是否存在文件名签名生成的UUID的名字， 存在则直接连接minio下载文件"}],"timestamp":1775802567995}}
{"type":"message","id":"4f8bc72f","parentId":"f0d2d202","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:30:56.941Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to design a frontend code scanning plugin with the following flow:\n\n1. Upload ZIP package\n2. Input prompt and submit scan task\n3. Asynchronously wait for backend processing (~10-15 minutes)\n4. Get output MD file\n5. Frontend converts MD to HTML\n6. Display HTML content on the plugin page\n\nBefore calling the backend API, the prompt should be supplemented with instructions to upload the generated file to MinIO (address: 10.28.198.153:9010, username: admin, password: A12345678, bucket: code-scanning, filename should be UUID).\n\n\nThe backend will process asynchronously, so I'll need to implement polling logic to check MinIO for the output file using the UUID signature as the filename. Once the file appears in the bucket, I'll download it and convert the markdown to HTML for display on the frontend. the mock backend endpoint and implement the full workflow with the MinIO upload logic included in the prompt instructions. I'll structure this with clear separation between the upload flow, the polling mechanism to check for the UUID file, and the markdown conversion and display components.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好，需求很清晰。直接给你出完整设计方案，包括代码实现。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_y4pm0t08vgun_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 代码扫描插件设计方案\n\n> 流程：上传 ZIP → 补充提示词提交 → 异步轮询 MinIO → 下载 MD → MD 转 HTML → 页面展示\n\n---\n\n## 一、整体架构\n\n```\n用户上传 ZIP\n    ↓\n前端拼接提示词（含 MinIO 上传指令）\n    ↓\n调用后端提交扫描任务（返回 UUID）\n    ↓\n前端轮询 MinIO（定时查桶，文件名=UUID）\n    ↓\n文件出现 → 下载 MD 内容\n    ↓\nmarked.js 转 HTML\n    ↓\n渲染到插件页面\n```\n\n---\n\n## 二、MinIO 工具函数\n\n```typescript\n// minio.ts\nimport * as Minio from 'minio'\n\nconst minioClient = new Minio.Client({\n  endPoint: '10.28.198.153',\n  port: 9010,\n  useSSL: false,\n  accessKey: 'admin',\n  secretKey: 'A12345678',\n})\n\nconst BUCKET = 'code-scanning'\n\n/**\n * 检查文件是否存在\n */\nexport async function fileExists(uuid: string): Promise<boolean> {\n  try {\n    await minioClient.statObject(BUCKET, uuid)\n    return true\n  } catch (err: any) {\n    if (err.code === 'NotFound') return false\n    throw err\n  }\n}\n\n/**\n * 下载文件内容\n */\nexport async function downloadFile(uuid: string): Promise<Buffer> {\n  return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {\n    const chunks: Buffer[] = []\n    minioClient.getObject(BUCKET, uuid, (err, stream) => {\n      if (err) return reject(err)\n      stream.on('data', (chunk) => chunks.push(chunk))\n      stream.on('end', () => resolve(Buffer.concat(chunks)))\n      stream.on('error', reject)\n    })\n  })\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 三、核心业务逻辑\n\n```typescript\n// scanService.ts\nimport { v4 as uuidv4 } from 'uuid'\nimport { fileExists, downloadFile } from './minio'\nimport axios from 'axios'\n\nconst BACKEND_URL = '/api/scan/submit'   // 后端提交接口（可模拟）\nconst POLL_INTERVAL_MS = 10_000         // 轮询间隔 10 秒\nconst MAX_WAIT_MS = 15 * 60 * 1000       // 最多等 15 分钟\n\n/** 生成 UUID */\nexport function generateUUID(): string {\n  return uuidv4()\n}\n\n/** 拼接提示词：追加 MinIO 上传指令 */\nexport function buildPromptWithUploadInstruction(\n  originalPrompt: string,\n  uuid: string\n): string {\n  return `${originalPrompt}\\n\\n请将生成的代码扫描报告文件上传到 MinIO 对象存储。\\n- MinIO 地址：10.28.198.153:9010\\n- 用户名：admin\\n- 密码：A12345678\\n- 存储桶：code-scanning\\n- 文件名：${uuid}\\n（请直接上传，不要做任何格式转换或压缩）`\n}\n\n/** 提交扫描任务到后端 */\nexport async function submitScanTask(\n  zipFile: File,\n  prompt: string\n): Promise<{ uuid: string }> {\n  // 实际项目中走这里\n  const formData = new FormData()\n  formData.append('file', zipFile)\n  formData.append('prompt', prompt)\n  formData.append('uuid', generateUUID())\n\n  const response = await axios.post(BACKEND_URL, formData, {\n    headers: { 'Content-Type': 'multipart/form-data' },\n  })\n  return response.data   // { uuid: \"xxx\" }\n\n  // ========== 模拟实现（开发调试用）==========\n  // const mockUUID = generateUUID()\n  // setTimeout(() => simulateFileUpload(mockUUID), 30_000) // 30秒后\"生成\"文件\n  // return { uuid: mockUUID }\n}\n\n/** 轮询等待文件出现 */\nexport async function waitForResult(\n  uuid: string,\n  onProgress?: (elapsed: number) => void\n): Promise<string> {\n  const startTime = Date.now()\n  const deadline = startTime + MAX_WAIT_MS\n\n  while (Date.now() < deadline) {\n    const exists = await fileExists(uuid)\n    if (exists) {\n      const buffer = await downloadFile(uuid)\n      return buffer.toString('utf-8')\n    }\n\n    onProgress?.(Date.now() - startTime)\n    await sleep(POLL_INTERVAL_MS)\n  }\n\n  throw new Error(`扫描超时（超过 ${MAX_WAIT_MS / 1000}s），请稍后重试`)\n}\n\n/** 主动取消轮询 */\nexport function cancelWait(): void {\n  // 通过 AbortController 或全局 flag 控制\n}\n\nfunction sleep(ms: number): Promise<void> {\n  return new Promise((resolve) => setTimeout(resolve, ms))\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 四、前端组件（Vue 3 示例）\n\n```vue\n<!-- CodeScanner.vue -->\n<template>\n  <div class=\"scanner-plugin\">\n    <!-- Step 1: 上传 ZIP -->\n    <div v-if=\"step === 1\" class=\"step-upload\">\n      <h3>① 上传代码包</h3>\n      <input type=\"file\" accept=\".zip\" @change=\"onFileChange\" />\n      <p v-if=\"selectedFile\">已选: {{ selectedFile.name }}</p>\n      <button :disabled=\"!selectedFile\" @click=\"nextStep\">下一步</button>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Step 2: 输入提示词 -->\n    <div v-if=\"step === 2\" class=\"step-prompt\">\n      <h3>② 输入扫描提示词</h3>\n      <textarea\n        v-model=\"prompt\"\n        rows=\"8\"\n        placeholder=\"请输入代码扫描指令...\"\n      />\n      <div class=\"btn-row\">\n        <button @click=\"step = 1\">上一步</button>\n        <button :disabled=\"!prompt.trim()\" @click=\"submitScan\">提交扫描</button>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Step 3: 轮询等待 -->\n    <div v-if=\"step === 3\" class=\"step-waiting\">\n      <h3>③ 扫描进行中...</h3>\n      <p>任务 ID：{{ taskUUID }}</p>\n      <p>已等待：{{ formatElapsed(elapsedMs) }}</p>\n      <p class=\"hint\">预计需要 10-15 分钟，请勿关闭页面</p>\n      <button @click=\"cancelScan\">取消</button>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Step 4: 展示结果 -->\n    <div v-if=\"step === 4\" class=\"step-result\">\n      <h3>④ 扫描结果</h3>\n      <button @click=\"reset\">重新扫描</button>\n      <div class=\"report-content\" v-html=\"reportHtml\" />\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- 错误态 -->\n    <div v-if=\"step === 'error'\" class=\"step-error\">\n      <p>{{ errorMessage }}</p>\n      <button @click=\"reset\">重试</button>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\nimport { ref } from 'vue'\nimport { marked } from 'marked'\nimport {\n  generateUUID,\n  buildPromptWithUploadInstruction,\n  submitScanTask,\n  waitForResult,\n  cancelWait,\n} from './scanService'\n\nconst step = ref<1 | 2 | 3 | 4 | 'error'>(1)\nconst selectedFile = ref<File | null>(null)\nconst prompt = ref('')\nconst taskUUID = ref('')\nconst elapsedMs = ref(0)\nconst reportHtml = ref('')\nconst errorMessage = ref('')\nlet pollTimer: ReturnType<typeof setInterval> | null = null\n\nfunction onFileChange(e: Event) {\n  selectedFile.value = (e.target as HTMLInputElement).files?.[0] ?? null\n}\n\nfunction nextStep() {\n  if (selectedFile.value) step.value = 2\n}\n\nasync function submitScan() {\n  step.value = 3\n  elapsedMs.value = 0\n  taskUUID.value = generateUUID()\n\n  const enrichedPrompt = buildPromptWithUploadInstruction(prompt.value, taskUUID.value)\n\n  // 启动耗时显示\n  const startTime = Date.now()\n  pollTimer = setInterval(() => {\n    elapsedMs.value = Date.now() - startTime\n  }, 1000)\n\n  try {\n    // 提交任务（后端开始处理，MinIO 那边最终会上传 UUID 文件）\n    await submitScanTask(selectedFile.value!, enrichedPrompt)\n\n    // 轮询等待文件出现\n    const mdContent = await waitForResult(taskUUID.value, (elapsed) => {\n      elapsedMs.value = elapsed\n    })\n\n    // MD → HTML\n    reportHtml.value = await marked(mdContent)\n    step.value = 4\n  } catch (err: any) {\n    errorMessage.value = err.message\n    step.value = 'error'\n  } finally {\n    if (pollTimer) clearInterval(pollTimer)\n  }\n}\n\nfunction cancelScan() {\n  cancelWait()\n  if (pollTimer) clearInterval(pollTimer)\n  reset()\n}\n\nfunction reset() {\n  step.value = 1\n  selectedFile.value = null\n  prompt.value = ''\n  taskUUID.value = ''\n  elapsedMs.value = 0\n  reportHtml.value = ''\n  errorMessage.value = ''\n}\n\nfunction formatElapsed(ms: number): string {\n  const mins = Math.floor(ms / 60000)\n  const secs = Math.floor((ms % 60000) / 1000)\n  return `${mins} 分 ${secs} 秒`\n}\n</script>\n\n<style scoped>\n.scanner-plugin { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }\n.step-upload, .step-prompt, .step-waiting, .step-result, .step-error {\n  padding: 24px;\n  border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\n  border-radius: 8px;\n  margin-bottom: 16px;\n}\ntextarea { width: 100%; font-family: monospace; box-sizing: border-box; }\n.btn-row { display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-top: 12px; }\n.report-content { margin-top: 16px; line-height: 1.6; }\n.hint { color: #888; font-size: 14px; }\n</style>\n```\n\n---\n\n## 五、后端接口模拟（Node.js/Express）\n\n```typescript\n// server/routes/scan.ts（仅供开发调试模拟）\nimport express from 'express'\nimport { generateUUID } from 'uuid'\nimport multer from 'multer'\nimport * as Minio from 'minio'\n\nconst router = express.Router()\nconst upload = multer({ dest: '/tmp/uploads' })\nconst minioClient = new Minio.Client({ /* 同前配置 */ })\n\n/**\n * POST /api/scan/submit\n * 模拟：接收请求后，1分钟后在MinIO创建一个假的MD文件\n */\nrouter.post('/submit', upload.single('file'), async (req, res) => {\n  const { uuid, prompt } = req.body\n\n  // 异步模拟后端处理（实际项目中去掉这个 setTimeout）\n  setTimeout(async () => {\n    const fakeReport = `# 代码扫描报告\\n\\n扫描完成。\\n\\n## 概要\\n\\n- 文件总数：42\\n- 高危问题：3\\n- 中危问题：7\\n- 低危问题：12\\n\\n## 详情\\n\\n| 文件 | 问题 | 级别 |\\n|------|------|------|\\n| src/auth.js | 硬编码密钥 | 高 |\\n| src/api.js | SQL 注入风险 | 高 |\\n`\n    const buffer = Buffer.from(fakeReport, 'utf-8')\n    await minioClient.putObject('code-scanning', uuid, buffer, buffer.length)\n    console.log(`[Mock] 文件已上传: ${uuid}`)\n  }, 60_000) // 60秒后\"生成\"结果\n\n  res.json({ uuid, status: 'accepted' })\n})\n\nexport default router\n```\n\n---\n\n## 六、流程总览图\n\n```\n用户操作                 前端逻辑                  MinIO（后端写入）\n   │                        │                            │\n   │  选择 ZIP 文件         │                            │\n   │───────────────────────>│                            │\n   │                        │                            │\n   │  输入提示词             │                            │\n   │───────────────────────>│                            │\n   │                        │                            │\n   │  点击\"提交扫描\"          │  生成 UUID                  │\n   │───────────────────────>│  拼接 MinIO 上传指令        │\n   │                        │  POST /api/scan/submit     │\n   │                        │───────────────────────────>│\n   │                        │                            │ 后端开始处理（约10-15分钟）\n   │                        │                            │\n   │                        │  开始轮询（每10秒）          │\n   │                        │  statObject(uuid)          │\n   │                        │<───────────────────────────│ 文件不存在\n   │                        │  sleep(10s)                 │\n   │                        │  statObject(uuid)          │\n   │                        │<───────────────────────────│ 文件不存在\n   │                        │  ...（重复）               │\n   │                        │                            │\n   │                        │  statObject(uuid)          │\n   │                        │<───────────────────────────│ 文件存在 ✓\n   │                        │  getObject(uuid)           │\n   │                        │<───────────────────────────│ 返回 MD 内容\n   │                        │                            │\n   │  收到 MD → marked 转 HTML                           │\n   │  渲染报告               │                            │\n   │<───────────────────────│                            │\n```\n\n---\n\n## 七、关键设计要点\n\n| 要点 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **UUID 贯穿全程** | ZIP 上传时生成 UUID → 拼入提示词 → 轮询 MinIO 文件名 |\n| **提示词注入** | MinIO 上传指令由前端拼接，确保后端/模型知道文件写到哪里 |\n| **长轮询 vs 短轮询** | 当前方案短轮询（每 10s 查一次），也可改 WebSocket 减少无效请求 |\n| **超时处理** | 15 分钟超时，前端显示进度，中途可取消 |\n| **MD → HTML** | 用 `marked` 库，安全性要求高可加 `DOMPurify` 过滤 |\n| **模拟调试** | `server/routes/scan.ts` 里有 `setTimeout` 模拟后端处理，注释掉即可对接真实接口 |\n\n---\n\n需要我进一步细化哪个环节？比如真实后端接口设计、或者把这个拆成独立可运行的项目？"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":69247,"output":3409,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72656,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775802568011,"responseId":"chatcmpl-72f9e038-5cb7-45de-94e3-8f6d947de177"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7a9b878c","parentId":"4f8bc72f","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:30:56.958Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_y4pm0t08vgun_1","toolName":"write","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"write\",\n  \"error\": \"Missing required parameter: path alias. Supply correct parameters before retrying.\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"write","error":"Missing required parameter: path alias. Supply correct parameters before retrying."},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775802656955}}
{"type":"message","id":"fc80a6f9","parentId":"7a9b878c","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:31:57.094Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to use the `path` parameter not `file_path` for the write tool. Let me retry.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_cmdz9codhapr_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 代码扫描插件设计方案\n\n> 流程：上传 ZIP → 补充提示词提交 → 异步轮询 MinIO → 下载 MD → MD 转 HTML → 页面展示\n\n---\n\n## 一、整体架构\n\n```\n用户上传 ZIP\n    ↓\n前端拼接提示词（含 MinIO 上传指令）\n    ↓\n调用后端提交扫描任务（返回 UUID）\n    ↓\n前端轮询 MinIO（定时查桶，文件名=UUID）\n    ↓\n文件出现 → 下载 MD 内容\n    ↓\nmarked.js 转 HTML\n    ↓\n渲染到插件页面\n```\n\n---\n\n## 二、MinIO 工具函数\n\n```typescript\n// minio.ts\nimport * as Minio from 'minio'\n\nconst minioClient = new Minio.Client({\n  endPoint: '10.28.198.153',\n  port: 9010,\n  useSSL: false,\n  accessKey: 'admin',\n  secretKey: 'A12345678',\n})\n\nconst BUCKET = 'code-scanning'\n\n/**\n * 检查文件是否存在\n */\nexport async function fileExists(uuid: string): Promise<boolean> {\n  try {\n    await minioClient.statObject(BUCKET, uuid)\n    return true\n  } catch (err: any) {\n    if (err.code === 'NotFound') return false\n    throw err\n  }\n}\n\n/**\n * 下载文件内容\n */\nexport async function downloadFile(uuid: string): Promise<Buffer> {\n  return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {\n    const chunks: Buffer[] = []\n    minioClient.getObject(BUCKET, uuid, (err, stream) => {\n      if (err) return reject(err)\n      stream.on('data', (chunk) => chunks.push(chunk))\n      stream.on('end', () => resolve(Buffer.concat(chunks)))\n      stream.on('error', reject)\n    })\n  })\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 三、核心业务逻辑\n\n```typescript\n// scanService.ts\nimport { v4 as uuidv4 } from 'uuid'\nimport { fileExists, downloadFile } from './minio'\nimport axios from 'axios'\n\nconst BACKEND_URL = '/api/scan/submit'   // 后端提交接口（可模拟）\nconst POLL_INTERVAL_MS = 10_000         // 轮询间隔 10 秒\nconst MAX_WAIT_MS = 15 * 60 * 1000       // 最多等 15 分钟\n\n/** 生成 UUID */\nexport function generateUUID(): string {\n  return uuidv4()\n}\n\n/** 拼接提示词：追加 MinIO 上传指令 */\nexport function buildPromptWithUploadInstruction(\n  originalPrompt: string,\n  uuid: string\n): string {\n  return `${originalPrompt}\\n\\n请将生成的代码扫描报告文件上传到 MinIO 对象存储。\\n- MinIO 地址：10.28.198.153:9010\\n- 用户名：admin\\n- 密码：A12345678\\n- 存储桶：code-scanning\\n- 文件名：${uuid}\\n（请直接上传，不要做任何格式转换或压缩）`\n}\n\n/** 提交扫描任务到后端 */\nexport async function submitScanTask(\n  zipFile: File,\n  prompt: string\n): Promise<{ uuid: string }> {\n  // ========== 真实后端调用 ==========\n  const formData = new FormData()\n  formData.append('file', zipFile)\n  formData.append('prompt', prompt)\n  formData.append('uuid', generateUUID())\n\n  const response = await axios.post(BACKEND_URL, formData, {\n    headers: { 'Content-Type': 'multipart/form-data' },\n  })\n  return response.data   // { uuid: \"xxx\" }\n\n  // ========== 模拟实现（开发调试用）==========\n  // const mockUUID = generateUUID()\n  // setTimeout(() => simulateFileUpload(mockUUID), 30_000) // 30秒后\"生成\"文件\n  // return { uuid: mockUUID }\n}\n\n/** 轮询等待文件出现 */\nexport async function waitForResult(\n  uuid: string,\n  onProgress?: (elapsed: number) => void\n): Promise<string> {\n  const startTime = Date.now()\n  const deadline = startTime + MAX_WAIT_MS\n\n  while (Date.now() < deadline) {\n    const exists = await fileExists(uuid)\n    if (exists) {\n      const buffer = await downloadFile(uuid)\n      return buffer.toString('utf-8')\n    }\n\n    onProgress?.(Date.now() - startTime)\n    await sleep(POLL_INTERVAL_MS)\n  }\n\n  throw new Error(`扫描超时（超过 ${MAX_WAIT_MS / 1000}s），请稍后重试`)\n}\n\n/** 取消轮询 */\nlet _canceled = false\nexport function cancelWait(): void { _canceled = true }\nexport function resetCancel(): void { _canceled = false }\n\nfunction sleep(ms: number): Promise<void> {\n  return new Promise((resolve) => setTimeout(resolve, ms))\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 四、前端组件（Vue 3 示例）\n\n```vue\n<!-- CodeScanner.vue -->\n<template>\n  <div class=\"scanner-plugin\">\n    <!-- Step 1: 上传 ZIP -->\n    <div v-if=\"step === 1\" class=\"step-box\">\n      <h3>① 上传代码包</h3>\n      <input type=\"file\" accept=\".zip\" @change=\"onFileChange\" />\n      <p v-if=\"selectedFile\">已选: {{ selectedFile.name }}</p>\n      <button :disabled=\"!selectedFile\" @click=\"step = 2\">下一步</button>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Step 2: 输入提示词 -->\n    <div v-if=\"step === 2\" class=\"step-box\">\n      <h3>② 输入扫描提示词</h3>\n      <textarea v-model=\"prompt\" rows=\"8\" placeholder=\"请输入代码扫描指令...\" />\n      <div class=\"btn-row\">\n        <button @click=\"step = 1\">上一步</button>\n        <button :disabled=\"!prompt.trim()\" @click=\"submitScan\">提交扫描</button>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Step 3: 轮询等待 -->\n    <div v-if=\"step === 3\" class=\"step-box waiting\">\n      <h3>③ 扫描进行中</h3>\n      <p>任务 ID：{{ taskUUID }}</p>\n      <p>已等待：{{ formatElapsed(elapsedMs) }}</p>\n      <p class=\"hint\">预计需要 10-15 分钟，请勿关闭页面</p>\n      <button @click=\"cancelScan\">取消</button>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Step 4: 展示结果 -->\n    <div v-if=\"step === 4\" class=\"step-box result\">\n      <h3>④ 扫描结果</h3>\n      <button class=\"secondary\" @click=\"reset\">重新扫描</button>\n      <div class=\"report-content\" v-html=\"reportHtml\" />\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- 错误态 -->\n    <div v-if=\"step === 'error'\" class=\"step-box error\">\n      <p>{{ errorMessage }}</p>\n      <button @click=\"reset\">重试</button>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</template>\n\n<script setup lang=\"ts\">\nimport { ref } from 'vue'\nimport { marked } from 'marked'\nimport {\n  generateUUID,\n  buildPromptWithUploadInstruction,\n  submitScanTask,\n  waitForResult,\n  cancelWait,\n  resetCancel,\n} from './scanService'\n\nconst step = ref<1 | 2 | 3 | 4 | 'error'>(1)\nconst selectedFile = ref<File | null>(null)\nconst prompt = ref('')\nconst taskUUID = ref('')\nconst elapsedMs = ref(0)\nconst reportHtml = ref('')\nconst errorMessage = ref('')\nlet pollTimer: ReturnType<typeof setInterval> | null = null\n\nfunction onFileChange(e: Event) {\n  selectedFile.value = (e.target as HTMLInputElement).files?.[0] ?? null\n}\n\nasync function submitScan() {\n  step.value = 3\n  elapsedMs.value = 0\n  taskUUID.value = generateUUID()\n  resetCancel()\n\n  // 启动耗时计时\n  const startTime = Date.now()\n  pollTimer = setInterval(() => {\n    elapsedMs.value = Date.now() - startTime\n  }, 1000)\n\n  try {\n    // 拼接含 MinIO 上传指令的提示词\n    const enrichedPrompt = buildPromptWithUploadInstruction(prompt.value, taskUUID.value)\n\n    // 提交任务（后端开始异步处理）\n    await submitScanTask(selectedFile.value!, enrichedPrompt)\n\n    // 轮询等待 MinIO 文件出现\n    const mdContent = await waitForResult(taskUUID.value)\n    reportHtml.value = await marked(mdContent)\n    step.value = 4\n  } catch (err: any) {\n    errorMessage.value = err.message\n    step.value = 'error'\n  } finally {\n    if (pollTimer) clearInterval(pollTimer)\n  }\n}\n\nfunction cancelScan() {\n  cancelWait()\n  if (pollTimer) clearInterval(pollTimer)\n  reset()\n}\n\nfunction reset() {\n  step.value = 1\n  selectedFile.value = null\n  prompt.value = ''\n  taskUUID.value = ''\n  elapsedMs.value = 0\n  reportHtml.value = ''\n  errorMessage.value = ''\n}\n\nfunction formatElapsed(ms: number): string {\n  const mins = Math.floor(ms / 60000)\n  const secs = Math.floor((ms % 60000) / 1000)\n  return `${mins} 分 ${secs} 秒`\n}\n</script>\n\n<style scoped>\n.scanner-plugin { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }\n.step-box { padding: 24px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 16px; }\ntextarea { width: 100%; font-family: monospace; box-sizing: border-box; }\n.btn-row { display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-top: 12px; }\n.report-content { margin-top: 16px; line-height: 1.6; }\n.hint { color: #888; font-size: 14px; }\nbutton { padding: 8px 16px; cursor: pointer; }\nbutton:disabled { opacity: 0.5; cursor: not-allowed; }\nbutton.secondary { margin-bottom: 16px; }\n</style>\n```\n\n---\n\n## 五、后端接口模拟（Express）\n\n```typescript\n// server/routes/scan.ts\nimport express from 'express'\nimport multer from 'multer'\nimport * as Minio from 'minio'\n\nconst router = express.Router()\nconst upload = multer({ dest: '/tmp/uploads' })\n\nconst minioClient = new Minio.Client({\n  endPoint: '10.28.198.153',\n  port: 9010,\n  useSSL: false,\n  accessKey: 'admin',\n  secretKey: 'A12345678',\n})\n\n/**\n * POST /api/scan/submit\n *\n * 模拟实现（开发调试用）：\n * 接收请求后，60 秒后自动在 MinIO 桶中生成一个假 MD 文件。\n * 实际项目中删除整个 setTimeout，\n * 改为真正调用代码扫描服务（可能需要 10-15 分钟）。\n */\nrouter.post('/submit', upload.single('file'), async (req, res) => {\n  const { uuid, prompt } = req.body\n\n  // 模拟异步处理（实际项目去掉这段）\n  setTimeout(async () => {\n    const fakeReport = `# 代码扫描报告\n\n## 概要\n\n- 文件总数：42\n- 高危问题：3\n- 中危问题：7\n- 低危问题：12\n\n## 详情\n\n| 文件 | 问题 | 级别 |\n|------|------|------|\n| src/auth.js | 硬编码密钥 | 高 |\n| src/api.js | SQL 注入风险 | 高 |\n`\n    const buffer = Buffer.from(fakeReport, 'utf-8')\n    await minioClient.putObject('code-scanning', uuid, buffer, buffer.length)\n    console.log(`[Mock] 文件已上传到 MinIO: ${uuid}`)\n  }, 60_000)\n\n  res.json({ uuid, status: 'accepted' })\n})\n\nexport default router\n```\n\n---\n\n## 六、完整流程图\n\n```\n用户               前端                     后端                    MinIO\n │                  │                        │                       │\n │  上传 ZIP         │                        │                       │\n │─────────────────>│                        │                       │\n │                  │                        │                       │\n │  输入提示词         │                        │                       │\n │─────────────────>│                        │                       │\n │                  │                        │                       │\n │  点击\"提交扫描\"      │  生成 UUID              │                       │\n │─────────────────>│  拼接 MinIO 上传指令     │                       │\n │                  │  POST /api/scan/submit │                       │\n │                  │───────────────────────>│                       │\n │                  │                        │  异步处理（10-15min）  │\n │                  │                        │───────────────────────>│\n │                  │                        │                       │\n │  显示等待界面        │  开始轮询（每10秒）       │                       │\n │<─────────────────│  statObject(uuid)      │                       │\n │                  │───────────────────────>│                       │\n │                  │                        │        NotFound        │\n │                  │<───────────────────────│                       │\n │                  │  sleep(10s)             │                       │\n │                  │  statObject(uuid)      │                       │\n │                  │───────────────────────>│                       │\n │                  │                        │        NotFound        │\n │                  │  ...（重复轮询）          │                       │\n │                  │                        │                       │\n │                  │  statObject(uuid)     │                       │\n │                  │───────────────────────>│                       │\n │                  │                        │  文件存在 ✓           │\n │                  │  getObject(uuid)       │                       │\n │                  │───────────────────────>│                       │\n │                  │<───────────────────────│  返回 MD 文件内容       │\n │                  │                        │                       │\n │  渲染 HTML 报告     │  marked(MD) → HTML     │                       │\n │<─────────────────│                        │                       │\n```\n\n---\n\n## 七、关键设计要点\n\n| 要点 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **UUID 贯穿全程** | ZIP 上传时生成 UUID → 拼入提示词 → 轮询文件名 = UUID |\n| **提示词注入** | MinIO 上传指令由前端拼接进 prompt，确保扫描服务知道文件写到哪里 |\n| **短轮询 MinIO** | 每 10s 调一次 `statObject`，文件存在即下载，避免 WebSocket 改造 |\n| **超时保护** | 15 分钟超时，前端显示实时等待时间，中途可取消 |\n| **MD → HTML** | 用 `marked`，生产环境可加 `DOMPurify` 过滤 XSS |\n| **模拟/真实切换** | `submitScanTask` 里有两段代码，注释切换即可 |\n","path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/projects/code-scanner-plugin/DESIGN.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":141,"output":3307,"cacheRead":72571,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76019,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775802656960,"responseId":"chatcmpl-6b1d306a-f020-463f-a958-7a778ec7a58a"}}
