{"type":"message","id":"f0713ff8","parentId":"8f858a82","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:42:56.605Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All done. Let me now give the user a summary of what was created and how to run it.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"搞完了 🦞 完整项目在这：\n\n```\nprojects/code-scanner-plugin/\n├── src/\n│   ├── minio.ts          # MinIO 连接（查文件/下载/上传）\n│   ├── scanService.ts    # 核心逻辑（拼提示词/提交/轮询）\n│   ├── CodeScanner.vue   # Vue 3 组件（4步状态机）\n│   ├── App.vue\n│   └── main.ts\n├── server/\n│   └── index.ts          # Express 模拟后端（60s后MinIO生成假MD）\n├── index.html\n├── vite.config.ts        # 开发代理 /api → localhost:3001\n├── tsconfig.json\n└── package.json\n```\n\n---\n\n## 怎么跑起来\n\n**终端 1 — 模拟后端：**\n```bash\ncd projects/code-scanner-plugin\nnpm install\nUSE_MOCK=true npx tsx server/index.ts\n```\n\n**终端 2 — 前端：**\n```bash\nnpm install\nnpm run dev\n# 访问 http://localhost:5173\n```\n\n---\n\n## 完整流程走一遍\n\n1. **上传 ZIP** → 生成 UUID\n2. **填提示词**（可选安全/质量/最佳实践模板）→ 末尾自动拼接 MinIO 上传指令\n3. **提交** → POST `/api/scan/submit`，后端立刻返回 202\n4. **等待界面** → 前端每 10s 轮询 `statObject(uuid)`，显示实时等待时间\n5. **60秒后**（模拟后端）→ MinIO 桶里出现 UUID 文件 → 前端下载 MD → `marked` 转 HTML → 渲染报告\n\n---\n\n**切换真实后端：** 把 `scanService.ts` 里的 `USE_MOCK` 注释掉，改掉 `BACKEND_SUBMIT_URL` 指向真实接口即可。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":176,"output":415,"cacheRead":87355,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87946,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775803362080,"responseId":"chatcmpl-23824ba4-0244-43ea-8521-ac94e3d92c51"}}
