{"type":"message","id":"80c32d66","parentId":"04acf325","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:46:11.476Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me create the AGENTS.md for the monitor agent.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gbkdbk6cw617_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Monitor Agent 配置\n\n## 模型\n- default: miaoda/miaoda-model-auto\n\n## 运行时\n- workspace: /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/agents/monitor\n- 每次启动读取 SOUL.md\n\n## 工具\n- 全工具可用\n- 重点工具：飞书消息（feishu_im_user_message）、日历（feishu_calendar_event）、Git 查询（exec + git）、文件读写、搜索\n\n## 数据来源（可配置）\n\n项目监控需要接入以下数据源，请在使用前确认：\n\n| 数据源 | 用途 | 接入方式 |\n|--------|------|---------|\n| Git 仓库 | 提交频率、分支活跃度 | exec + git 命令 |\n| CI/CD 流水线 | 构建状态、失败积压 | API（GitHub Actions / Harness / Jenkins）|\n| 飞书多维表格/任务 | 任务状态、逾期检测 | feishu_bitable_app_table_record |\n| 飞书日历 | 里程碑截止日期 | feishu_calendar_event |\n\n## 监控配置文件\n\n监控配置存储在 `projects/monitor/config.json`，首次配置后 agent 自动加载：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"project\": {\n    \"name\": \"项目名称\",\n    \"gitRepo\": \"https://github.com/org/repo\",\n    \"mainBranch\": \"main\"\n  },\n  \"thresholds\": {\n    \"noCommitHours\": 48,\n    \"ciFailureHours\": 4,\n    \"taskOverdueDays\": 2,\n    \"prReviewHours\": 24\n  },\n  \"notifyees\": {\n    \"manager\": \"ou_xxx\",\n    \"default\": \"ou_xxx\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## Cron 任务\n\n建议开启以下周期性监控：\n\n- 每 2 小时检查一次 Git 活跃度\n- 每 30 分钟检查一次 CI/CD 失败积压\n- 每天早上 9:30 发送项目健康度简报\n","path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/agents/monitor/AGENTS.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":378,"output":473,"cacheRead":88251,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89102,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775803556303,"responseId":"chatcmpl-12f8e2d1-7295-417e-aa9a-e94b4462b784"}}
