{"type":"message","id":"48dfc7dd","parentId":"c2496a9c","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:47:43.654Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me provide a summary to the user.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"搞定了 🦞 监控助手「雷达」已创建：\n\n```\nagents/monitor/\n├── SOUL.md                  ← 身份定义（推进器、督促策略、语气原则）\n├── AGENTS.md                ← 配置（接入 Git/CI-CD/飞书任务）\n└── src/\n    ├── monitorService.ts    ← 核心：停滞检测 + 健康度评分 + 消息模板\n    └── monitorAgent.ts      ← 主入口：扫描→报告→督促全流程\nprojects/monitor/\n└── config.json              ← 监控配置（阈值、通知人、调度）\n```\n\n---\n\n**它能做什么：**\n\n| 监控维度 | 停滞阈值 | 动作 |\n|---------|---------|------|\n| Git 无提交 | 默认 48h | 提醒责任人 |\n| CI/CD 失败 | 默认 4h | @reviewer |\n| 任务逾期 | 默认 2 天 | 通知经理 |\n| PR 未 review | 默认 24h | 催促 reviewer |\n| Blocker 未处理 | 默认 48h | 升级上报 |\n\n**督促三层升级：**\n```\n第1次 → 飞书提醒，说明情况\n第2次 → 10分钟后重催，说明影响\n第3次 → 30分钟后上报项目经理\n```\n\n---\n\n**用之前先改配置：**\n把 `projects/monitor/config.json` 里的 `gitRepo`、`mainBranch`、`notifyees` 换成你们实际的。\n\n然后可以直接问它：\n- \"查看当前项目状态\"\n- \"给张三分发一条督促\"\n- \"生成今天的项目健康报告\""}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":302,"output":336,"cacheRead":92283,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92921,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775803650719,"responseId":"chatcmpl-4840e60b-26e2-498e-94db-d48a79c16e86"}}
