{"type":"message","id":"fbefa38d","parentId":"96098a17","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:51:51.981Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The files exist. They're all there:\n- dev-manager\n- harness\n- ops\n- product-manager\n- qa\n\nThe user is asking about why they can't see the four Harness Engineering agents. They're probably looking at some UI that lists agents. The four Harness Engineering agents (dev-manager, product-manager, qa, ops) are in the workspace at `agents/`. But the user might be looking at an OpenClaw control panel or some other interface that doesn't show all agents, or there's a specific way to register/display agents.\n\nActually, the user said \"当前界面\" - this might refer to the OpenClaw webchat control UI (openclaw-control-ui). Perhaps there's a specific UI in the OpenClaw system where agents need to be registered or configured to appear.\n\n\nThese agents are stored in the workspace filesystem but OpenClaw might need to be configured to recognize and display them. Looking at the control UI metadata, I see there's an openclaw-control-ui sender, which could be a separate control panel interface where agents need to be explicitly configured to appear. The agents might just be files in the workspace that need to be registered with the system rather than automatically showing up in the UI.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"文件都在，没丢：\n\n```\nagents/\n├── harness/           ✅\n├── dev-manager/       ✅\n├── product-manager/    ✅\n├── qa/                 ✅\n└── ops/                ✅\n```\n\n你是在哪个界面看不到？是 OpenClaw 的控制台，还是飞书里？可能是界面只显示已激活/注册的 Agent，而不是文件系统里的所有文件。告诉我你指的是哪个界面，我帮你查。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":409,"output":333,"cacheRead":93627,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94369,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775803899313,"responseId":"chatcmpl-058350f4-849d-47cc