{"type":"message","id":"23d28a6c","parentId":"63beb8f3","timestamp":"2026-04-10T07:02:09.531Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这个在下午 14:38 已经实现过了，`projects/code-scanner-plugin/` 里全套代码都在。要不要我先检查一下当前状态，然后补充模拟 MinIO 的完整实现？代码都在，但 MinIO 现在连的是真实地址。需要加一个本地模拟 MinIO 的完整实现，这样开发调试不需要依赖外网。现在创建一个连接本地模拟服务的客户端：更新 scanService.ts 支持 mock/real 切换：更新 mock 后端，把真实 MinIO 替换成本地模拟："}],"timestamp":1775804529521,"stopReason":"stop","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"gateway-injected","idempotencyKey":"6654de84-d06d-406c-bf0a-1d3cc37c1126:assistant","openclawAbort":{"aborted":true,"origin":"rpc","runId":"6654de84-d06d-406c-bf0a-1d3cc37c1126"}}}
