{"type":"message","id":"839405b2","parentId":"3e8ad303","timestamp":"2026-04-10T07:02:09.544Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now update the mock server to upload to the local mock MinIO instead of the real one.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"更新 mock 后端，把真实 MinIO 替换成本地模拟：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_60rdyhaja9sq_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"/**\n * server/index.ts — Express 模拟后端（配合 Mock MinIO 使用）\n *\n * 作用：开发调试用，模拟真实的代码扫描服务\n *\n * 行为：\n * POST /api/scan/submit → 立即返回 202 Accepted\n * → 30秒后调用本地 Mock MinIO (localhost:9000) 生成假 MD 文件\n *\n * 使用真实 MinIO 时，替换 uploadTextFile 为真实 minio 包的调用即可\n */\n\nimport express from 'express'\nimport multer from 'multer'\nimport cors from 'cors'\nimport { v4 as uuidv4 } from 'uuid'\nimport { uploadTextFile } from '../src/mockMinioClient'   // 改为本地 Mock\n// import { uploadTextFile } from '../src/minio'          // 真实 MinIO 改用这行\n\nconst app = express()\nconst PORT = 3001\n\napp.use(cors())\napp.use(express.json())\n\nconst upload = multer({ dest: '/tmp/scan-uploads' })\n\n// ============= 模拟数据生成 =============\n\nfunction generateFakeReport(uuid: string): string {\n  return `# 🔍 代码安全扫描报告\n\n**任务 ID：** \\`${uuid}\\`\n**扫描时间：** ${new Date().toLocaleString('zh-CN', { timeZone: 'Asia/Shanghai' })}\n**扫描范围：** 全部代码文件（模拟数据）\n**项目：** 前端代码扫描插件\n\n---\n\n## 📊 扫描概要\n\n| 指标 | 数量 |\n|------|------|\n| 扫描文件总数 | 127 |\n| 代码行数 | 4,832 |\n| 高危问题 | 3 |\n| 中危问题 | 7 |\n| 低危问题 | 12 |\n| 建议优化 | 5 |\n\n---\n\n## 🚨 高危问题（必须修复）\n\n### 🔴 1. SQL 注入风险\n- **文件：** \\`src/database/query.ts\\`\n- **行号：** 23, 45, 67\n- **严重性：** 高\n- **描述：** 用户输入直接拼接到 SQL 语句中，未使用参数化查询\n- **建议：** 使用 ORM 或参数化查询\n\n\\`\\`\\`typescript\n//"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"aborted","times