{"type":"message","id":"9138d511","parentId":"9623f68b","timestamp":"2026-04-10T07:02:39.921Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to use Vue to implement this. The code scanner plugin is already built with Vue (Vue 3 + TypeScript + Vite). The user might be saying they want me to rewrite it or they want a pure Vue implementation. Let me check what's already there and then provide a cleaner, complete Vue implementation.\n\nActually, I think the user is just confirming they want it done with Vue, which it already is. But they might want me to present the complete, ready-to-run Vue project more clearly. Let me provide a clean summary of what exists and how to run it.\n\nWait, actually maybe the user wants a single-file Vue component implementation that's cleaner. Let me check the current CodeScanner.vue which is already Vue. The code I wrote before is Vue. Maybe the user just wants me to confirm it's Vue and show them how to run it.\n\n\nLooking at the existing implementation, it's already Vue 3 with the Composition API, so the project is set up correctly. The user probably just wants reassurance that it's Vue and a clear explanation of how to get it running.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"已经是 Vue 3 了 🦞 给你整理一下怎么跑起来：\n\n---\n\n**项目结构：**\n```\ncode-scanner-plugin/\n├── src/\n│   ├── mockMinioClient.ts   ← 本地模拟 MinIO（新增）\n│   ├── minio.ts              ← 真实 MinIO 客户端\n│   ├── scanService.ts        ← 核心逻辑（自动识别 mock/real）\n│   └── CodeScanner.vue       ← Vue 3 插件页面（已完整）\n├── server/\n│   ├── index.ts              ← Express 模拟后端\n│   └── mockMinio.ts          ← 本地模拟 MinIO Server（新增）\n├── package.json\n└── vite.config.ts\n```\n\n---\n\n**三步启动：**\n\n```bash\ncd /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/projects/code-scanner-plugin\nnpm install\n```\n\n**终端 1 — Mock MinIO（模拟对象存储）：**\n```bash\nnpx tsx server/mockMinio.ts\n```\n\n**终端 2 — Mock 后端（模拟扫描服务，60s 后注入 MD 文件）：**\n```bash\nnpx tsx server/index.ts\n```\n\n**终端 3 — 前端页面：**\n```bash\nnpm run dev\n# 访问 http://localhost:5173\n```\n\n---\n\n**完整流程走一遍：**\n1. 上传任意 ZIP 文件\n2. 输入提示词（或选一个快捷模板）\n3. 点击提交 → 后端 60 秒后注入 MD 文件到 Mock MinIO\n4. 前端每 5 秒轮询一次，文件出现后自动拉取 → marked 转 HTML → 渲染报告\n\n---\n\n**切换真实 MinIO：**\n把 `src/scanService.ts` 第一行改成：\n```ts\nconst USE_MOCK = false\n```\n然后把 `server/index.ts` 里的 `minioClient` 配置改成真实地址即可。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":4586,"output":611,"cacheRead":105275,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":110472,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775804529909,"responseId":"chatcmpl-8031296b-0040-4dad-a097-b2a6d0ec0478"}}
