n✗ Build failed in 589ms\nerror during build:\n[vite]: Rollup failed to resolve import \"minio\" from \"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/projects/code-scanner-plugin/src/minio.ts\".\nThis is most likely unintended because it can break your application at runtime.\nIf you do want to externalize this module explicitly add it to\n`build.rollupOptions.external`\n    at viteLog (file:///home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/projects/code-scanner-plugin/node_modules/vite/dist/node/chunks/dep-Dq2t6Dq0.js:46399:15)\n    at onRollupLog (file:///home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/projects/code-scanner-plugin/node_modules/vite/dist/node/chunks/dep-Dq2t6Dq0.js:46449:5)\n    at onLog (file:///home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/projects/code-scanner-plugin/node_modules/vite/dist/node/chunks/dep-Dq2t6Dq0.js:46097:7)\n    at file:///home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/projects/code-scanner-plugin/node_modules/rollup/dist/es/shared/node-entry.js:21369:32\n    at Object.logger [as onLog] (file:///home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/projects/code-scanner-plugin/node_modules/rollup/dist/es/shared/node-entry.js:23364:9)\n    at ModuleLoader.handleInvalidResolvedId (file:///home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/projects/code-scanner-plugin/node_modules/rollup/dist/es/shared/node-entry.js:22108:26)\n    at file:///home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/projects/code-scanner-plugin/node_modules/rollup/dist/es/shared/node-entry.js:22066:26","cwd":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775804774464}}
{"type":"message","id":"a6888d16","parentId":"b8410cdb","timestamp":"2026-04-10T07:06:35.127Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The build fails because `minio.ts` is imported in `scanService.ts` but `minio` package is not installed. In mock mode, we're using `mockMinioClient` instead. The issue is that `scanService.ts` imports both `mockMinioClient` and `minio`, but `minio` package isn't installed.\n\nThe solution: in `scanService.ts`, when `USE_MOCK = true`, we should NOT import from `minio` at all. I need to restructure the imports so that the real minio is only imported when `USE_MOCK = false`.\n\nLet me fix `scanService.ts` to conditionally import.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"`scanService.ts` 在 mock 模式下也尝试导入 `minio`（未安装），需要条件导入：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_n8zeksd47hz6_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"/**\n * scanService.ts — 核心业务逻辑\n * 流程：提交任务 → 轮询 MinIO → 返回 MD 内容\n */\n\nimport axios from 'axios'\nimport { v4 as uuidv4 } from 'uuid'\n\n// ============= 模式切换 =============\nconst USE_MOCK = true  // ← 改 false 使用真实 MinIO\n\n// 动态导入，避免未安装 minio 时 build 报错\nasync function getMinioClient() {\n  if (USE_MOCK) {\n    const m = await import('./mockMinioClient')\n    return { fileExists: m.fileExists, downloadTextFile: m.downloadTextFile }\n  } else {\n    const m = await import('./minio')\n    return { fileExists: m.fileExists, downloadTextFile: m.downloadTextFile }\n  }\n}\n\n// ============= 配置 =============\nconst BACKEND_SUBMIT_URL = USE_MOCK\n  ? 'http://localhost:3001/api/scan/submit'\n  : '/api/scan/submit'\n\nconst POLL_INTERVAL_MS = USE_MOCK ? 5_000 : 10_000\nconst MAX_WAIT_MS = USE_MOCK ? 5 * 60 * 1000 : 15 * 60 * 1000\n// ==================================\n\nlet _canceled = false\n\n// ============= 导出函数 =============\n\nexport function generateUUID(): string {\n  return uuidv4()\n}\n\nexport function buildPromptWithUploadInstruction(\n  originalPrompt: string,\n  _uuid: string\n): string {\n  if (USE_MOCK) {\n    return `${originalPrompt}\\n\\n请生成一份中文 Markdown 格式的代码扫描报告。`\n  }\n  return `${originalPrompt}\n\n请将生成的代码扫描报告文件上传到 MinIO 对象存储：\n- MinIO 地址：10.28.198.153:9010\n- 用户名：admin\n- 密码：A12345678\n- 存储桶：code-scanning\n- 文件名：${_uuid}\n（请直接上传原始 Markdown 文件，不要压缩）`\n}\n\nexport async function submitScanTask(\n  zipFile: File,\n  enrichedPrompt: string,\n  uuid: string\n): Promise<{ uuid: string }> {\n  const formData = new FormData()\n  formData.append('file', zipFile)\n  formData.append('prompt', enrichedPrompt)\n  formData.append('uuid', uuid)\n\n  const response = await axios.post(BACKEND_SUBMIT_URL, formData, {\n    headers: { 'Content-Type': 'multipart/form-data' },\n    timeout: 30_000,\n  })\n  return response.data\n}\n\nexport async function waitForResult(\n  uuid: string,\n  onProgress?: (elapsedMs: number) => void,\n  onTick?: () => void\n): Promise<string> {\n  _canceled = false\n  const startTime = Date.now()\n  const deadline = startTime + MAX_WAIT_MS\n  const { fileExists, downloadTextFile } = await getMinioClient()\n\n  while (!_canceled && Date.now() < deadline) {\n    const elapsed = Date.now() - startTime\n    onProgress?.(elapsed)\n\n    try {\n      const exists = await fileExists(uuid)\n      if (exists) {\n        const content = await downloadTextFile(uuid)\n        return content\n      }\n    } catch (err) {\n      console.warn(`[waitForResult] 轮询出错:`, err)\n    }\n\n    onTick?.()\n    await sleep(POLL_INTERVAL_MS)\n  }\n\n  if (_canceled) throw new Error('用户取消了扫描')\n  throw new Error(`扫描超时（等待超过 ${MAX_WAIT_MS / 1000} 秒）`)\n}\n\nexport function cancelWait(): void {\n  _canceled = true\n}\n\nexport function resetCancel(): void {\n  _canceled = false\n}\n\nfunction sleep(ms: number): Promise<void> {\n  return new Promise((resolve) => setTimeout(resolve, ms))\n}\n","path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/projects/code-scanner-plugin/src/scanService.ts"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":879,"output":1041,"cacheRead":116027,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":117947,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775804774473,"responseId":"chatcmpl-6f1348d3-e392-4a24-9720-436ad8015c55"}}
