{"type":"message","id":"da1ca388","parentId":"a75a3f38","timestamp":"2026-04-10T07:06:49.125Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The error says it's resolving `minio` from `minio.ts` which still has the `import * as Minio from 'minio'` at the top. Even though I use dynamic import in `scanService.ts`, the file `minio.ts` itself still has a top-level import of the `minio` package. \n\nThe problem is that Rollup statically analyzes all imports, even dynamic ones. Since `minio.ts` file contains `import * as Minio from 'minio'`, Rollup tries to resolve it.\n\nThe solution is either:\n1. Delete or rename `minio.ts` since we're in mock mode","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"`minio.ts` 本身有顶层 `import 'minio'`，Rollup 会静态扫描到它。最简单的办法——在 mock 模式下删掉它：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kt2osdnislgh_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mv /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/projects/code-scanner-plugin/src/minio.ts \\\n   /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/projects/code-scanner-plugin/src/minio.ts.bak && echo \"backed up\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":641,"output":241,"cacheRead":117819,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118701,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775804800354,"responseId":"chatcmpl-d7a221f3-cc2d-4484-bade-750b7d54e568"}}
