{"type":"message","id":"6ff2e513","parentId":"f62a6c4b","timestamp":"2026-04-10T07:26:19.189Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No GitHub credentials found. I need to ask the user for a GitHub Personal Access Token (PAT) to push to the repository. This is standard for headless git operations.\n\nThe repository URL would be: https://github.com/962996947/yaxin.git\n\nBut to push, we need authentication. I should ask the user for a GitHub PAT (Personal Access Token). GitHub no longer supports password authentication for git push.\n\nLet me ask for the token.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"仓库 URL 是 `https://github.com/962996947/yaxin.git`，但推送需要 GitHub 认证。\n\nGitHub 自 2021 年起不再支持密码登录，需要用 **Personal Access Token (PAT)**。\n\n**请提供你的 GitHub Personal Access Token**，我用来配置认证后推送。\n\n获取方式：\n1. 登录 GitHub → Settings → Developer settings → Personal access tokens → Tokens (classic)\n2. Generate new token (classic)\n3. 勾选 `repo` 权限（完整仓库访问）\n4. 复制 token 给我\n\nToken 格式类似：`ghp_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx`"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":331,"output":231,"cacheRead":130363,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":130925,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775805969236,"responseId":"chatcmpl-f5aa25ed-69d9-4c9d-bde0-47b6e01b549d"}}
