{"type":"message","id":"918dffc1","parentId":"0b343bff","timestamp":"2026-04-10T07:31:49.323Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user has provided their GitHub Personal Access Token. I need to:\n1. Configure git remote with the token embedded in the URL\n2. Configure git credentials to store the token\n3. Add only the relevant project files (not sensitive openclaw config/sessions)\n4. Commit and push\n\nImportant: I must NOT expose the token in my reply. I'll configure it securely.\n\nThe repo URL will be: https://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@github.com/962996947/yaxin.git\n\nOr I can use git credential store to store the credentials.\n\n\nNow I'm realizing the workspace contains sensitive configuration files like openclaw.json and session logs that shouldn't be committed. I'll configure the remote URL with the token, set up git to ignore those sensitive files, stage only the project files, commit with a descriptive message, and push to the repository.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"配置认证并只提交项目文件（排除敏感配置）：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_aaglql7hs6qa_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 1. 配置远程仓库（token 嵌入 URL）\ncd /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace\ngit remote add origin https://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@github.com/962996947/yaxin.git 2>/dev/null || \\\ngit remote set-url origin https://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@github.com/962996947/yaxin.git\n\n# 2. 配置credential为store（避免每次都要输入）\ngit config --global credential.helper store\n\n# 3. 先写一次凭证\necho \"https://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@github.com\" > ~/.git-credentials\n\ngit remote -v"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":130749,"output":429,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":131178,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775806284926,"responseId