{"type":"message","id":"8800f135","parentId":"abb448c8","timestamp":"2026-04-10T07:32:02.920Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to set up .gitignore to exclude sensitive files, then add and commit only project files, then push. Let me check what's in the workspace that should be committed vs what should be ignored.\n\nThe workspace contains:\n- agents/ - Harness Agent definitions (SOUL.md, AGENTS.md) - should commit\n- projects/ - project code (code-scanner-plugin, harness-dev-loop) - should commit\n- HARNESS_ENGINEERING.md, HARNESS_IO.md - documentation - should commit\n- memory/, MEMORY.md - session logs and memory - should NOT commit (personal/session-specific)\n- BOOTSTRAP.md, SOUL.md, IDENTITY.md, USER.md, AGENTS.md, TOOLS.md, HEARTBEAT.md - workspace config - some personal\n\n\n- openclaw.json and session files need to be excluded since they contain sensitive configuration data.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8o1t9rjmosyz_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace\n\n# 创建 .gitignore，排除敏感文件\ncat > .gitignore << 'EOF'\n# 系统隐藏文件\n.DS_Store\nThumbs.db\n\n# OpenClaw 运行时敏感文件\nopenclaw.json\nopenclaw.json.bak\nidentity/\nmemory/\n\n# Agent 会话日志\nagents/main/sessions/\nagents/harness/sessions/\nagents/dev-manager/sessions/\nagents/product-manager/sessions/\nagents/qa/sessions/\nagents/ops/sessions/\n\n# 临时文件\n*.log\n*.tmp\n*.bak\n.env\n.env.*\n\n# 依赖\nnode_modules/\ndist/\n\n# 模拟开发文件（非真实场景）\n**/node_modules/\n**/*.log\nEOF\n\necho \"✅ .gitignore 已创建\"\ncat .gitignore"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":472,"output":376,"cacheRead":130811,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":131659,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775806309366,"responseId":"chatcmpl-2d9eb7d0-56f4-43c9-9304-2f21ac13c