个能连 github.com 的代理**\n\n如果你的 agent 部署环境有代理，把代理地址给我，加上这段环境变量就能 push：\n\n```bash\nexport https_proxy=http://你的代理地址:端口\ngit push origin HEAD:main\n```\n\n你有哪种条件？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":613,"output":483,"cacheRead":144699,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":145795,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775806749668,"responseId":"chatcmpl-63262854-e534-4f88-902e-a0ae2c32c7ae"}}
