{"type":"message","id":"98dbd34f","parentId":"fb967f31","timestamp":"2026-04-10T07:50:24.192Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The `gh` CLI version is 2.8.9 and has a bug. This is a known issue with older versions. Let me try a different approach.\n\nSince HTTPS connectivity works (verified with curl), and the issue is that `git push` is timing out, let me try using git with verbose output and a longer timeout.\n\nActually, let me think about this differently. The curl to github.com worked - TLS handshake was successful. The `git push` is hanging. This might be because git needs to negotiate the git protocol (git-upload-pack/git-receive-pack) which might be getting blocked, even though the HTTPS port itself is accessible.\n\nLet me try a different approach: use git with SSH protocol if possible. \n\nWait, port 22 is actually open, so I could switch to SSH instead of HTTPS. Let me configure the remote to use SSH.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"HTTPS 能连通但 git 协议卡住。试试 SSH 方式：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zc7nxw9dmp02_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/gem/workspace/agent\n\n# 检查是否有 SSH 密钥\nls ~/.ssh/ 2>/dev/null || echo \"无SSH密钥\"\n# 生成 ED25519 密钥对（快速）\nssh-keygen -t ed25519 -C \"yaxin-agent@feishu\" -f /tmp/yaxin_push_key -N \"\" -q 2>&1\necho \"---\"\ncat /tmp/yaxin_push_key.pub","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":577,"output":323,"cacheRead":149179,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":150079,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775807410955,"responseId":"chatcmpl-648a8017-fd4b-4156-a219-20d86dd71e7b"}}
