{"type":"message","id":"3180e188","parentId":"1adf507c","timestamp":"2026-04-10T08:23:39.119Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now update the Mock server to make it more realistic - the backend should not directly call uploadTextFile (which uploads to the mock MinIO), but should simulate \"LLM generates report and uploads to MinIO\" by waiting for a while and then injecting the file to the mock MinIO.\n\nActually, the current mock server does this correctly - it waits 60s then uploads to the mock MinIO (which in turn is accessible via the mockMinioClient at localhost:9000).\n\nBut the key issue is that `USE_MOCK` in scanService.ts also controls whether to use real or mock MinIO. When `USE_MOCK=true`, the frontend polls the mock MinIO (localhost:9000), not the real MinIO. This is correct for development.\n \nI need to reconsider the architecture here - the real flow has the LLM processing the uploaded ZIP and prompt, then uploading the report to the real MinIO at 10.28.198.153:9010, while the mock setup has the backend waiting 60 seconds before uploading to a local mock MinIO instance at localhost:9000 instead.\n\nThe issue is that `mockMinioClient.ts` is hardcoded to always connect to localhost:9000, even though in production it should point to the actual MinIO server, and the `uploadTextFile` function in `mockMinioClient.ts` is only used by the mock server itself, not by the frontend's actual upload logic.\n\nLooking at the flow more carefully: the frontend submits with the enriched prompt containing the MinIO upload instructions, the mock backend receives this and simulates the LLM by waiting 60 seconds before uploading the report directly to the mock MinIO via `uploadTextFile`. The frontend then polls the mock MinIO to check if the file exists and downloads it when ready.\n\nI need to fix the scanService.ts file by removing the USE_MOCK branches for `buildPromptWithUploadInstruction`, and then verify that the `fileExists` logic in mockMinioClient.ts correctly handles the case where the mock server should return 200 when the file is present.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在修正 Mock Server，使其更真实地模拟\"大模型按追加指令上传到 MinIO\"的过程，并调整轮询间隔：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_aucgu4gwivig_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/projects/code-scanner-plugin/server/index.ts","newText":"/**\n * server/index.ts — Express 模拟后端\n *\n * 作用：开发调试用，模拟真实代码扫描服务\n * 模拟场景：收到 ZIP + 提示词（末尾已追加 MinIO 上传指令），\n *           假装是大模型在处理，约 60s 后\"按照提示词指令\"上传报告到 MinIO\n *\n * 行为：POST /api/scan/submit → 立即返回 202，\n *       60秒后模拟\"大模型\"上传 MD 报告文件到 Mock MinIO（localhost:9000）\n */","oldText":"/**\n * server/index.ts — Express 模拟后端\n *\n * 作用：开发调试用，模拟真实代码扫描服务\n * 行为：POST /api/scan/submit → 立即返回 202，\n *        60秒后在本地 Mock MinIO（localhost:9000）注入 MD 报告文件\n */"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":1705,"output":709,"cacheRead":70331,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72745,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775809389144,"responseId":"chatcmpl-169e410e-834d-4d69-8fee-fe6260409039"}}
