{"type":"message","id":"314395bc","parentId":"92ef22b8","timestamp":"2026-04-10T08:24:06.668Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me also verify the overall flow one more time to make sure everything is correct.\n\nThe key changes made:\n1. `buildPromptWithUploadInstruction` now always includes the MinIO upload instruction (removed the USE_MOCK shortcut that omitted it)\n\nLet me summarize the complete flow for the user.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## ✅ 修正完成，完整流程确认\n\n```\n用户上传 ZIP + 提示词\n        ↓\n  submitScan()\n        ↓\n  buildPromptWithUploadInstruction()  ← 提示词末尾自动追加：\n  ┌────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n  │ 请将生成的代码扫描报告文件上传到 MinIO 对象存储：  │\n  │ - MinIO 地址：10.28.198.153:9010           │\n  │ - 用户名：admin                            │\n  │ - 密码：A12345678                         │\n  │ - 存储桶：code-scanning                   │\n  │ - 文件名：${UUID}                          │\n  └────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n        ↓\n  POST /api/scan/submit (202 立即返回)\n        ↓\n  waitForResult() 轮询\n        ↓\n  fileExists(uuid)  ←  GET /{uuid} → HTTP 200 = 文件存在\n        ↓\n  downloadTextFile(uuid)\n        ↓\n  marked(MD) → HTML\n        ↓\n  页面展示 + 下载按钮\n```\n\n**两处修改：**\n1. `src/scanService.ts` — `buildPromptWithUploadInstruction` 始终追加 MinIO 上传指令，移除了 Mock 模式省略此步骤的 shortcut\n2. `server/index.ts` — 注释更新，说明模拟的是\"大模型按追加指令上传\"的过程\n\nMock 模式 5 秒轮询（开发调试），切 `USE_MOCK=false` 后自动切换为真实 MinIO + 10 秒轮询。需要我提交到 GitHub 吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":232,"output":402,"cacheRead":73019,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73653,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775809433707,"responseId":"chatcmpl-bccd0b49-f04c-4a6f-b962-f5a1ef29fe0d"}}
