{"type":"message","id":"d40e99e7","parentId":"f219e979","timestamp":"2026-04-10T08:39:23.897Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_4obbh79vevdf_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"| 指标 | 数量 |\n|------|------|\n| 扫描文件总数 | 42 |\n| 高危问题 | 3 |\n| 中危问题 | 7 |\n| 低危问题 | 12 |\n\n---\n\n## 🚨 高危问题\n\n### 1. SQL 注入风险\n- **文件：** \\`src/database/query.ts:23\\`\n- **描述：** 用户输入直接拼接到 SQL 语句\n\n### 2. 硬编码密钥\n- **文件：** \\`src/config/secrets.ts:5\\`\n\n---\n\n*此为 Mock 数据，用于开发调试*\n`\n    const filePath = getObjectPath(mockUuid)\n    fs.writeFileSync(filePath, Buffer.from(fakeReport, 'utf-8'))\n    res.writeHead(200, { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' })\n    res.end(JSON.stringify({ uuid: mockUuid, seeded: true, path: filePath }))\n    return\n  }\n\n  // DELETE /mock/clear — 清空所有模拟文件\n  if (pathname === '/mock/clear' && req.method === 'DELETE') {\n    const files = fs.readdirSync(DATA_DIR)\n    for (const f of files) {\n      fs.unlinkSync(path.join(DATA_DIR, f))\n    }\n    res.writeHead(200, { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' })\n    res.end(JSON.stringify({ cleared: files.length }))\n    return\n  }\n\n  // 列出所有模拟文件\n  if (pathname === '/mock/list' && req.method === 'GET') {\n    const files = fs.readdirSync(DATA_DIR).map((f) => {\n      const stat = fs.statSync(path.join(DATA_DIR, f))\n      return { name: f, size: stat.size, modified: stat.mtime.toISOString() }\n    })\n    res.writeHead(200, { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' })\n    res.end(JSON.stringify({ files, count: files.length }))\n    return\n  }\n\n  res.writeHead(200)\n  res.end(`Mock MinIO Server (port ${PORT})\n存储目录: ${DATA_DIR}\n\n可用接口:\n  HEAD/GET/PUT  /{objectName}     — MinIO 风格对象操作\n  GET           /health            — 健康检查\n  POST          /mock/seed?uuid=xxx — 注入假 MD 文件\n  GET           /mock/list          — 列出所有模拟文件\n  DELETE        /mock/clear         — 清空所有模拟文件\n`)\n})\n\n// ============= 启动 =============\n\nserver.listen(PORT, () => {\n  console.log(`\\n🔧 Mock MinIO Server 已启动 (端口 ${PORT})`)\n  console.log(`   模拟桶: ${BUCKET}`)\n  console.log(`   存储目录: ${DATA_DIR}`)\n  console.log(`   对象操作: http://localhost:${PORT}/{objectName}`)\n  console.log(`   状态页:   http://localhost:${PORT}/\\n`)\n})\n\nextraServer.listen(PORT + 1, () => {\n  console.log(`   控制面板: http://localhost:${PORT + 1}/mock/`)\n})\n\n// 优雅退出\nprocess.on('SIGINT', () => {\n\n[6 more lines in file. Use offset=300 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775810363893}}
{"type":"message","id":"4a0d4b81","parentId":"d40e99e7","timestamp":"2026-04-10T08:39:40.769Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me update the extraServer's `/mock/seed` endpoint to use the shared `handleSeed` function, and update the test to use the 9000 seed endpoint. Actually, since handleSeed is now defined at the top level, the extraServer can also use it. But actually the extraServer is on port 9001 and the test needs port 9000's GET /{uuid} to work. Let me just update the test to call port 9000's /seed endpoint.\n\nActually, the current extraServer (9001) still has its own seed handler with the same fakeReport content. \n\nI'll leave that as is and just update the test to call port 9000's seed instead. Let me restart the mockMinio server and then run the test again.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"重启 Mock MinIO 服务以加载新代码：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wkrkjjff95jh_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"pkill -f \"tsx server/mockMinio\" 2>/dev/null; sleep 1; echo \"killed\"","timeout":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":789,"output":234,"cacheRead":90043,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91066,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775810363901,"responseId":"chatcmpl-3149668a-58ec-49e6-9e87-238e1fa34dcb"}}
