{"type":"message","id":"ac613569","parentId":"c65d4019","timestamp":"2026-04-10T08:41:29.445Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Also, I need to verify the seed works by checking that GET on port 9000 finds the file. Let me also add a quick check after seeding. Also, I need to restart the mockMinio server first before running the test.\n\nLet me also update the waitForResult polling test - the issue was that the seed was on 9001 but polling was on 9000. Now with seed on 9000, it should work. But the wait interval is 5 seconds. After seeding, the next poll should find the file (5s later).\n\nLet me also add a check that the seeded file is accessible from port 9000 immediately after seeding.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ra1o3ucweyeq_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"filePath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/projects/code-scanner-plugin/e2e-test.mjs","newString":"  // 用 mockMinio 的 seed 接口在端口 9000 注入 MD 文件（同一 DATA_DIR，GET 轮询可读）\n  const seedRes = await fetch(`http://localhost:9000/seed?uuid=${encodeURIComponent(uuid)}`)\n  const seedData = await seedRes.json()\n  info(`Mock MinIO seed 响应: ${JSON.stringify(seedData)}`)\n\n  // 验证文件立即可读（同一端口 9000）\n  const verifyRes = await fetch(`http://localhost:9000/${encodeURIComponent(uuid)}`)\n  if (!verifyRes.ok) throw new Error(`seed 后文件在 9000 仍不可读: ${verifyRes.status}`)\n  const verifyText = await verifyRes.text()\n  if (!verifyText.includes('代码扫描报告')) throw new Error(`seed 文件内容异常: ${verifyText.slice(0, 50)}`)\n  pass(`seed 文件已注入，9000 GET 可读 (${verifyText.length} 字节)`)","oldText":"  // 从页面提取 UUID\n  const uuidText = await page.locator('.status-value.uuid').textContent().catch(() => '')\n  const uuid = uuidText.trim()\n  if (!uuid) throw new Error('无法获取 UUID')\n\n  // 用 mockMinio 的 seed 接口在端口 9000 注入 MD 文件（同一 DATA_DIR，GET 轮询可读）\n  const seedRes = await fetch(`http://localhost:9000/seed?uuid=${encodeURIComponent(