{"type":"message","id":"464ce0ff","parentId":"2c5a706d","timestamp":"2026-04-10T08:57:30.226Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found it! The error is:\n\n```\nReferenceError: Buffer is not defined\n    at downloadTextFile (http://localhost:5174/src/mockMinioClient.ts:27:3)\n```\n\n`Buffer` is a Node.js API, not available in browsers! The `downloadTextFile` function in `mockMinioClient.ts` uses `Buffer.from(ab).toString('utf-8')`, but in the browser environment, `Buffer` is not defined.\n\nI need to fix `downloadTextFile` to use `TextDecoder` instead of `Buffer` for browser compatibility.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了！**根因：`Buffer` 是 Node.js API，浏览器中没有**。修复 `downloadTextFile`：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_o9acu6horlbz_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '26,35p' /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/projects/code-scanner-plugin/src/mockMinioClient.ts","timeout":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":1008,"output":209,"cacheRead":119163,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":120380,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775811442513,"responseId":"chatcmpl-b3babb73-a947-401f-b9b0-e260baf3eb38"}}
