{"type":"message","id":"76f21d1d","parentId":"e755da0d","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:00:54.627Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The push was successful. All 20 files are now in the GitHub repository.\n\nLet me also note the key fix that was pushed:\n- `mockMinioClient.ts` - Buffer replaced with TextDecoder/TextEncoder/Uint8Array for browser compatibility\n- `server/mockMinio.ts` - Added `/seed?uuid=` endpoint on port 9000\n- `server/index.ts` - Updated comments\n- `scanService.ts` - MinIO upload instruction always appended\n- Plus E2E test files","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"已推送 ✅\n\n**commit**: `7c6563b5f93f464d1bf8a8b7433907771181d9ad`\n**仓库**: https://github.com/wangyang962996947/yaxins\n**文件**: 20 个\n\n本次推送内容：\n- **`src/mockMinioClient.ts`** — `Buffer` → `TextDecoder`/`TextEncoder`/`Uint8Array`（浏览器兼容）\n- **`server/mockMinio.ts`** — 新增 `GET /seed?uuid=` 端点\n- **`src/scanService.ts`** — 提示词始终追加 MinIO 上传指令\n- **`server/index.ts`** — 注释更新\n- **`e2e-test.mjs`** — Playwright 全链路测试脚本\n- **`pw-debug.mjs` / `pw-log-debug.mjs`** — 调试脚本"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":364,"output":293,"cacheRead":113339,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":113996,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775811646083,"responseId":"chatcmpl-adf27cde-633e-4231-86e7-cf63809ef9d2"}}
