{"type":"message","id":"d3b6f291","parentId":"82df953a","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:26:45.915Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to remove the mock services (mockMinio.ts and server/index.ts) and instead simulate the requests locally (in-browser). Let me plan the changes:\n\n1. Remove `server/` directory (mockMinio.ts and index.ts)\n2. Remove `USE_MOCK` flag from `scanService.ts`\n3. Simulate the backend and MinIO behavior entirely in the browser\n4. The simulation should:\n   - `submitScanTask`: Return immediately with 202, then after ~5-10 seconds, \"create\" the MD file (store in memory or localStorage)\n   - `fileExists`: Check if the simulated file exists in memory\n   - `downloadTextFile`: Return the simulated MD content from memory\n5. Update the frontend code to handle everything locally\n6. Update README.md\n7. Remove the mock-server and mock-minio npm scripts\n\nLet me design the local simulation:\n\nFor the \"backend simulation\":\n- Store a Map of uuid → {content, ready, timeout} in memory\n- `submitScanTask`: Generate the fake MD report, store it, return 202 immediately\n- After a delay (e.g., 5-8 seconds), mark the file as \"ready\"\n- `waitForResult` polls `fileExists` which checks the in-memory Map\n\nFor the \"MinIO simulation\":\n- In-memory Map: `uuid → mdContent`\n- `fileExists(uuid)`: checks if uuid is in the map\n- `downloadTextFile(uuid)`: returns the content\n\nSo essentially, the simulation merges both the backend and MinIO into one in-browser simulation:\n1. `submitScanTask` generates a fake MD report and stores it in a module-level Map\n2. After a random delay (5-10s), marks it as \"ready\"\n3. `fileExists` checks the Map\n4. `downloadTextFile` retrieves from the Map\n\nThis means I can remove the server directory entirely, delete the mock-related npm scripts, and simplify scanService.ts to just use this in-browser simulation.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好，移除 mock 服务，改成纯浏览器端本地模拟。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pnra2s6npj36_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/projects/code-scanning-plugin/src/\necho \"\"\nls /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/projects/code-scanner-plugin/server/","timeout":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":116082,"output":510,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116592,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775813182389,"responseId":"chatcmpl-8d43d93d-b8a8-4db4-bb99-7c7e9c6eb0d4"}}
