{"type":"message","id":"ce919a25","parentId":"e9728133","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:27:06.378Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me plan the changes:\n\n1. **Remove `server/` directory** - delete both files\n2. **Create `src/simulator.ts`** - in-browser simulation of backend + MinIO\n3. **Rewrite `src/scanService.ts`** - remove USE_MOCK, use simulator\n4. **Update `src/mockMinioClient.ts`** - maybe keep for reference or remove\n5. **Update `package.json`** - remove mock-server/mock-minio scripts, remove server deps\n6. **Update `README.md`**\n\nThe simulator approach:\n- Module-level Map: `uuid → { content: string, ready: boolean, timeoutId?: number }`\n\n\n- `submitScanTask` generates a fake MD report and stores it in the Map, then sets a timeout to mark it ready after 5-8 seconds\n- `fileExists` and `downloadTextFile` check and retrieve from the Map\n- When `waitForResult` polls, it sees the file is ready and returns the content\n\nI'll consolidate everything into a single `src/simulator.ts` file.\n\nFor the package.json dependencies, I need to remove the backend packages like express, multer, cors, and uuid since we're doing in-browser simulation now, but keep axios, marked, and vue. The mockMinioClient.ts becomes unnecessary, though I should keep minio.ts for when we connect to the real backend later.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"先读当前关键文件，然后统一修改：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_74w957h4r3lz_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/projects/code-scanner-plugin/src/scanService.ts","timeout":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":835,"output":359,"cacheRead":116475,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":117669,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775813213759,"responseId":"chatcmpl-a50c2f12-4c44-43c4-bd8e-d562e9ef29fa"}}
{"type":"message","id":"db10740c","parentId":"ce919a25","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:27:06.421Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_74w957h4r3lz_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/**\n * scanService.ts — 核心业务逻辑\n * 流程：提交任务 → 轮询 MinIO → 返回 MD 内容\n */\n\nimport axios from 'axios'\nimport { v4 as uuidv4 } from 'uuid'\n\n// ============= 模式切换 =============\nconst USE_MOCK = true  // ← 改 false 使用真实 MinIO\n\n// 动态导入，避免未安装 minio 时 build 报错\nasync function getMinioClient() {\n  if (USE_MOCK) {\n    const m = await import('./mockMinioClient')\n    return { fileExists: m.fileExists, downloadTextFile: m.downloadTextFile }\n  } else {\n    const m = await import('./minio')\n    return { fileExists: m.fileExists, downloadTextFile: m.downloadTextFile }\n  }\n}\n\n// ============= 配置 =============\nconst BACKEND_SUBMIT_URL = USE_MOCK\n  ? 'http://localhost:3001/api/scan/submit'\n  : '/api/scan/submit'\n\nconst POLL_INTERVAL_MS = USE_MOCK ? 5_000 : 10_000\nconst MAX_WAIT_MS = USE_MOCK ? 5 * 60 * 1000 : 15 * 60 * 1000\n// ==================================\n\nlet _canceled = false\n\n// ============= 导出函数 =============\n\nexport function generateUUID(): string {\n  return uuidv4()\n}\n\nexport function buildPromptWithUploadInstruction(\n  originalPrompt: string,\n  uuid: string\n): string {\n  // 追加 MinIO 上传指令，模拟后端大模型在生成报告后自动上传到 MinIO\n  return `${originalPrompt}\n\n请将生成的代码扫描报告文件上传到 MinIO 对象存储：\n- MinIO 地址：10.28.198.153:9010\n- 用户名：admin\n- 密码：A12345678\n- 存储桶：code-scanning\n- 文件名：${uuid}\n（请直接上传原始 Markdown 文件，不要压缩）`\n}\n\nexport async function submitScanTask(\n  zipFile: File,\n  enrichedPrompt: string,\n  uuid: string\n): Promise<{ uuid: string }> {\n  const formData = new FormData()\n  formData.append('file', zipFile)\n  formData.append('prompt', enrichedPrompt)\n  formData.append('uuid', uuid)\n\n  const response = await axios.post(BACKEND_SUBMIT_URL, formData, {\n    headers: { 'Content-Type': 'multipart/form-data' },\n    timeout: 30_000,\n  })\n  return response.data\n}\n\nexport async function waitForResult(\n  uuid: string,\n  onProgress?: (elapsedMs: number) => void,\n  onTick?: () => void\n): Promise<string> {\n  _canceled = false\n  const startTime = Date.now()\n  const deadline = startTime + MAX_WAIT_MS\n  const { fileExists, downloadTextFile } = await getMinioClient()\n\n  while (!_canceled && Date.now() < deadline) {\n    const elapsed = Date.now() - startTime\n    onProgress?.(elapsed)\n\n    try {\n      const exists = await fileExists(uuid)\n      if (exists) {\n        const content = await downloadTextFile(uuid)\n        return content\n      }\n    } catch (err) {\n      console.warn(`[waitForResult] 轮询出错:`, err)\n    }\n\n    onTick?.()\n    await sleep(POLL_INTERVAL_MS)\n  }\n\n  if (_canceled) throw new Error('用户取消了扫描')\n  throw new Error(`扫描超时（等待超过 ${MAX_WAIT_MS / 1000} 秒）`)\n}\n\nexport function cancelWait(): void {\n  _canceled = true\n}\n\nexport function resetCancel(): void {\n  _canceled = false\n}\n\nfunction sleep(ms: number): Promise<void> {\n  return new Promise((resolve) => setTimeout(resolve, ms))\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":14,"aggregated":"/**\n * scanService.ts — 核心业务逻辑\n * 流程：提交任务 → 轮询 MinIO → 返回 MD 内容\n */\n\nimport axios from 'axios'\nimport { v4 as uuidv4 } from 'uuid'\n\n// ============= 模式切换 =============\nconst USE_MOCK = true  // ← 改 false 使用真实 MinIO\n\n// 动态导入，避免未安装 minio 时 build 报错\nasync function getMinioClient() {\n  if (USE_MOCK) {\n    const m = await import('./mockMinioClient')\n    return { fileExists: m.fileExists, downloadTextFile: m.downloadTextFile }\n  } else {\n    const m = await import('./minio')\n    return { fileExists: m.fileExists, downloadTextFile: m.downloadTextFile }\n  }\n}\n\n// ============= 配置 =============\nconst BACKEND_SUBMIT_URL = USE_MOCK\n  ? 'http://localhost:3001/api/scan/submit'\n  : '/api/scan/submit'\n\nconst POLL_INTERVAL_MS = USE_MOCK ? 5_000 : 10_000\nconst MAX_WAIT_MS = USE_MOCK ? 5 * 60 * 1000 : 15 * 60 * 1000\n// ==================================\n\nlet _canceled = false\n\n// ============= 导出函数 =============\n\nexport function generateUUID(): string {\n  return uuidv4()\n}\n\nexport function buildPromptWithUploadInstruction(\n  originalPrompt: string,\n  uuid: string\n): string {\n  // 追加 MinIO 上传指令，模拟后端大模型在生成报告后自动上传到 MinIO\n  return `${originalPrompt}\n\n请将生成的代码扫描报告文件上传到 MinIO 对象存储：\n- MinIO 地址：10.28.198.153:9010\n- 用户名：admin\n- 密码：A12345678\n- 存储桶：code-scanning\n- 文件名：${uuid}\n（请直接上传原始 Markdown 文件，不要压缩）`\n}\n\nexport async function submitScanTask(\n  zipFile: File,\n  enrichedPrompt: string,\n  uuid: string\n): Promise<{ uuid: string }> {\n  const formData = new FormData()\n  formData.append('file', zipFile)\n  formData.append('prompt', enrichedPrompt)\n  formData.append('uuid', uuid)\n\n  const response = await axios.post(BACKEND_SUBMIT_URL, formData, {\n    headers: { 'Content-Type': 'multipart/form-data' },\n    timeout: 30_000,\n  })\n  return response.data\n}\n\nexport async function waitForResult(\n  uuid: string,\n  onProgress?: (elapsedMs: number) => void,\n  onTick?: () => void\n): Promise<string> {\n  _canceled = false\n  const startTime = Date.now()\n  const deadline = startTime + MAX_WAIT_MS\n  const { fileExists, downloadTextFile } = await getMinioClient()\n\n  while (!_canceled && Date.now() < deadline) {\n    const elapsed = Date.now() - startTime\n    onProgress?.(elapsed)\n\n    try {\n      const exists = await fileExists(uuid)\n      if (exists) {\n        const content = await downloadTextFile(uuid)\n        return content\n      }\n    } catch (err) {\n      console.warn(`[waitForResult] 轮询出错:`, err)\n    }\n\n    onTick?.()\n    await sleep(POLL_INTERVAL_MS)\n  }\n\n  if (_canceled) throw new Error('用户取消了扫描')\n  throw new Error(`扫描超时（等待超过 ${MAX_WAIT_MS / 1000} 秒）`)\n}\n\nexport function cancelWait(): void {\n  _canceled = true\n}\n\nexport function resetCancel(): void {\n  _canceled = false\n}\n\nfunction sleep(ms: number): Promise<void> {\n  return new Promise((resolve) => setTimeout(resolve, ms))\n}","cwd":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775813226412}}
{"type":"message","id":"3a61492b","parentId":"db10740c","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:27:20.359Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me design the new simulator:\n\n1. **`src/simulator.ts`** - In-browser simulation:\n   - `SimulatedFile` Map: uuid → { content: string, ready: boolean }\n   - `generateFakeReport(uuid, prompt)`: generates a realistic fake MD report\n   - `submitScanTask(zipFile, enrichedPrompt, uuid)`: stores the report, sets timeout, returns 202\n   - `fileExists(uuid)`: checks if ready in the Map\n   - `downloadTextFile(uuid)`: returns content from Map\n\n2. **`src/scanService.ts`** - simplified, no USE_MOCK:\n   - Just imports from `./simulator`\n   - Exports the same functions but using the simulator\n\n3. **`src/mockMinioClient.ts`** - can be removed (or kept as reference to real minio)\n\n4. **`src/minio.ts`** - kept for real backend\n\n5. **`package.json`** - remove express, multer, cors, @types/*, tsx from dependencies, and remove mock-server and mock-minio scripts\n\n6. **`server/`** directory - deleted\n\nNow for the fake report generation, I want to create something more realistic that actually reflects the submitted prompt and UUID, with proper structure including scan overview, vulnerability sections, and recommendations.\n\nFor the timing, I'll use 5-8 seconds instead of 60s since there's no actual backend processing happening.\n\nLet me start building the simulator with the file map and core functions.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在统一改造：删除 server 目录，新建本地模拟器，重写 scanService：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9ee9njut5dqp_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"rm -rf /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/projects/code-scanner-plugin/server/\necho \"server/ 已删除\"\nls /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/projects/code-scanner-plugin/","timeout":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":1132,"output":404