{"type":"message","id":"7a51ce53","parentId":"7287863b","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:40:24.740Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[media attached: /home/gem/workspace/agent/media/inbound/æ_ºè½_ç_æ_å¼_æ_ä_å_é_è¾_å_å_å_æ_æ_å---86831fee-316d-4313-9ea8-8dd1145b9989 (text/html) | /home/gem/workspace/agent/media/inbound/æ_ºè½_ç_æ_å¼_æ_ä_å_é_è¾_å_å_å_æ_æ_å---86831fee-316d-4313-9ea8-8dd1145b9989]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Avoid absolute paths (MEDIA:/...) and ~ paths — they are blocked for security. Keep caption in the text body.\nSystem: [2026-04-10 17:40:23 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a [msg:om_x100b52b816acf0a4c3cfa3faa435627, file, 1 attachment(s)]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52b816acf0a4c3cfa3faa435627\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-10 17:40 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a\"\n}\n```\n\n[Feishu ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a Fri 2026-04-10 17:40 GMT+8] ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a: [File: /home/gem/workspace/agent/media/inbound/æ_ºè½_ç_æ_å¼_æ_ä_å_é_è¾_å_å_å_æ_æ_å---86831fee-316d-4313-9ea8-8dd1145b9989]\n\n<file name=\"æ_ºè½_ç_æ_å¼_æ_ä_å_é_è¾_å_å_å_æ_æ_å---86831fee-316d-4313-9ea8-8dd1145b9989\" mime=\"text/plain\">\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n<title>携转用户开户业务逻辑安全分析报告.md</title>\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-type\" content=\"text/html;charset=UTF-8\">\n\n<style>\n/* https://github.com/microsoft/vscode/blob/master/extensions/markdown-language-features/media/markdown.css */\n/*---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n * Copyright (c) Microsoft Corporation. All rights reserved.\n * Licensed under the MIT License. See License.txt in the project root for license information.\n *--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/\n\nbody {\n font-family: var(--vscode-markdown-font-family, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe WPC\", \"Segoe UI\", \"Ubuntu\", \"Droid Sans\", sans-serif);\n font-size: var(--vscode-markdown-font-size, 14px);\n padding: 0 26px;\n line-height: var(--vscode-markdown-line-height, 22px);\n word-wrap: break-word;\n}\n\n#code-csp-warning {\n position: fixed;\n top: 0;\n right: 0;\n color: white;\n margin: 16px;\n text-align: center;\n font-size: 12px;\n font-family: sans-serif;\n background-color:#444444;\n cursor: pointer;\n padding: 6px;\n box-shadow: 1px 1px 1px rgba(0,0,0,.25);\n}\n\n#code-csp-warning:hover {\n text-decoration: none;\n background-color:#007acc;\n box-shadow: 2px 2px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.25);\n}\n\nbody.scrollBeyondLastLine {\n margin-bottom: calc(100vh - 22px);\n}\n\nbody.showEditorSelection .code-line {\n position: relative;\n}\n\nbody.showEditorSelection .code-active-line:before,\nbody.showEditorSelection .code-line:hover:before {\n content: \"\";\n display: block;\n position: absolute;\n top: 0;\n left: -12px;\n height: 100%;\n}\n\nbody.showEditorSelection li.code-active-line:before,\nbody.showEditorSelection li.code-line:hover:before {\n left: -30px;\n}\n\n.vscode-light.showEditorSelection .code-active-line:before {\n border-left: 3px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n}\n\n.vscode-light.showEditorSelection .code-line:hover:before {\n border-left: 3px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.40);\n}\n\n.vscode-light.showEditorSelection .code-line .code-line:hover:before {\n border-left: none;\n}\n\n.vscode-dark.showEditorSelection .code-active-line:before {\n border-left: 3px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);\n}\n\n.vscode-dark.showEditorSelection .code-line:hover:before {\n border-left: 3px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.60);\n}\n\n.vscode-dark.showEditorSelection .code-line .code-line:hover:before {\n border-left: none;\n}\n\n.vscode-high-contrast.showEditorSelection .code-active-line:before {\n border-left: 3px solid rgba(255, 160, 0, 0.7);\n}\n\n.vscode-high-contrast.showEditorSelection .code-line:hover:before {\n border-left: 3px solid rgba(255, 160, 0, 1);\n}\n\n.vscode-high-contrast.showEditorSelection .code-line .code-line:hover:before {\n border-left: none;\n}\n\nimg {\n max-width: 100%;\n max-height: 100%;\n}\n\na {\n text-decoration: none;\n}\n\na:hover {\n text-decoration: underline;\n}\n\na:focus,\ninput:focus,\nselect:focus,\ntextarea:focus {\n outline: 1px solid -webkit-focus-ring-color;\n outline-offset: -1px;\n}\n\nhr {\n border: 0;\n height: 2px;\n border-bottom: 2px solid;\n}\n\nh1 {\n padding-bottom: 0.3em;\n line-height: 1.2;\n border-bottom-width: 1px;\n border-bottom-style: solid;\n}\n\nh1, h2, h3 {\n font-weight: normal;\n}\n\ntable {\n border-collapse: collapse;\n}\n\ntable > thead > tr > th {\n text-align: left;\n border-bottom: 1px solid;\n}\n\ntable > thead > tr > th,\ntable > thead > tr > td,\ntable > tbody > tr > th,\ntable > tbody > tr > td {\n padding: 5px 10px;\n}\n\ntable > tbody > tr + tr > td {\n border-top: 1px solid;\n}\n\nblockquote {\n margin: 0 7px 0 5px;\n padding: 0 16px 0 10px;\n border-left-width: 5px;\n border-left-style: solid;\n}\n\ncode {\n font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, \"Droid Sans Mono\", \"Courier New\", monospace, \"Droid Sans Fallback\";\n font-size: 1em;\n line-height: 1.357em;\n}\n\nbody.wordWrap pre {\n white-space: pre-wrap;\n}\n\npre:not(.hljs),\npre.hljs code > div {\n padding: 16px;\n border-radius: 3px;\n overflow: auto;\n}\n\npre code {\n color: var(--vscode-editor-foreground);\n tab-size: 4;\n}\n\n/** Theming */\n\n.vscode-light pre {\n background-color: rgba(220, 220, 220, 0.4);\n}\n\n.vscode-dark pre {\n background-color: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.4);\n}\n\n.vscode-high-contrast pre {\n background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\n}\n\n.vscode-high-contrast h1 {\n border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\n}\n\n.vscode-light table > thead > tr > th {\n border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.69);\n}\n\n.vscode-dark table > thead > tr > th {\n border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.69);\n}\n\n.vscode-light h1,\n.vscode-light hr,\n.vscode-light table > tbody > tr + tr > td {\n border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);\n}\n\n.vscode-dark h1,\n.vscode-dark hr,\n.vscode-dark table > tbody > tr + tr > td {\n border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);\n}\n\n</style>\n\n<style>\n/* Tomorrow Theme */\n/* http://jmblog.github.com/color-themes-for-google-code-highlightjs */\n/* Original theme - https://github.com/chriskempson/tomorrow-theme */\n\n/* Tomorrow Comment */\n.hljs-comment,\n.hljs-quote {\n color: #8e908c;\n}\n\n/* Tomorrow Red */\n.hljs-variable,\n.hljs-template-variable,\n.hljs-tag,\n.hljs-name,\n.hljs-selector-id,\n.hljs-selector-class,\n.hljs-regexp,\n.hljs-deletion {\n color: #c82829;\n}\n\n/* Tomorrow Orange */\n.hljs-number,\n.hljs-built_in,\n.hljs-builtin-name,\n.hljs-literal,\n.hljs-type,\n.hljs-params,\n.hljs-meta,\n.hljs-link {\n color: #f5871f;\n}\n\n/* Tomorrow Yellow */\n.hljs-attribute {\n color: #eab700;\n}\n\n/* Tomorrow Green */\n.hljs-string,\n.hljs-symbol,\n.hljs-bullet,\n.hljs-addition {\n color: #718c00;\n}\n\n/* Tomorrow Blue */\n.hljs-title,\n.hljs-section {\n color: #4271ae;\n}\n\n/* Tomorrow Purple */\n.hljs-keyword,\n.hljs-selector-tag {\n color: #8959a8;\n}\n\n.hljs {\n display: block;\n overflow-x: auto;\n color: #4d4d4c;\n padding: 0.5em;\n}\n\n.hljs-emphasis {\n font-style: italic;\n}\n\n.hljs-strong {\n font-weight: bold;\n}\n</style>\n\n<style>\n/*\n * Markdown PDF CSS\n */\n\n body {\n font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe WPC\", \"Segoe UI\", \"Ubuntu\", \"Droid Sans\", sans-serif, \"Meiryo\";\n padding: 0 12px;\n}\n\npre {\n background-color: #f8f8f8;\n border: 1px solid #cccccc;\n border-radius: 3px;\n overflow-x: auto;\n white-space: pre-wrap;\n overflow-wrap: break-word;\n}\n\npre:not(.hljs) {\n padding: 23px;\n line-height: 19px;\n}\n\nblockquote {\n background: rgba(127, 127, 127, 0.1);\n border-color: rgba(0, 122, 204, 0.5);\n}\n\n.emoji {\n height: 1.4em;\n}\n\ncode {\n font-size: 14px;\n line-height: 19px;\n}\n\n/* for inline code */\n:not(pre):not(.hljs) > code {\n color: #C9AE75; /* Change the old color so it seems less like an error */\n font-size: inherit;\n}\n\n/* Page Break : use <div class=\"page\"/> to insert page break\n-------------------------------------------------------- */\n.page {\n page-break-after: always;\n}\n\n</style>\n\n<script src=\"https://unpkg.com/mermaid/dist/mermaid.min.js\"></script>\n</head>\n<body>\n <script>\n mermaid.initialize({\n startOnLoad: true,\n theme: document.body.classList.contains('vscode-dark') || document.body.classList.contains('vscode-high-contrast')\n ? 'dark'\n : 'default'\n });\n </script>\n<h1 id=\"%E6%90%BA%E8%BD%AC%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E5%BC%80%E6%88%B7-%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A\">携转用户开户 业务逻辑安全分析报告</h1>\n<h2 id=\"%E4%B8%80%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E6%A6%82%E8%A7%88\">一、漏洞概览</h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:left\">漏洞编号</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:left\">漏洞名称</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:left\">严重程度</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:left\">漏洞类型</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">VUL-001</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">开户提交接口重复提交（幂等性缺失）</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">高危</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">业务流程绕过/参数重放</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">VUL-002</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">携入号码归属地校验硬编码绕过</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">高危</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">权限与访问控制/权限提升路径</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">VUL-003</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">吉祥号码验证码授权仅前端控制</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">高危</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">权限与访问控制/越权操作</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">VUL-004</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">NP_VERIFY记录删除与开户操作非原子性</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">高危</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">业务流程绕过/状态机异常</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">VUL-005</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">营销活动类型02权限校验可被绕过</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">中危</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">权限与访问控制/权限提升路径</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">VUL-006</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">证件预占释放条件不完整</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">中危</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">业务流程绕过/状态机异常</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">VUL-007</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">随机密码弱随机数生成</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">中危</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">数据校验缺失/数据类型混淆</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">VUL-008</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">协议生成接口非幂等可被滥用</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">中危</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">业务流程绕过/参数重放</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">VUL-009</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">值班长验证码无频率限制和重试锁定</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">中危</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">验证码与限流/无操作频率限制</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">VUL-010</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">一证多名检查仅覆盖证件类型0</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">低危</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">数据校验缺失/业务规则绕过</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">VUL-011</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">吉祥号操作日志异常被静默吞没</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">低危</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">信息泄露/审计缺失</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"%E4%BA%8C%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E8%AF%A6%E6%83%85\">二、漏洞详情</h2>\n<h3 id=\"21-%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E5%BC%80%E6%88%B7%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B---%E5%BC%80%E6%88%B7%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%8D%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E5%B9%82%E7%AD%89%E6%80%A7%E7%BC%BA%E5%A4%B1\">2.1 提交开户流程 - 开户提交接口重复提交（幂等性缺失）</h3>\n<p><strong>漏洞类型：</strong> 业务流程绕过/参数重放</p>\n<p><strong>风险等级：</strong> 高危</p>\n<p><strong>漏洞描述：</strong>\n<code>onTradeSubmit</code> 接口调用 <code>createNpSubscriber</code> 创建用户、账户、订购和携转关系记录，整个流程无任何幂等性控制。攻击者可通过拦截请求并重复发送，在同一携入号码上创建多个用户账户，导致重复开户、资源浪费、计费混乱等严重后果。业务逻辑说明文档 6.5 节已明确标注&quot;重复提交会创建重复用户&quot;。</p>\n<p><strong>关键代码片段：</strong></p>\n<p><code>NpSubscriberOpen.java:134-185</code></p>\n<pre class=\"hljs\"><code><div><span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">onTradeSubmit</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">(IRequestCycle cycle)</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">throws</span> Exception\n</span>{\n IData param = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.getData();\n IData acctInfo = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.getData(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"acctinfo\"</span>);\n param.putAll(acctInfo);\n IDataset offerList = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> DatasetList(param.getString(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"SELECTED_OFFER_VALUE\"</span>));\n <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// ... 组装offerList</span>\n param.put(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"OFFERS\"</span>, offerList);\n param.put(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"ROUTE_CODE\"</span>,<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.getVisit().getLoginEparchyCode());\n\n IData result = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> DataMap();\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">boolean</span> hasError = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">false</span>;\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">try</span>{\n result =<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.call(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"OrderCentre.person.INpSubscriberOpenOperateSV.createNpSubscriber\"</span>, param);\n }<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">catch</span>(Exception e) {\n String eMsg = e.getMessage();\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(!StringUtil.contains(eMsg,<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"证件号码被预占\"</span>)){\n hasError=<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">true</span>;\n }\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">throw</span> e;\n }<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">finally</span>{\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(hasError){\n <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//证件解预占</span>\n IData input = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> DataMap();\n input.put(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"CUST_NAME\"</span>, param.getString(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"PARTY_NAME\"</span>,param.getString(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"UP_NAME\"</span>,<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"\"</span>)));\n input.put(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"IDEN_TYPE_ID\"</span>, idenTypeID);\n input.put(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"IDEN_NR\"</span>, param.getString(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"IDEN_NR\"</span>));\n input.put(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"CAMP_ON\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"02\"</span>);\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.call(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"CustomerCentre.custmgr.ICCOutOperateSV.cardCampOn\"</span>, input);\n }\n }\n setAjax(result);\n}\n</div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>漏洞成因分析：</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-mermaid\"><div class=\"mermaid\">sequenceDiagram\n participant Attacker as 攻击者\n participant FE as 前端\n participant API as NpSubscriberOpen.onTradeSubmit\n participant SV as createNpSubscriber\n participant DB as 数据库\n \n Note over Attacker,DB: 漏洞利用流程 - 重复提交开户\n Attacker->>FE: 正常完成开户流程\n FE->>API: 提交开户请求(携带完整表单数据)\n API->>SV: createNpSubscriber\n SV->>DB: INSERT 用户表/账户表/订购表/携转关系表\n DB-->>SV: TRADE_ID, 开户成功\n SV-->>API: 返回成功\n API-->>FE: 开户完成\n Note over Attacker: 拦截并保存该请求\n Attacker->>API: 重放同一请求(相同ACCESS_NUM, IDEN_NR)\n Note over API: 无请求去重/幂等校验\n API->>SV: createNpSubscriber(相同参数)\n SV->>DB: 再次INSERT\n Note over DB: 若无唯一约束则创建重复记录\n DB-->>SV: 可能成功\n SV-->>API: 返回成功\n API-->>Attacker: 重复开户成功\n</div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>复现步骤：</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>登录系统，进入携转用户开户页面</li>\n<li>正常完成携入号码校验、SIM卡校验、套餐选择、协议签订全流程</li>\n<li>打开浏览器开发者工具，切换到 Network 面板</li>\n<li>点击&quot;提交&quot;按钮，拦截 <code>onTradeSubmit</code> 请求</li>\n<li>记录请求参数（ACCESS_NUM、IDEN_NR、SELECTED_OFFER_VALUE 等）</li>\n<li>等待首次提交完成后，使用 Burp Repeater 或 curl 重放同一请求</li>\n<li>观察响应，检查数据库是否创建了重复用户记录</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>预期结果：</strong> 系统应检测到重复提交，返回&quot;该号码已存在开户工单&quot;或类似错误</p>\n<p><strong>实际结果：</strong> 系统无幂等性校验，可能创建重复用户/账户/订购记录</p>\n<p><strong>验证请求示例：</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"hljs\"><code><div><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">POST</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">/person/cs/npsubscriberopen/NpSubscriberOpen.app?service=listener/onTradeSubmit</span> HTTP/1.1\n<span class=\"hljs-attribute\">Host</span>: crm.example.com\n<span class=\"hljs-attribute\">Cookie</span>: JSESSIONID=xxx\n<span class=\"hljs-attribute\">Content-Type</span>: application/x-www-form-urlencoded\n\n<span class=\"dts\">ACCESS_NUM=<span class=\"hljs-number\">13800138000</span><span class=\"hljs-variable\">&amp;</span>IDEN_NR=<span class=\"hljs-number\">530102199001011234</span><span class=\"hljs-variable\">&amp;</span>PARTY_NAME=张三<span class=\"hljs-variable\">&amp;</span>SELECTED_OFFER_VALUE=[{<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"OFFER_ID\"</span>:<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"100001\"</span>}]<span class=\"hljs-variable\">&amp;</span>ICC_ID=<span class=\"hljs-number\">89860000000000000001</span>&amp;...\n</span></div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>修复建议：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>代码层面：</strong> 在 <code>onTradeSubmit</code> 入口处增加唯一性校验，基于 ACCESS_NUM + 当前日期 + 操作员ID 生成请求指纹，写入 Redis 或数据库去重表，设置合理过期时间（如5分钟）</li>\n<li><strong>代码层面：</strong> 在 <code>createNpSubscriber</code> 服务中增加前置校验：<code>SELECT COUNT(*) FROM 用户表 WHERE ACCESS_NUM = ? AND STATUS = '有效'</code>，若已存在则拒绝</li>\n<li><strong>架构层面：</strong> 引入分布式锁（Redis SETNX），以 ACCESS_NUM 为 key，在开户提交期间持有锁，防止并发提交</li>\n<li><strong>配置层面：</strong> 数据库层面对 ACCESS_NUM + STATUS 添加唯一约束</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>参考：</strong> 类似案例 - CWE-362: Concurrent Execution using Shared Resource with Improper Synchronization</p>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"22-%E6%90%BA%E5%85%A5%E5%8F%B7%E7%A0%81%E6%A0%A1%E9%AA%8C%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B---%E5%BD%92%E5%B1%9E%E5%9C%B0%E6%A0%A1%E9%AA%8C%E7%A1%AC%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81%E7%BB%95%E8%BF%87\">2.2 携入号码校验流程 - 归属地校验硬编码绕过</h3>\n<p><strong>漏洞类型：</strong> 权限与访问控制/权限提升路径</p>\n<p><strong>风险等级：</strong> 高危</p>\n<p><strong>漏洞描述：</strong>\n<code>CheckAccessNumSVC</code> 在校验携入号码归属地时，对工号 <code>IBOSS000</code> 做了硬编码豁免，跳过归属地一致性校验。这意味着任何能使用该工号（或伪造该工号）的操作员可以为任意地州的携入号码办理开户，突破了地州业务隔离的安全边界。</p>\n<p><strong>关键代码片段：</strong></p>\n<p><code>CheckAccessNumSVC.java:141-148</code></p>\n<pre class=\"hljs\"><code><div>String staffId = String.valueOf(userinfo.get(BcConstants.TRADE_STAFF_ID));\n\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">// ... 查询号码归属地 areaCode</span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(!StringUtil.equals(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"IBOSS000\"</span>, staffId)){<span class=\"hljs-comment\">//接口进来不校验 hedong3</span>\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (!StringUtils.equals(areaCode,tradeEparchyCode))\n {\n <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//登陆员工地州:\"+tradeEparchyCode+\"与携入号码归属地:\"+areaCode+\"不一致!</span>\n CSBizException.bizerr(OrderException.CRM_ORDER_85,tradeEparchyCode,areaCode);\n }\n}\n</div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>漏洞成因分析：</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-mermaid\"><div class=\"mermaid\">sequenceDiagram\n participant Attacker as 恶意操作员\n participant API as CheckAccessNumSVC\n participant DB as 号码资源表\n \n Note over Attacker,DB: 漏洞利用流程 - 跨地州携入开户\n Attacker->>API: checkAccessNum(ACCESS_NUM=异地号码)\n Note over API: staffId = \"IBOSS000\"\n Note over API: 硬编码判断: 跳过归属地校验\n API->>DB: SELECT 携转用户表(不校验地州)\n DB-->>API: 返回携转数据\n API-->>Attacker: 校验通过, 可继续开户\n Note over Attacker: 跨地州携入开户成功\n</div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>复现步骤：</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>使用工号 <code>IBOSS000</code> 登录系统（或通过接口调用模拟该工号）</li>\n<li>进入携转用户开户页面</li>\n<li>输入一个归属地与当前登录地州不一致的携入号码</li>\n<li>点击校验按钮</li>\n<li>观察响应，确认是否通过校验</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>预期结果：</strong> 系统应校验操作员地州与号码归属地一致性，跨地州应拒绝</p>\n<p><strong>实际结果：</strong> 工号 <code>IBOSS000</code> 完全跳过归属地校验，可为任意地州号码开户</p>\n<p><strong>验证请求示例：</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"hljs\"><code><div><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">POST</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">/person/cs/npsubscriberopen/NpSubscriberOpen.app?service=listener/checkAccessNum</span> HTTP/1.1\n<span class=\"hljs-attribute\">Host</span>: crm.example.com\n<span class=\"hljs-attribute\">Cookie</span>: JSESSIONID=xxx\n<span class=\"hljs-attribute\">Content-Type</span>: application/x-www-form-urlencoded\n\n<span class=\"dts\">ACCESS_NUM=<span class=\"hljs-number\">13908710001</span><span class=\"hljs-variable\">&amp;</span>NP_BACK=<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span><span class=\"hljs-variable\">&amp;</span>AGENT_DEPART_ID=<span class=\"hljs-variable\">&amp;</span>EC_GROUP_ID=\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\"># 假设当前登录地州为<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"昆明\"</span>，但号码归属地为<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"大理\"</span></span>\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\"># 使用IBOSS000工号登录时可绕过校验</span>\n</span></div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>修复建议：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>代码层面：</strong> 移除硬编码 <code>IBOSS000</code> 豁免逻辑，改为通过权限配置表控制跨地州操作权限</li>\n<li><strong>代码层面：</strong> 若确实需要接口调用豁免，应通过请求来源标识（如 IP 白名单、API Gateway 签名）而非工号判断</li>\n<li><strong>配置层面：</strong> 建立跨地州操作审批流程，所有跨地州操作记录审计日志并触发告警</li>\n<li><strong>架构层面：</strong> 引入 API Gateway 层，区分前端页面调用和后端系统接口调用</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"23-%E5%90%89%E7%A5%A5%E5%8F%B7%E7%A0%81%E6%9D%83%E9%99%90%E6%A0%A1%E9%AA%8C%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B---%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81%E7%A0%81%E6%8E%88%E6%9D%83%E4%BB%85%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6\">2.3 吉祥号码权限校验流程 - 验证码授权仅前端控制</h3>\n<p><strong>漏洞类型：</strong> 权限与访问控制/越权操作</p>\n<p><strong>风险等级：</strong> 高危</p>\n<p><strong>漏洞描述：</strong>\n吉祥号码需要值班长验证码授权才能办理，但验证码校验结果 <code>yzmValidFlag</code> 仅存储在前端 JavaScript 变量中。攻击者可通过修改前端 JS 变量或直接构造请求绕过验证码校验，在未经值班长授权的情况下为吉祥号码开户。</p>\n<p><strong>关键代码片段：</strong></p>\n<p><code>NpSubscriberOpen.java:275-299</code> - 吉祥号判断仅返回 ISLUCKY 标记</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs\"><code><div><span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">initIMPOWER</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">(IRequestCycle cycle)</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">throws</span> Exception\n</span>{\n IData param = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.getData();\n IData result1 = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.call(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"ResourceCentre.resource.INumberIntfQuerySV.querySingNumInfo\"</span>, param);\n String islucky= (String) result1.getDataset(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"DATAS\"</span>).get(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"BEAUTIFUAL_TAG\"</span>);\n <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// ... 记录日志</span>\n retInfo.put(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"ISLUCKY\"</span>, islucky);\n setAjax(retInfo);\n}\n</div></code></pre>\n<p><code>onTradeSubmit</code> 中<strong>未校验</strong>吉祥号码验证码状态：</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs\"><code><div><span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">onTradeSubmit</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">(IRequestCycle cycle)</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">throws</span> Exception\n</span>{\n IData param = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.getData();\n <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// ... 无任何吉祥号验证码校验逻辑</span>\n result = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.call(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"OrderCentre.person.INpSubscriberOpenOperateSV.createNpSubscriber\"</span>, param);\n setAjax(result);\n}\n</div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>漏洞成因分析：</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-mermaid\"><div class=\"mermaid\">sequenceDiagram\n participant Attacker as 恶意操作员\n participant FE as 前端JS\n participant API as NpSubscriberOpen.onTradeSubmit\n participant SV as createNpSubscriber\n participant DB as 数据库\n \n Note over Attacker,DB: 漏洞利用流程 - 绕过吉祥号码验证码\n Attacker->>FE: 输入吉祥号码\n FE->>API: initIMPOWER(ACCESS_NUM)\n API-->>FE: ISLUCKY=1 (是吉祥号)\n Note over FE: 前端显示验证码区域\n Note over Attacker: 不输入验证码，直接修改JS\n Attacker->>FE: yzmValidFlag = 0 (前端变量)\n Attacker->>FE: 点击提交\n FE->>API: onTradeSubmit(完整表单数据)\n Note over API: 未校验验证码状态\n API->>SV: createNpSubscriber\n SV->>DB: INSERT 用户/账户/订购\n DB-->>SV: 成功\n SV-->>API: 开户成功\n API-->>Attacker: 吉祥号码开户完成(未授权)\n</div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>复现步骤：</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>登录系统，进入携转用户开户页面</li>\n<li>输入一个吉祥号码（触发 ISLUCKY=1）</li>\n<li>不输入值班长工号和验证码</li>\n<li>打开浏览器开发者工具 Console</li>\n<li>执行 <code>yzmValidFlag = 0</code> 修改前端校验标志</li>\n<li>填写其他必填信息，点击提交</li>\n<li>观察是否成功开户</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>预期结果：</strong> 吉祥号码必须通过值班长验证码校验才能提交开户</p>\n<p><strong>实际结果：</strong> 前端校验可被绕过，后端未做二次校验，吉祥号码无需授权即可开户</p>\n<p><strong>验证请求示例：</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"hljs\"><code><div><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">POST</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">/person/cs/npsubscriberopen/NpSubscriberOpen.app?service=listener/onTradeSubmit</span> HTTP/1.1\n<span class=\"hljs-attribute\">Host</span>: crm.example.com\n<span class=\"hljs-attribute\">Cookie</span>: JSESSIONID=xxx\n<span class=\"hljs-attribute\">Content-Type</span>: application/x-www-form-urlencoded\n\n<span class=\"dts\">ACCESS_NUM=<span class=\"hljs-number\">13888888888</span><span class=\"hljs-variable\">&amp;</span>IDEN_NR=<span class=\"hljs-number\">530102199001011234</span><span class=\"hljs-variable\">&amp;</span>PARTY_NAME=张三<span class=\"hljs-variable\">&amp;</span>SELECTED_OFFER_VALUE=[{<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"OFFER_ID\"</span>:<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"100001\"</span>}]&amp;...\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\"># 注意：请求中无任何验证码相关参数，后端也未校验</span>\n</span></div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>修复建议：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>代码层面：</strong> 在 <code>onTradeSubmit</code> 中增加吉祥号码校验逻辑：查询号码是否为吉祥号，若是则校验验证码状态（从数据库或缓存中读取 <code>smsValidFlag</code>）</li>\n<li><strong>代码层面：</strong> 验证码校验结果应存储在服务端（Session/Redis），而非前端 JS 变量</li>\n<li><strong>架构层面：</strong> 将吉祥号码授权作为独立的前置审批流程，审批通过后才允许进入开户提交环节</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"24-%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E5%BC%80%E6%88%B7%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B---npverify%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4%E4%B8%8E%E5%BC%80%E6%88%B7%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E9%9D%9E%E5%8E%9F%E5%AD%90%E6%80%A7\">2.4 提交开户流程 - NP_VERIFY记录删除与开户操作非原子性</h3>\n<p><strong>漏洞类型：</strong> 业务流程绕过/状态机异常</p>\n<p><strong>风险等级：</strong> 高危</p>\n<p><strong>漏洞描述：</strong>\n在 <code>CreateNpDistrictVerb.run()</code> 中，NP_VERIFY（携入申请审核）记录在开户流程<strong>中间阶段</strong>被物理删除。如果后续步骤（资源选占、账户创建等）失败，NP_VERIFY 记录已被删除但开户未完成，导致该携入号码无法再次办理开户（查询不到审核记录），形成业务死锁。</p>\n<p><strong>关键代码片段：</strong></p>\n<p><code>CreateNpDistrictVerb.java:66-73</code></p>\n<pre class=\"hljs\"><code><div><span class=\"hljs-comment\">//物理删除NP_VERIFY</span>\nInteractionDatabus databus = InteractionDatabus.getDatabus();\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">int</span> submitType = databus.getSubmitType();\nString businessSceneType = databus.getFirstRequest().getString(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"BUSINESS_SCENE_TYPE\"</span>,<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"\"</span>);\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(!<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"CHBN_ORDER\"</span>.equals(businessSceneType) || submitType != SubmitTypeConst.PRE_CHECK) {\n IOmNpVerifyOprateSV omNpVerifyOprateSV = (IOmNpVerifyOprateSV) ServiceFactory.getService(IOmNpVerifyOprateSV<span class=\"hljs-class\">.<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span>)</span>;\n npVerifyInfo.delete();\n omNpVerifyOprateSV.delData(npVerifyInfo);\n}\n\nec.add(sca,nde);\n</div></code></pre>\n<p>同时 <code>NpSubscriberOpenSVC.java:474-491</code> 中也存在类似的直接 SQL 删除：</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs\"><code><div><span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">private</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">dealOmNpVerify</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">(DataContainer[] auditDcs)</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">throws</span> Exception </span>{\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">int</span> i=<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>;i&lt;auditDcs.length; i++){\n DataContainer value = auditDcs[i];\n String np_very_id = value.getAsString(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"NP_VERIFY_ID\"</span>);\n <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// ... 保存到历史表</span>\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">int</span> num = insv.saveOmNpDistrict(value);\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(num == <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>){\n <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//清除掉审核数据表中的数据记录</span>\n String connName = <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"JOUR\"</span> + CenterFactory.getCenterInfo().getCenter();\n String sql = <span class=\"hljs-string\">\" DELETE FROM OM_NP_VERIFY WHERE NP_VERIFY_ID = :NP_VERIFY_ID \"</span>;\n Map&lt;String,String&gt; param = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> HashMap&lt;String,String&gt;();\n param.put(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"NP_VERIFY_ID\"</span>, np_very_id);\n ExecuteSqlUtil.execute(connName, sql, param);\n }\n }\n}\n</div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>漏洞成因分析：</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-mermaid\"><div class=\"mermaid\">sequenceDiagram\n participant User as 操作员\n participant API as onTradeSubmit\n participant Verb as CreateNpDistrictVerb\n participant Modifier as NpResOccupyModifier\n participant DB as 数据库\n \n Note over User,DB: 漏洞利用流程 - 非原子删除导致业务死锁\n User->>API: 提交开户\n API->>Verb: run() - 创建携号信息\n Verb->>DB: DELETE FROM OM_NP_VERIFY (物理删除)\n DB-->>Verb: 删除成功\n Verb->>Modifier: 继续后续流程\n Modifier->>DB: 选占号码资源\n DB-->>Modifier: 资源不足/选占失败\n Note over Modifier: 异常抛出，流程中断\n Note over DB: NP_VERIFY已删除，开户未完成\n Note over User: 再次尝试为该号码开户\n User->>API: checkAccessNum(同一号码)\n API->>DB: SELECT OM_NP_VERIFY\n DB-->>API: 无记录 (flag=1)\n API-->>User: \"不存在携入申请审核记录\"\n Note over User: 业务死锁 - 无法再次开户\n</div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>复现步骤：</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>准备一个携入号码，确保其 OM_NP_VERIFY 表中有审核通过的记录</li>\n<li>登录系统，进入携转用户开户页面</li>\n<li>完成携入号码校验、SIM卡校验、套餐选择</li>\n<li>点击提交开户</li>\n<li>在 <code>CreateNpDistrictVerb</code> 删除 NP_VERIFY 记录后、开户完成前，模拟资源选占失败（如 SIM 卡资源不足）</li>\n<li>观察开户失败后，再次尝试为该号码办理开户</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>预期结果：</strong> 开户失败时应回滚 NP_VERIFY 记录删除操作，或将其标记为&quot;处理中&quot;而非物理删除</p>\n<p><strong>实际结果：</strong> NP_VERIFY 记录被提前删除，开户失败后无法恢复，号码无法再次办理</p>\n<p><strong>修复建议：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>代码层面：</strong> 将 NP_VERIFY 记录的删除操作移至整个开户流程的最后一步（所有资源选占、数据写入成功后）</li>\n<li><strong>代码层面：</strong> 使用状态标记替代物理删除：<code>UPDATE OM_NP_VERIFY SET STATUS = 'USED' WHERE NP_VERIFY_ID = ?</code></li>\n<li><strong>代码层面：</strong> 在事务回滚逻辑中增加 NP_VERIFY 记录恢复机制</li>\n<li><strong>架构层面：</strong> 整个开户流程应包裹在数据库事务中，确保原子性</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"25-%E5%A5%97%E9%A4%90%E5%92%8C%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B---%E8%90%A5%E9%94%80%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B02%E6%9D%83%E9%99%90%E6%A0%A1%E9%AA%8C%E5%8F%AF%E8%A2%AB%E7%BB%95%E8%BF%87\">2.5 套餐和活动选择流程 - 营销活动类型02权限校验可被绕过</h3>\n<p><strong>漏洞类型：</strong> 权限与访问控制/权限提升路径</p>\n<p><strong>风险等级：</strong> 中危</p>\n<p><strong>漏洞描述：</strong>\n<code>NPOPENTAKEACTIVE</code> 权限用于控制操作员是否可以受理携号入网营销活动（类型02的 offer）。但在 <code>NpSubscriberOpenSVC</code> 中，当 <code>OPEN_TYPE=11</code>（携号副卡开户）时，权限校验被完全绕过（<code>isNpGiftOpen</code> 标记），任何操作员都可以为携号副卡添加营销活动。</p>\n<p><strong>关键代码片段：</strong></p>\n<p><code>NpSubscriberOpenSVC.java:230-310</code></p>\n<pre class=\"hljs\"><code><div><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">boolean</span> npOpenTakeActiveGlag = PrivCheck.checkDomPermission(opId, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"NPOPENTAKEACTIVE\"</span>);\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 是否携号副卡开户</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">boolean</span> isNpGiftOpen = StringUtils.equals(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"11\"</span>, request.getString(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"OPEN_TYPE\"</span>));\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span>(TreePart offer : offers)\n{\n String offerId = offer.getString(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"OFFER_ID\"</span>);\n OfferCfg cfg = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> OfferCfg(offerId);\n <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// ...</span>\n }<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"02\"</span>.equals(cfg.getType())){\n <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//if(PrivCheck.checkDomPermission(opId, \"NPOPENTAKEACTIVE\"))</span>\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(npOpenTakeActiveGlag || isNpGiftOpen) <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 副卡开户绕过权限</span>\n {\n campnOffer = offer;\n }\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n CSBizException.bizerr(OrderException.CRM_ORDER_715,<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"当前工号没有受理携号入网政策的特权，不能办理入网活动\"</span>);\n }\n }\n}\n</div></code></pre>\n<p>同时前端 <code>NpSubscriberOpen.java:143-151</code> 也存在同样的绕过：</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs\"><code><div><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(PrivCheck.checkDomPermission(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.getVisit().getStaffId(), <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"NPOPENTAKEACTIVE\"</span>))\n{\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(StringUtils.isNotBlank(param.getString(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"SELECTED_ACTIVE_VALUE\"</span>)) &amp;&amp; !<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"undefined\"</span>.equals(param.getString(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"SELECTED_ACTIVE_VALUE\"</span>))){\n param.put(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"IS_ACTIVE_OPEN\"</span>,<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"1\"</span>);<span class=\"hljs-comment\">//开户营销标记</span>\n IDataset active = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> DatasetList(param.getString(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"SELECTED_ACTIVE_VALUE\"</span>));\n offerList.addAll(active);\n }\n}\n</div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>漏洞成因分析：</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-mermaid\"><div class=\"mermaid\">sequenceDiagram\n participant Attacker as 低权限操作员\n participant FE as 前端\n participant API as onTradeSubmit\n participant SV as NpSubscriberOpenSVC\n participant DB as 数据库\n \n Note over Attacker,DB: 漏洞利用流程 - 通过副卡开户绕过营销权限\n Attacker->>FE: 构造请求 OPEN_TYPE=11\n FE->>API: onTradeSubmit(OPEN_TYPE=11, SELECTED_ACTIVE_VALUE)\n Note over API: 权限校验: PrivCheck.checkDomPermission -> false\n Note over API: 但 SELECTED_ACTIVE_VALUE 仍被传入\n API->>SV: createNpSubscriber\n Note over SV: isNpGiftOpen = true (OPEN_TYPE=11)\n Note over SV: 权限校验被绕过: npOpenTakeActiveGlag || isNpGiftOpen = true\n SV->>DB: INSERT 营销活动订购记录\n DB-->>SV: 成功\n SV-->>API: 开户成功(含营销活动)\n API-->>Attacker: 营销活动添加成功\n</div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>复现步骤：</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>使用一个没有 <code>NPOPENTAKEACTIVE</code> 权限的普通操作员账号登录</li>\n<li>正常进入携转用户开户页面</li>\n<li>通过开发者工具修改请求参数，将 <code>OPEN_TYPE</code> 修改为 <code>11</code></li>\n<li>在 <code>SELECTED_ACTIVE_VALUE</code> 中添加营销活动 offer（类型02）</li>\n<li>提交开户请求</li>\n<li>观察营销活动是否被成功添加</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>预期结果：</strong> 无权限的操作员即使通过副卡开户类型也不能添加营销活动</p>\n<p><strong>实际结果：</strong> OPEN_TYPE=11 时权限校验被完全绕过，可添加任意营销活动</p>\n<p><strong>修复建议：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>代码层面：</strong> 移除 <code>isNpGiftOpen</code> 对权限校验的绕过，副卡开户也应校验 <code>NPOPENTAKEACTIVE</code> 权限</li>\n<li><strong>代码层面：</strong> 若副卡开户确实需要特殊处理，应使用独立的权限标识（如 <code>NPGIFTOPEN_ACTIVE</code>）而非完全绕过</li>\n<li><strong>代码层面：</strong> 前端 <code>onTradeSubmit</code> 和 <code>sendEpaperPre</code> 中也应同步修复权限校验逻辑</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"26-%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E5%BC%80%E6%88%B7%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B---%E8%AF%81%E4%BB%B6%E9%A2%84%E5%8D%A0%E9%87%8A%E6%94%BE%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4\">2.6 提交开户流程 - 证件预占释放条件不完整</h3>\n<p><strong>漏洞类型：</strong> 业务流程绕过/状态机异常</p>\n<p><strong>风险等级：</strong> 中危</p>\n<p><strong>漏洞描述：</strong>\n在 <code>onTradeSubmit</code> 的异常处理中，仅当 <code>hasError=true</code> 时才释放证件预占。但 <code>hasError</code> 的判定条件为 <code>!StringUtil.contains(eMsg,&quot;证件号码被预占&quot;)</code>，即当异常消息包含&quot;证件号码被预占&quot;时 <code>hasError=false</code>，不会释放预占。然而此时开户实际上失败了，证件预占状态未被清理，导致该证件无法再次办理业务。</p>\n<p><strong>关键代码片段：</strong></p>\n<p><code>NpSubscriberOpen.java:157-183</code></p>\n<pre class=\"hljs\"><code><div>IData result = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> DataMap();\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">boolean</span> hasError = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">false</span>;\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">try</span>{\n result =<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.call(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"OrderCentre.person.INpSubscriberOpenOperateSV.createNpSubscriber\"</span>, param);\n}<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">catch</span>(Exception e) {\n String eMsg = e.getMessage();\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(!StringUtil.contains(eMsg,<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"证件号码被预占\"</span>)){\n hasError=<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">true</span>;\n }\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">throw</span> e;\n}<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">finally</span>{\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(hasError){\n <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//证件解预占</span>\n IData input = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> DataMap();\n input.put(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"CUST_NAME\"</span>, param.getString(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"PARTY_NAME\"</span>,param.getString(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"UP_NAME\"</span>,<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"\"</span>)));\n String idenTypeID=param.getString(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"IDEN_TYPE_ID\"</span>);\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(StringUtils.isBlank(idenTypeID))\n {\n idenTypeID=param.getString(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"IDEN_TYPE_CODE\"</span>,<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"10000000\"</span>);<span class=\"hljs-comment\">//默认为身份证</span>\n }\n input.put(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"IDEN_TYPE_ID\"</span>, idenTypeID);\n input.put(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"IDEN_NR\"</span>, param.getString(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"IDEN_NR\"</span>));\n input.put(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"CAMP_ON\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"02\"</span>);\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.call(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"CustomerCentre.custmgr.ICCOutOperateSV.cardCampOn\"</span>, input);\n }\n}\n</div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>漏洞成因分析：</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-mermaid\"><div class=\"mermaid\">sequenceDiagram\n participant User as 操作员\n participant API as onTradeSubmit\n participant SV as createNpSubscriber\n participant DB as 数据库\n \n Note over User,DB: 漏洞利用流程 - 证件预占未释放\n User->>API: 提交开户\n API->>SV: createNpSubscriber\n SV->>DB: 证件预占检查\n DB-->>SV: 证件已被预占(其他工单占用)\n SV-->>API: 抛出异常 \"证件号码被预占\"\n Note over API: eMsg 包含 \"证件号码被预占\"\n Note over API: hasError = false (不释放预占)\n Note over API: 但开户确实失败了\n API-->>User: 开户失败: 证件号码被预占\n Note over User: 证件持续被预占，无法再次办理\n Note over User: 需等待预占超时或管理员手动释放\n</div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>复现步骤：</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>操作员A为用户张三办理开户，提交后系统对证件进行预占</li>\n<li>操作员B尝试用同一证件为张三办理另一笔业务</li>\n<li>系统返回&quot;证件号码被预占&quot;错误</li>\n<li>操作员A的开户流程因其他原因失败（如资源不足）</li>\n<li>检查证件预占状态，发现仍未释放</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>预期结果：</strong> 无论何种原因导致开户失败，都应释放证件预占</p>\n<p><strong>实际结果：</strong> 当异常消息包含&quot;证件号码被预占&quot;时，预占状态不被释放</p>\n<p><strong>修复建议：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>代码层面：</strong> 修改异常处理逻辑，所有开户失败场景都应释放证件预占：</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"hljs\"><code><div>}<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">finally</span>{\n <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 无论何种异常，只要开户失败就释放预占</span>\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(hasError || result == <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">null</span> || result.isEmpty()){\n <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 释放证件预占</span>\n }\n}\n</div></code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>代码层面：</strong> 预占应设置自动过期时间，超时后自动释放</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"27-%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E5%BC%80%E6%88%B7%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B---%E9%9A%8F%E6%9C%BA%E5%AF%86%E7%A0%81%E5%BC%B1%E9%9A%8F%E6%9C%BA%E6%95%B0%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90\">2.7 提交开户流程 - 随机密码弱随机数生成</h3>\n<p><strong>漏洞类型：</strong> 数据校验缺失/数据类型混淆</p>\n<p><strong>风险等级：</strong> 中危</p>\n<p><strong>漏洞描述：</strong>\n当 <code>NEED_PASSWORD=0</code> 时，系统自动生成6位数字随机密码。但使用的是 <code>java.util.Random</code> 而非 <code>java.security.SecureRandom</code>。<code>java.util.Random</code> 是基于线性同余生成器（LCG）的伪随机数生成器，其输出可被预测。攻击者若知道某个时间点生成的密码，可推算出同一时间段内生成的其他密码。</p>\n<p><strong>关键代码片段：</strong></p>\n<p><code>NpSubscriberOpenSVC.java:408-416</code></p>\n<pre class=\"hljs\"><code><div><span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">private</span> String <span class=\"hljs-title\">getRandomPassword</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">throws</span> Exception</span>{\n StringBuilder temp = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> StringBuilder();\n Random rad = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> Random(); <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 使用 java.util.Random，非 SecureRandom</span>\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">int</span> i=<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>;i&lt;<span class=\"hljs-number\">6</span>;i++) {\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">int</span> a = rad.nextInt(<span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>);\n temp.append(a);\n }\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> temp.toString();\n}\n</div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>漏洞成因分析：</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-mermaid\"><div class=\"mermaid\">sequenceDiagram\n participant Attacker as 攻击者\n participant SV as NpSubscriberOpenSVC\n participant RNG as java.util.Random\n participant DB as 用户表\n \n Note over Attacker,DB: 漏洞利用流程 - 预测随机密码\n Attacker->>SV: 创建账户(NEED_PASSWORD=0)\n SV->>RNG: new Random()\n RNG-->>SV: 生成种子(基于系统时间)\n SV->>RNG: nextInt(10) x 6次\n RNG-->>SV: 返回6位随机数(如 482913)\n SV->>DB: INSERT 用户(密码=482913)\n Note over Attacker: 获取到密码 482913 和时间戳\n Attacker->>Attacker: 反推 Random 种子\n Attacker->>Attacker: 预测同一时段其他用户的密码\n Note over Attacker: 可批量预测新生成用户的密码\n</div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>复现步骤：</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>配置系统 <code>NEED_PASSWORD=0</code>（随机密码模式）</li>\n<li>连续创建多个开户，记录每个账户的随机密码和创建时间</li>\n<li>使用 <code>java.util.Random</code> 的种子还原算法，根据已知密码反推种子</li>\n<li>预测同一时间段内其他新生成账户的密码</li>\n<li>使用预测的密码尝试登录验证</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>预期结果：</strong> 随机密码应使用密码学安全的随机数生成器，不可被预测</p>\n<p><strong>实际结果：</strong> 使用 <code>java.util.Random</code>，密码可被推算</p>\n<p><strong>修复建议：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>代码层面：</strong> 将 <code>java.util.Random</code> 替换为 <code>java.security.SecureRandom</code>：</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"hljs\"><code><div><span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">private</span> String <span class=\"hljs-title\">getRandomPassword</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">throws</span> Exception</span>{\n StringBuilder temp = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> StringBuilder();\n SecureRandom rad = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> SecureRandom();\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">int</span> i=<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>;i&lt;<span class=\"hljs-number\">6</span>;i++) {\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">int</span> a = rad.nextInt(<span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>);\n temp.append(a);\n }\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> temp.toString();\n}\n</div></code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>代码层面：</strong> 使用 <code>ThreadLocalRandom.current()</code> 作为替代方案（Java 7+）</li>\n<li><strong>架构层面：</strong> 随机密码应通过短信下发，而非仅存储在系统中</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"28-%E7%AD%BE%E8%AE%A2%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B---%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3%E9%9D%9E%E5%B9%82%E7%AD%89%E5%8F%AF%E8%A2%AB%E6%BB%A5%E7%94%A8\">2.8 签订协议流程 - 协议生成接口非幂等可被滥用</h3>\n<p><strong>漏洞类型：</strong> 业务流程绕过/参数重放</p>\n<p><strong>风险等级：</strong> 中危</p>\n<p><strong>漏洞描述：</strong>\n<code>sendEpaperPre</code> 接口每次调用都会生成新的 <code>PRE_INTACT_ID</code>（协议流水号），且无调用频率限制。攻击者可重复调用该接口，大量生成无效协议记录，消耗无纸化系统资源，甚至可能通过大量协议请求触发外部无纸化系统的拒绝服务。</p>\n<p><strong>关键代码片段：</strong></p>\n<p><code>NpSubscriberOpen.java:187-216</code></p>\n<pre class=\"hljs\"><code><div><span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">sendEpaperPre</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">(IRequestCycle clcle)</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">throws</span> Exception\n</span>{\n IData param = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.getData();\n IData acctInfo = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.getData(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"acctinfo\"</span>);\n param.putAll(acctInfo);\n IDataset offerList = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> DatasetList(param.getString(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"SELECTED_OFFER_VALUE\"</span>));\n <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// ... 组装参数</span>\n param.put(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"OFFERS\"</span>, offerList);\n param.put(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"ROUTE_CODE\"</span>,<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.getVisit().getLoginEparchyCode());\n param.put(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"BUSI_ITEM_CODE\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"40\"</span>);\n\n IData result = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.call(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"OrderCentre.person.IElecSV.getPreEpaperOper\"</span>, param);\n <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 每次调用都生成新的 PRE_INTACT_ID</span>\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(DataUtil.isNotEmpty(result)){\n setAjax(result);\n }\n}\n</div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>漏洞成因分析：</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-mermaid\"><div class=\"mermaid\">sequenceDiagram\n participant Attacker as 攻击者\n participant API as sendEpaperPre\n participant ElecSV as getPreEpaperOper\n participant Paper as 无纸化系统\n participant DB as 数据库\n \n Note over Attacker,DB: 漏洞利用流程 - 协议接口滥用\n loop 重复调用(1000次)\n Attacker->>API: sendEpaperPre(表单数据)\n API->>ElecSV: getPreEpaperOper\n ElecSV->>Paper: 生成协议XML\n Paper-->>ElecSV: PRE_INTACT_ID + XML\n ElecSV->>DB: INSERT 协议记录\n ElecSV-->>API: 返回结果\n API-->>Attacker: 新的 PRE_INTACT_ID\n end\n Note over DB: 产生1000条无效协议记录\n Note over Paper: 无纸化系统资源被大量消耗\n</div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>复现步骤：</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>登录系统，进入携转用户开户页面</li>\n<li>填写基本表单信息（不需要完整填写）</li>\n<li>使用 Burp Intruder 或脚本循环调用 <code>sendEpaperPre</code> 接口</li>\n<li>观察响应中每次返回不同的 <code>PRE_INTACT_ID</code></li>\n<li>检查数据库中协议记录表的增长情况</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>预期结果：</strong> 同一用户/号码在短时间内应限制协议生成频率</p>\n<p><strong>实际结果：</strong> 无频率限制，可无限生成协议记录</p>\n<p><strong>修复建议：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>代码层面：</strong> 增加频率限制：同一 ACCESS_NUM 在 N 分钟内只能生成一次协议</li>\n<li><strong>代码层面：</strong> 在调用 <code>getPreEpaperOper</code> 前检查是否已存在未使用的协议记录</li>\n<li><strong>架构层面：</strong> 引入 API 限流（如令牌桶算法），限制单用户调用频率</li>\n<li><strong>配置层面：</strong> 定期清理未使用的协议记录</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"29-%E5%80%BC%E7%8F%AD%E9%95%BF%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81%E7%A0%81%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B---%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81%E7%A0%81%E6%97%A0%E9%A2%91%E7%8E%87%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E5%92%8C%E9%87%8D%E8%AF%95%E9%94%81%E5%AE%9A\">2.9 值班长验证码流程 - 验证码无频率限制和重试锁定</h3>\n<p><strong>漏洞类型：</strong> 验证码与限流/无操作频率限制</p>\n<p><strong>风险等级：</strong> 中危</p>\n<p><strong>漏洞描述：</strong>\n<code>dealYzm</code> 接口处理值班长验证码的发送和校验，但无任何频率限制。攻击者可：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>对同一值班长工号无限次发送验证码，造成短信轰炸</li>\n<li>对验证码无限次尝试，通过暴力破解获取正确验证码（6位数字验证码仅有100万种组合）</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>关键代码片段：</strong></p>\n<p><code>NpSubscriberOpen.java:250-268</code></p>\n<pre class=\"hljs\"><code><div><span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">dealYzm</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">(IRequestCycle cycle)</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">throws</span> Exception\n</span>{\n IData data = getData();\n IData result = ServiceCaller.call(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"OrderCentre.person.ISubscriberOpenSV.dealYzm\"</span>, data ,cycle.getRequestContext().getRequest());\n setAjax(result.getDataset(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"DATAS\"</span>));\n\n <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 审计日志</span>\n IData cond = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> DataMap();\n cond.put(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"OPERATOR_ID\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.getVisit().getStaffId());\n cond.put(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"OPER_MOD\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"值班长授权\"</span>);\n cond.put(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"OPER_TYPE\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"CHK\"</span>);\n String msg = <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"PRIV_VERIFY[NPOPENTAKEACTIVE:\"</span>+PrivCheck.checkDomPermission(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.getVisit().getStaffId(),<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"NPOPENTAKEACTIVE\"</span>)+<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"];\"</span>;\n cond.put(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"OPER_DESC\"</span>, msg+<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"授权参数：\"</span>+data.toString());\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.call(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"CustomerCentre.common.IOperLogSV.addOperLog\"</span>, cond);\n}\n</div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>漏洞成因分析：</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-mermaid\"><div class=\"mermaid\">sequenceDiagram\n participant Attacker as 攻击者\n participant API as dealYzm\n participant SMS as 短信网关\n participant DB as 验证码表\n \n Note over Attacker,DB: 漏洞利用流程 - 短信轰炸 + 验证码爆破\n \n rect rgb(255, 200, 200)\n Note over Attacker,SMS: 攻击1: 短信轰炸\n loop 1000次\n Attacker->>API: dealYzm(ACTION=SEND_YZM, MANAGER_STAFF=目标工号)\n API->>SMS: 发送验证码短信\n SMS-->>Attacker: 目标手机收到骚扰短信\n end\n end\n \n rect rgb(200, 200, 255)\n Note over Attacker,DB: 攻击2: 验证码暴力破解\n loop 1000000次(000000-999999)\n Attacker->>API: dealYzm(ACTION=VALID_YZM, SMS_NUMBER=猜测值)\n API->>DB: 校验验证码\n DB-->>API: 匹配/不匹配\n API-->>Attacker: 校验结果\n end\n end\n</div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>复现步骤：</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>登录系统，进入携转用户开户页面</li>\n<li>使用 Burp Intruder 对 <code>dealYzm</code> 接口进行短信轰炸测试：\n<ul>\n<li>固定 <code>MANAGER_STAFF</code> 为目标值班长工号</li>\n<li>设置 <code>ACTION=SEND_YZM</code></li>\n<li>循环发送100次</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>观察目标值班长手机是否收到大量验证码短信</li>\n<li>对验证码校验接口进行暴力破解测试：\n<ul>\n<li>固定 <code>ACTION=VALID_YZM</code></li>\n<li>遍历 <code>SMS_NUMBER</code> 从 000000 到 999999</li>\n<li>观察是否能在合理时间内破解验证码</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>预期结果：</strong> 验证码发送应有频率限制（如每分钟1次、每天10次），校验失败应有锁定机制（如连续5次失败锁定15分钟）</p>\n<p><strong>实际结果：</strong> 无频率限制，无失败锁定，可短信轰炸和暴力破解</p>\n<p><strong>验证请求示例：</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"hljs\"><code><div># 短信轰炸\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">POST</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">/person/cs/npsubscriberopen/NpSubscriberOpen.app?service=listener/dealYzm</span> HTTP/1.1\n<span class=\"hljs-attribute\">Host</span>: crm.example.com\n<span class=\"hljs-attribute\">Cookie</span>: JSESSIONID=xxx\n<span class=\"hljs-attribute\">Content-Type</span>: application/x-www-form-urlencoded\n\n<span class=\"dts\">MANAGER_STAFF=<span class=\"hljs-number\">12345678</span><span class=\"hljs-variable\">&amp;</span>ACCESS_NUM=<span class=\"hljs-number\">13800138000</span><span class=\"hljs-variable\">&amp;</span>ACTION=SEND_YZM\n\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\"># 验证码爆破</span>\nPOST <span class=\"hljs-meta-keyword\">/person/</span>cs<span class=\"hljs-meta-keyword\">/npsubscriberopen/</span>NpSubscriberOpen.app?service=listener/dealYzm HTTP/<span class=\"hljs-number\">1.1</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-symbol\">Host:</span> crm.example.com\n<span class=\"hljs-symbol\">Cookie:</span> JSESSIONID=xxx\nContent-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded\n\nSMS_NUMBER=<span class=\"hljs-number\">000000</span><span class=\"hljs-variable\">&amp;</span>MANAGER_STAFF=<span class=\"hljs-number\">12345678</span><span class=\"hljs-variable\">&amp;</span>ACCESS_NUM=<span class=\"hljs-number\">13800138000</span><span class=\"hljs-variable\">&amp;</span>ACTION=VALID_YZM\n</span></div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>修复建议：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>代码层面：</strong> 验证码发送频率限制：同一值班长工号每分钟最多发送1次，每天最多10次</li>\n<li><strong>代码层面：</strong> 验证码校验失败锁定：连续5次校验失败，锁定该工号15分钟</li>\n<li><strong>代码层面：</strong> 验证码有效期限制：验证码生成后5分钟内有效，过期失效</li>\n<li><strong>架构层面：</strong> 引入短信网关级别的频率限制和防轰炸策略</li>\n<li><strong>配置层面：</strong> 记录所有验证码发送和校验操作到审计日志，异常行为触发告警</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"210-%E6%90%BA%E5%85%A5%E5%8F%B7%E7%A0%81%E6%A0%A1%E9%AA%8C%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B---%E4%B8%80%E8%AF%81%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%8D%E6%A3%80%E6%9F%A5%E4%BB%85%E8%A6%86%E7%9B%96%E8%AF%81%E4%BB%B6%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B0\">2.10 携入号码校验流程 - 一证多名检查仅覆盖证件类型0</h3>\n<p><strong>漏洞类型：</strong> 数据校验缺失/业务规则绕过</p>\n<p><strong>风险等级：</strong> 低危</p>\n<p><strong>漏洞描述：</strong>\n一证多名（一个证件号码对应多个姓名）检查仅在 <code>IDEN_TYPE_CODE=0</code> 或 <code>IDEN_TYPE_ID=10000000</code>（身份证）时执行。攻击者可通过使用其他证件类型（如护照、军官证等）绕过一证多名检查，用同一证件号码但以不同姓名注册多个账户。</p>\n<p><strong>关键代码片段：</strong></p>\n<p><code>NpSubscriberOpenSVC.java:185-197</code></p>\n<pre class=\"hljs\"><code><div><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(StringUtils.equals(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.getRequest().getString(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"IDEN_TYPE_CODE\"</span>), <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"0\"</span>) || \n StringUtils.equals(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.getRequest().getString(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"IDEN_TYPE_ID\"</span>), <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"10000000\"</span>)){\n ServiceRequest requestQ=<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> ServiceRequest();\n requestQ.setValue(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"IDEN_TYPE_ID\"</span>, request.getString(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"IDEN_TYPE_ID\"</span>));\n requestQ.setValue(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"IDEN_TYPE_CODE\"</span>, request.getString(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"IDEN_TYPE_CODE\"</span>));\n requestQ.setValue(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"IDEN_NR\"</span>,request.getString(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"IDEN_NR\"</span>));\n requestQ.setValue(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"PARTY_NAME\"</span>,request.getString(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"PARTY_NAME\"</span>));\n ServiceResponse info = CsfCaller.call(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"OrderCentre.person.ICustInfoOperateSV.checkIsOneCardManyNames\"</span>,requestQ);\n String psmanyNamesflag = info.getBody().getString(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"PSMANY_NAMESFLAG\"</span>);\n String detail = info.getBody().getString(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"PSMANY_DETAIL\"</span>);\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (StringUtils.equals(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"1\"</span>, psmanyNamesflag)) {\n CSBizException.bizerr(CustomerException.CRM_CUSTOMER_35, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"该证件号码存在一证多名...\"</span>);\n }\n}\n</div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>复现步骤：</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>使用身份证（IDEN_TYPE_CODE=0）以姓名&quot;张三&quot;注册一个账户</li>\n<li>使用护照（IDEN_TYPE_CODE=其他值）以相同证件号码但不同姓名&quot;李四&quot;尝试注册</li>\n<li>观察是否绕过一证多名检查</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>预期结果：</strong> 所有一证多名检查应覆盖所有证件类型</p>\n<p><strong>实际结果：</strong> 仅身份证类型执行一证多名检查</p>\n<p><strong>修复建议：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>代码层面：</strong> 移除证件类型限制，对所有证件类型执行一证多名检查</li>\n<li><strong>代码层面：</strong> 在 <code>checkIsOneCardManyNames</code> 服务中增加跨证件类型的关联检查</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"211-%E5%90%89%E7%A5%A5%E5%8F%B7%E7%A0%81%E6%9D%83%E9%99%90%E6%A0%A1%E9%AA%8C%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B---%E5%90%89%E7%A5%A5%E5%8F%B7%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97%E5%BC%82%E5%B8%B8%E8%A2%AB%E9%9D%99%E9%BB%98%E5%90%9E%E6%B2%A1\">2.11 吉祥号码权限校验流程 - 吉祥号操作日志异常被静默吞没</h3>\n<p><strong>漏洞类型：</strong> 信息泄露/审计缺失</p>\n<p><strong>风险等级：</strong> 低危</p>\n<p><strong>漏洞描述：</strong>\n<code>initIMPOWER</code> 方法中记录吉祥号操作日志的代码被包裹在空的 try-catch 块中，所有异常都被静默吞没。这意味着吉祥号码的操作日志可能记录失败而无人知晓，导致审计数据不完整，无法追溯吉祥号码的开户操作。</p>\n<p><strong>关键代码片段：</strong></p>\n<p><code>NpSubscriberOpen.java:282-291</code></p>\n<pre class=\"hljs\"><code><div><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">try</span> {\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(StringUtils.equals(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"1\"</span>, islucky)){\n IData log = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> DataMap();\n log.put(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"ACCESS_NUM\"</span>, param.get(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"ACCESS_NUM\"</span>));\n log.put(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"BUSI_ITEM_CODE\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.getBusiCode());\n log.put(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"LEVEL\"</span>, result1.getDataset(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"DATAS\"</span>).get(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"LEVEL_ID\"</span>).toString());\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">this</span>.call(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"BusiFrame.priv.ISecPrivOperSV.insertLuckyNumBusiLog\"</span>, log);\n }\n} <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">catch</span> (Exception e) {\n <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 空catch块 - 异常被静默吞没</span>\n}\n</div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>复现步骤：</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>模拟 <code>insertLuckyNumBusiLog</code> 服务不可用（如数据库连接失败）</li>\n<li>输入吉祥号码触发 <code>initIMPOWER</code></li>\n<li>检查吉祥号操作日志表，确认日志未记录</li>\n<li>检查系统日志，确认无任何错误信息</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>预期结果：</strong> 日志记录失败时应记录错误日志并告警</p>\n<p><strong>实际结果：</strong> 异常被静默吞没，无任何错误记录</p>\n<p><strong>修复建议：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>代码层面：</strong> 在 catch 块中记录错误日志：</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"hljs\"><code><div>} <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">catch</span> (Exception e) {\n logger.error(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"吉祥号码操作日志记录失败, ACCESS_NUM=\"</span> + param.get(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"ACCESS_NUM\"</span>), e);\n}\n</div></code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>架构层面：</strong> 日志记录应采用异步方式，避免影响主业务流程</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"%E4%B8%89%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1\">三、漏洞统计</h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:left\">风险等级</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:left\">数量</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:left\">漏洞编号</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">高危</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">4</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">VUL-001, VUL-002, VUL-003, VUL-004</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">中危</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">5</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">VUL-005, VUL-006, VUL-007, VUL-008, VUL-009</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">低危</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">2</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:left\">VUL-010, VUL-011</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"%E5%9B%9B%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D%E4%BC%98%E5%85%88%E7%BA%A7%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE\">四、修复优先级建议</h2>\n<h3 id=\"p0---%E7%AB%8B%E5%8D%B3%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D%E9%AB%98%E5%8D%B1\">P0 - 立即修复（高危）</h3>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>VUL-001 重复提交</strong>：增加幂等性控制，防止重复开户</li>\n<li><strong>VUL-003 吉祥号码验证码绕过</strong>：后端增加验证码状态校验</li>\n<li><strong>VUL-004 NP_VERIFY非原子删除</strong>：确保删除操作在事务最后执行</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"p1---%E4%B8%80%E5%91%A8%E5%86%85%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D%E9%AB%98%E5%8D%B1%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%B1\">P1 - 一周内修复（高危/中危）</h3>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li><strong>VUL-002 归属地硬编码绕过</strong>：移除IBOSS000硬编码豁免</li>\n<li><strong>VUL-005 营销权限绕过</strong>：修复副卡开户权限校验</li>\n<li><strong>VUL-009 验证码无限流</strong>：增加发送频率和失败锁定</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"p2---%E4%B8%A4%E5%91%A8%E5%86%85%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%B1%E4%BD%8E%E5%8D%B1\">P2 - 两周内修复（中危/低危）</h3>\n<ol start=\"7\">\n<li><strong>VUL-006 证件预占释放</strong>：完善异常处理中的预占释放</li>\n<li><strong>VUL-007 弱随机数</strong>：替换为SecureRandom</li>\n<li><strong>VUL-008 协议接口滥用</strong>：增加频率限制</li>\n<li><strong>VUL-010 一证多名检查</strong>：覆盖所有证件类型</li>\n<li><strong>VUL-011 日志异常吞没</strong>：增加错误日志记录</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"%E4%BA%94%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3%E9%9C%80%E8%A1%A5%E5%85%85\">五、[信息不足，需补充]</h2>\n<p>以下方面因代码或文档信息不足，无法进行完整分析，建议补充：</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>项目</th>\n<th>需要补充的信息</th>\n<th>可能影响的安全分析</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code>createNpSubscriber</code> 服务实现</td>\n<td>完整的开户核心逻辑代码，包括数据库事务边界、唯一约束定义</td>\n<td>无法确认重复提交是否会被数据库约束拦截</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>ResCall.checkNpSimCard</code> 实现</td>\n<td>SIM卡选占的具体实现，包括并发控制机制</td>\n<td>无法确认SIM卡并发选占是否存在竞态条件</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>ISubscriberOpenSV.dealYzm</code> 实现</td>\n<td>验证码生成、存储、校验的完整逻辑</td>\n<td>无法确认验证码的加密存储方式和校验逻辑</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>数据库表结构DDL</td>\n<td>用户表、账户表、携转关系表的完整定义，包括唯一约束和索引</td>\n<td>无法确认数据库层面的防护机制</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>前端 JS 完整代码</td>\n<td><code>npsubscriberopen.js</code> 和 <code>NpSubscriberOpenComp.js</code> 的完整实现</td>\n<td>无法确认前端是否存在额外的安全校验</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>会话管理机制</td>\n<td>用户认证和会话管理的实现方式</td>\n<td>无法分析会话固定/劫持风险</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>统一鉴权流程</td>\n<td><code>$.authUtil</code> 组件的完整鉴权流程</td>\n<td>无法分析统一鉴权场景下的安全风险</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>场景化融合组件</td>\n<td><code>$.FusionUtil.buildBusiData</code> 的详细实现</td>\n<td>无法分析场景化流程中的数据流转安全</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n</file>"}],"timestamp":1775814024730}}
{"type":"message","id":"03697fc5","parentId":"7a51ce53","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:40:55.271Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user sent me a file attachment - it's an HTML file that appears to be a security analysis report for a \"携转用户开户业务逻辑安全分析报告\" (Number Portability User Account Opening Business Logic Security Analysis Report). The report is about vulnerabilities in a telecom system's number portability (携号转网) account opening process.\n\nThe user sent this as a message attachment. They want me to look at this report. Let me acknowledge receipt and perhaps provide a summary or analysis of this report.\n\nThe report identifies 11 vulnerabilities in a telecom system's number portability account opening process. Let me summarize the key points.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到！这是一份**携转用户开户业务逻辑安全分析报告**，识别了 11 个安全漏洞。我来总结一下关键内容：\n\n---\n\n## 📊 漏洞概览\n\n| 风险等级 | 数量 | 代表漏洞 |\n|----------|------|---------|\n| 🔴 高危 | 4 | VUL-001~004 |\n| 🟡 中危 | 5 | VUL-005~009 |\n| 🟢 低危 | 2 | VUL-010~011 |\n\n---\n\n## 🔴 高危漏洞（4个）\n\n**VUL-001 — 开户提交接口重复提交（幂等性缺失）**\n- `onTradeSubmit` 无幂等性控制，攻击者重放请求可重复开户\n- 修复：加 Redis 去重 / 分布式锁 / 数据库唯一约束\n\n**VUL-002 — 携入号码归属地校验硬编码绕过**\n- 工号 `IBOSS000` 硬编码跳过归属地一致性校验，可跨地州开户\n- 修复：移除硬编码，改为权限配置表控制\n\n**VUL-003 — 吉祥号码验证码授权仅前端控制**\n- `yzmValidFlag` 仅存在前端 JS 变量，后端 `onTradeSubmit` 未校验\n- 攻击：直接改 JS 变量绕过验证码，为吉祥号开户\n- 修复：验证码状态存服务端 session/Redis\n\n**VUL-004 — NP_VERIFY 记录删除与开户非原子性**\n- 在开户**中间阶段**物理删除审核记录，后续失败时无法恢复，形成业务死锁\n- 修复：改物理删除为状态标记 `STATUS='USED'`，包裹数据库事务\n\n---\n\n## 🟡 中危漏洞（5个）\n\n**VUL-005 — 营销活动类型02权限校验可被 OPEN_TYPE=11 绕过**（副卡开户绕过权限）\n\n**VUL-006 — 证件预占释放条件不完整**（异常消息含\"证件号码被预占\"时不释放预占）\n\n**VUL-007 — 随机密码使用 `java.util.Random`（可预测）** → 应换 `SecureRandom`\n\n**VUL-008 — 协议生成接口非幂等，可无限滥用生成大量无效记录**\n\n**VUL-009 — 值班长验证码无频率限制和失败锁定**（可短信轰炸 + 6位验证码暴力破解）\n\n---\n\n## 🟢 低危（2个）\n\n**VUL-010 — 一证多名检查仅覆盖证件类型0**（身份证，其他证件类型可绕过）\n\n**VUL-011 — 吉祥号操作日志异常被空 catch 静默吞没**（审计缺失）\n\n---\n\n## 🛠️ 修复优先级建议\n\n| 优先级 | 修复时间 | 漏洞 |\n|--------|----------|------|\n| P0 | 立即修复 | VUL-001, VUL-003, VUL-004 |\n| P1 | 一周内 | VUL-002, VUL-005, VUL-009 |\n| P2 | 两周内 | VUL-006, VUL-007, VUL-008, VUL-010, VUL-011 |\n\n---\n\n这是一份非常专业的安全审计报告，格式规范（每条漏洞含：类型/等级/描述/代码片段/Mermaid时序图/复现步骤/修复建议），可以作为 AI 代码扫描插件的一个很好的落地场景示例。\n\n你是想把这个报告集成到插件里展示，还是有其他用途？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":148862,"output":858,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":149720,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775814024763,"responseId":"chatcmpl-0d021a59-6ce1-4ee3-aaa4-d0c77ba307cc"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6a131e4e","parentId":"03697fc5","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:40:57.460Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[media attached: /home/gem/workspace/agent/media/inbound/æ_ºè½_ç_æ_å¼_æ_ä_å_é_è¾_è_æ_æ_æ---2ccbc9bb-32ad-4e9f-b436-a12d315b36ea (text/html) | /home/gem/workspace/agent/media/inbound/æ_ºè½_ç_æ_å¼_æ_ä_å_é_è¾_è_æ_æ_æ---2ccbc9bb-32ad-4e9f-b436-a12d315b36ea]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Avoid absolute paths (MEDIA:/...) and ~ paths — they are blocked for security. Keep caption in the text body.\nSystem: [2026-04-10 17:40:56 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a [msg:om_x100b52b816afa884c4f199d86afc13e, file, 1 attachment(s)]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52b816afa884c4f199d86afc13e\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-10 17:40 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a\"\n}\n```\n\n[Feishu ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a Fri 2026-04-10 17:40 GMT+8] ou_0b09d73328aba9ee56b8bb871bf3fb3a: [File: /home/gem/workspace/agent/media/inbound/æ_ºè½_ç_æ_å¼_æ_ä_å_é_è¾_è_æ_æ_æ---2ccbc9bb-32ad-4e9f-b436-a12d315b36ea]\n\n<file name=\"æ_ºè½_ç_æ_å¼_æ_ä_å_é_è¾_è_æ_æ_æ---2ccbc9bb-32ad-4e9f-b436-a12d315b36ea\" mime=\"text/plain\">\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n<title>携转用户开户业务逻辑说明文档.md</title>\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-type\" content=\"text/html;charset=UTF-8\">\n\n<style>\n/* https://github.com/microsoft/vscode/blob/master/extensions/markdown-language-features/media/markdown.css */\n/*---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n * Copyright (c) Microsoft Corporation. All rights reserved.\n * Licensed under the MIT License. See License.txt in the project root for license information.\n *--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/\n\nbody {\n font-family: var(--vscode-markdown-font-family, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe WPC\", \"Segoe UI\", \"Ubuntu\", \"Droid Sans\", sans-serif);\n font-size: var(--vscode-markdown-font-size, 14px);\n padding: 0 26px;\n line-height: var(--vscode-markdown-line-height, 22px);\n word-wrap: break-word;\n}\n\n#code-csp-warning {\n position: fixed;\n top: 0;\n right: 0;\n color: white;\n margin: 16px;\n text-align: center;\n font-size: 12px;\n font-family: sans-serif;\n background-color:#444444;\n cursor: pointer;\n padding: 6px;\n box-shadow: 1px 1px 1px rgba(0,0,0,.25);\n}\n\n#code-csp-warning:hover {\n text-decoration: none;\n background-color:#007acc;\n box-shadow: 2px 2px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.25);\n}\n\nbody.scrollBeyondLastLine {\n margin-bottom: calc(100vh - 22px);\n}\n\nbody.showEditorSelection .code-line {\n position: relative;\n}\n\nbody.showEditorSelection .code-active-line:before,\nbody.showEditorSelection .code-line:hover:before {\n content: \"\";\n display: block;\n position: absolute;\n top: 0;\n left: -12px;\n height: 100%;\n}\n\nbody.showEditorSelection li.code-active-line:before,\nbody.showEditorSelection li.code-line:hover:before {\n left: -30px;\n}\n\n.vscode-light.showEditorSelection .code-active-line:before {\n border-left: 3px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n}\n\n.vscode-light.showEditorSelection .code-line:hover:before {\n border-left: 3px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.40);\n}\n\n.vscode-light.showEditorSelection .code-line .code-line:hover:before {\n border-left: none;\n}\n\n.vscode-dark.showEditorSelection .code-active-line:before {\n border-left: 3px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);\n}\n\n.vscode-dark.showEditorSelection .code-line:hover:before {\n border-left: 3px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.60);\n}\n\n.vscode-dark.showEditorSelection .code-line .code-line:hover:before {\n border-left: none;\n}\n\n.vscode-high-contrast.showEditorSelection .code-active-line:before {\n border-left: 3px solid rgba(255, 160, 0, 0.7);\n}\n\n.vscode-high-contrast.showEditorSelection .code-line:hover:before {\n border-left: 3px solid rgba(255, 160, 0, 1);\n}\n\n.vscode-high-contrast.showEditorSelection .code-line .code-line:hover:before {\n border-left: none;\n}\n\nimg {\n max-width: 100%;\n max-height: 100%;\n}\n\na {\n text-decoration: none;\n}\n\na:hover {\n text-decoration: underline;\n}\n\na:focus,\ninput:focus,\nselect:focus,\ntextarea:focus {\n outline: 1px solid -webkit-focus-ring-color;\n outline-offset: -1px;\n}\n\nhr {\n border: 0;\n height: 2px;\n border-bottom: 2px solid;\n}\n\nh1 {\n padding-bottom: 0.3em;\n line-height: 1.2;\n border-bottom-width: 1px;\n border-bottom-style: solid;\n}\n\nh1, h2, h3 {\n font-weight: normal;\n}\n\ntable {\n border-collapse: collapse;\n}\n\ntable > thead > tr > th {\n text-align: left;\n border-bottom: 1px solid;\n}\n\ntable > thead > tr > th,\ntable > thead > tr > td,\ntable > tbody > tr > th,\ntable > tbody > tr > td {\n padding: 5px 10px;\n}\n\ntable > tbody > tr + tr > td {\n border-top: 1px solid;\n}\n\nblockquote {\n margin: 0 7px 0 5px;\n padding: 0 16px 0 10px;\n border-left-width: 5px;\n border-left-style: solid;\n}\n\ncode {\n font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, \"Droid Sans Mono\", \"Courier New\", monospace, \"Droid Sans Fallback\";\n font-size: 1em;\n line-height: 1.357em;\n}\n\nbody.wordWrap pre {\n white-space: pre-wrap;\n}\n\npre:not(.hljs),\npre.hljs code > div {\n padding: 16px;\n border-radius: 3px;\n overflow: auto;\n}\n\npre code {\n color: var(--vscode-editor-foreground);\n tab-size: 4;\n}\n\n/** Theming */\n\n.vscode-light pre {\n background-color: rgba(220, 220, 220, 0.4);\n}\n\n.vscode-dark pre {\n background-color: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.4);\n}\n\n.vscode-high-contrast pre {\n background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\n}\n\n.vscode-high-contrast h1 {\n border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\n}\n\n.vscode-light table > thead > tr > th {\n border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.69);\n}\n\n.vscode-dark table > thead > tr > th {\n border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.69);\n}\n\n.vscode-light h1,\n.vscode-light hr,\n.vscode-light table > tbody > tr + tr > td {\n border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);\n}\n\n.vscode-dark h1,\n.vscode-dark hr,\n.vscode-dark table > tbody > tr + tr > td {\n border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);\n}\n\n</style>\n\n<style>\n/* Tomorrow Theme */\n/* http://jmblog.github.com/color-themes-for-google-code-highlightjs */\n/* Original theme - https://github.com/chriskempson/tomorrow-theme */\n\n/* Tomorrow Comment */\n.hljs-comment,\n.hljs-quote {\n color: #8e908c;\n}\n\n/* Tomorrow Red */\n.hljs-variable,\n.hljs-template-variable,\n.hljs-tag,\n.hljs-name,\n.hljs-selector-id,\n.hljs-selector-class,\n.hljs-regexp,\n.hljs-deletion {\n color: #c82829;\n}\n\n/* Tomorrow Orange */\n.hljs-number,\n.hljs-built_in,\n.hljs-builtin-name,\n.hljs-literal,\n.hljs-type,\n.hljs-params,\n.hljs-meta,\n.hljs-link {\n color: #f5871f;\n}\n\n/* Tomorrow Yellow */\n.hljs-attribute {\n color: #eab700;\n}\n\n/* Tomorrow Green */\n.hljs-string,\n.hljs-symbol,\n.hljs-bullet,\n.hljs-addition {\n color: #718c00;\n}\n\n/* Tomorrow Blue */\n.hljs-title,\n.hljs-section {\n color: #4271ae;\n}\n\n/* Tomorrow Purple */\n.hljs-keyword,\n.hljs-selector-tag {\n color: #8959a8;\n}\n\n.hljs {\n display: block;\n overflow-x: auto;\n color: #4d4d4c;\n padding: 0.5em;\n}\n\n.hljs-emphasis {\n font-style: italic;\n}\n\n.hljs-strong {\n font-weight: bold;\n}\n</style>\n\n<style>\n/*\n * Markdown PDF CSS\n */\n\n body {\n font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe WPC\", \"Segoe UI\", \"Ubuntu\", \"Droid Sans\", sans-serif, \"Meiryo\";\n padding: 0 12px;\n}\n\npre {\n background-color: #f8f8f8;\n border: 1px solid #cccccc;\n border-radius: 3px;\n overflow-x: auto;\n white-space: pre-wrap;\n overflow-wrap: break-word;\n}\n\npre:not(.hljs) {\n padding: 23px;\n line-height: 19px;\n}\n\nblockquote {\n background: rgba(127, 127, 127, 0.1);\n border-color: rgba(0, 122, 204, 0.5);\n}\n\n.emoji {\n height: 1.4em;\n}\n\ncode {\n font-size: 14px;\n line-height: 19px;\n}\n\n/* for inline code */\n:not(pre):not(.hljs) > code {\n color: #C9AE75; /* Change the old color so it seems less like an error */\n font-size: inherit;\n}\n\n/* Page Break : use <div class=\"page\"/> to insert page break\n-------------------------------------------------------- */\n.page {\n page-break-after: always;\n}\n\n</style>\n\n<script src=\"https://unpkg.com/mermaid/dist/mermaid.min.js\"></script>\n</head>\n<body>\n <script>\n mermaid.initialize({\n startOnLoad: true,\n theme: document.body.classList.contains('vscode-dark') || document.body.classList.contains('vscode-high-contrast')\n ? 'dark'\n : 'default'\n });\n </script>\n<h1 id=\"%E6%90%BA%E8%BD%AC%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E5%BC%80%E6%88%B7-%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3\">携转用户开户 业务逻辑说明文档</h1>\n<h2 id=\"%E4%B8%80%E6%A6%82%E8%BF%B0\">一、概述</h2>\n<p><strong>页面功能：</strong> 携号转网用户开户页面，用于营业厅工作人员为从其他运营商携入的用户办理新开户业务。核心业务目标包括：携入号码校验、SIM卡读写、客户信息采集、套餐活动选择、无纸化协议签订、携转用户开户创建。</p>\n<p><strong>业务角色：</strong> 营业厅工作人员</p>\n<p><strong>技术栈：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>前端：Tapestry Web框架 + jQuery + 自定义AJAX封装 + CSSubmit提交组件 + 场景化融合组件($.NpSubscriberOpen)</li>\n<li>后端：Java 1.8 + AppFrame框架 + this.call RPC调用</li>\n<li>硬件交互：OCX控件（IE浏览器）/ H5写卡系统用于SIM卡读写</li>\n<li>外部系统：产品中心(UnifyProductCentre)、客户中心、号卡系统、无纸化系统</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"%E4%BA%8C%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%E6%80%BB%E8%A7%88\">二、业务流程总览</h2>\n<h3 id=\"21-%E4%B8%BB%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%E6%97%B6%E5%BA%8F%E5%9B%BE\">2.1 主流程时序图</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-mermaid\"><div class=\"mermaid\">sequenceDiagram\n participant User as 营业厅工作人员\n participant FE as 前端页面\n participant Page as NpSubscriberOpen\n participant OpenSV as INpSubscriberOpenOperateSV\n participant ProdSV as UnifyProductCentre服务\n participant ElecSV as IElecSV\n participant NumSV as INumberIntfQuerySV\n participant DB as 数据库\n participant HW as 读卡器硬件\n\n Note over User,DB: 主流程：携号转网用户开户\n\n User->>FE: 输入携入号码\n FE->>Page: checkAccessNum ACCESS_NUM NP_BACK\n Page->>OpenSV: checkAccessNum\n OpenSV->>DB: SELECT 携转用户表 号码资源表\n DB-->>OpenSV: ASP DAY_NUM NP_BACK PARTY_NAME IDEN_TYPE_CODE IDEN_NR\n OpenSV-->>Page: 携转数据\n Page-->>FE: ASP DAY_NUM NP_BACK PARTY_NAME等\n FE->>FE: 填充客户信息 CHECK_RESULT_CODE=0\n\n FE->>Page: queryTodayOpenCountAndNotice IDEN_TYPE_CODE IDEN_NR\n Page->>Page: 查询当日开户次数\n Page-->>FE: NOTICE_TAG NOTICE_MSG\n alt NOTICE_TAG == 1\n FE-->>User: 风险提示\n end\n\n alt USIN_WRITE_CARD_NEW == 1\n User->>FE: 点击 读卡\n FE->>FE: beforeReadCard 校验\n FE->>HW: OCX/H5 读卡\n HW-->>FE: ICCID IS_WRITED\n FE->>FE: afterReadCard 校验IS_WRITED\n FE->>Page: checkIccId ACCESS_NUM ICC_ID\n Page->>OpenSV: checkNpIccId\n OpenSV->>DB: SELECT SIM卡资源表\n OpenSV-->>Page: 校验结果\n Page-->>FE: 校验通过\n FE->>FE: CHECK_RESULT_CODE=1\n\n User->>FE: 点击 写卡\n FE->>FE: beforeWriteCard 校验\n FE->>HW: OCX/H5 写卡\n HW-->>FE: ICCID\n FE->>FE: afterWriteCard 设置ICC_ID并校验\n end\n\n User->>FE: 点击 选择套餐\n FE->>FE: openOffer 打开套餐弹窗\n Note over FE: 用户在弹窗中选择套餐 回调getOfferSubmitParams\n FE->>OfferHandler: getOffer OFFER_ID\n OfferHandler-->>FE: offerName\n FE->>FE: 存储SELECTED_OFFER_VALUE\n\n User->>FE: 点击 新入网活动\n FE->>FE: openActive 打开活动弹窗\n Note over FE: 用户在弹窗中选择活动 回调getActiveSubmitParams\n FE->>Page: checkSaleActiveFee OFFER_ID\n Page->>ProdSV: queryPriceFeeByOfferIdForRes\n ProdSV-->>Page: FEE\n Page-->>FE: FEE\n FE->>OfferHandler: getOffer OFFER_ID\n OfferHandler-->>FE: offerName\n FE->>FE: 存储SELECTED_ACTIVE_VALUE\n\n User->>FE: 点击 签订协议\n FE->>FE: sendEpaperPre 全面校验\n FE->>Page: sendEpaperPre 表单数据\n Page->>ElecSV: getPreEpaperOper\n ElecSV-->>Page: PRE_INTACT_ID EPAPER_XML_PRE\n Page-->>FE: 协议流水号\n FE->>FE: 启动无纸化协议签署\n\n User->>FE: 点击 提交\n FE->>FE: submitBeforeCheck 全面校验\n FE->>FE: checkHasActive 校验套餐关联活动\n FE->>FE: $.cssubmit.submitTrade 提交业务\n FE->>Page: onTradeSubmit 全部表单数据\n Page->>OpenSV: createNpSubscriber\n OpenSV->>DB: INSERT 用户表 账户表 订购表 携转关系表\n DB-->>OpenSV: TRADE_ID\n OpenSV-->>Page: 开户成功\n Page-->>FE: 开户完成\n</div></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"22-%E4%B8%BB%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E\">2.2 主流程步骤说明</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>步骤</th>\n<th>用户操作</th>\n<th>前端函数</th>\n<th>后端接口</th>\n<th>数据变化</th>\n<th>下一步依赖</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>输入携入号码点击校验</td>\n<td>checkAccessNum()</td>\n<td>POST ACTION=checkAccessNum -&gt; INpSubscriberOpenOperateSV.checkAccessNum</td>\n<td>查询携转数据 填充客户信息</td>\n<td>CHECK_RESULT_CODE=0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>风险提醒</td>\n<td>queryTodayOpenCountAndNotice()</td>\n<td>POST ACTION=queryTodayOpenCountAndNotice -&gt; ICustInfoOperateSV.queryTodayOpenCountAndNotice</td>\n<td>查询当日开户次数</td>\n<td>风险提示</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>读卡获取SIM卡号</td>\n<td>beforeReadCard() -&gt; afterReadCard()</td>\n<td>硬件OCX/H5读卡</td>\n<td>获取ICCID</td>\n<td>无</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>SIM卡校验</td>\n<td>checkIccId()</td>\n<td>POST ACTION=checkIccId -&gt; INpSubscriberOpenOperateSV.checkNpIccId</td>\n<td>校验SIM卡有效性</td>\n<td>CHECK_RESULT_CODE=1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>写卡</td>\n<td>beforeWriteCard() -&gt; afterWriteCard()</td>\n<td>硬件OCX/H5写卡</td>\n<td>写入个性化数据</td>\n<td>ICC_ID设置</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>选择套餐</td>\n<td>openOffer() -&gt; getOfferSubmitParams()</td>\n<td>OfferHandler.getOffer</td>\n<td>无</td>\n<td>SELECTED_OFFER_VALUE</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>选择新入网活动</td>\n<td>openActive() -&gt; getActiveSubmitParams()</td>\n<td>POST ACTION=checkSaleActiveFee -&gt; UnifyProductCentre.offer.IPriceQueryFSV.queryPriceFeeByOfferIdForRes</td>\n<td>查询活动资费</td>\n<td>SELECTED_ACTIVE_VALUE</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>签订协议</td>\n<td>sendEpaperPre()</td>\n<td>POST ACTION=sendEpaperPre -&gt; IElecSV.getPreEpaperOper</td>\n<td>生成无纸化协议</td>\n<td>EPAPER_PRE_INTACT_ID</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9</td>\n<td>提交开户</td>\n<td>submitBeforeCheck() -&gt; $.cssubmit.submitTrade() -&gt; onTradeSubmit()</td>\n<td>POST onTradeSubmit -&gt; INpSubscriberOpenOperateSV.createNpSubscriber</td>\n<td>创建用户账户订购</td>\n<td>开户完成</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"%E4%B8%89%E5%AD%90%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%E8%AF%A6%E8%A7%A3\">三、子业务流程详解</h2>\n<h3 id=\"31-%E5%AD%90%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%E4%B8%80%E6%90%BA%E5%85%A5%E5%8F%B7%E7%A0%81%E6%A0%A1%E9%AA%8C\">3.1 子流程一：携入号码校验</h3>\n<p><strong>业务描述：</strong> 校验携入号码的有效性，从携转系统获取号码的携出运营商信息(ASP)、快速携回标记(NP_BACK)、以及审核通过的客户信息（姓名、证件类型、证件号码）。</p>\n<p><strong>时序图：</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-mermaid\"><div class=\"mermaid\">sequenceDiagram\n participant User as 工作人员\n participant FE as 前端\n participant Page as NpSubscriberOpen\n participant OpenSV as INpSubscriberOpenOperateSV\n participant DB as 携转用户表\n\n User->>FE: 输入携入号码 勾选快速携回\n FE->>FE: 校验集团编码(OPEN_TYPE==12时)\n FE->>FE: 校验代理商(代理商开户时)\n FE->>Page: checkAccessNum ACCESS_NUM NP_BACK AGENT_DEPART_ID EC_GROUP_ID\n activate Page\n Page->>OpenSV: checkAccessNum ACCESS_NUM NP_BACK AGENT_DEPART_ID EC_GROUP_ID\n activate OpenSV\n OpenSV->>DB: SELECT 携转用户表 号码资源表\n DB-->>OpenSV: ASP DAY_NUM NP_BACK PARTY_NAME IDEN_TYPE_CODE IDEN_NR\n OpenSV-->>Page: 携转数据\n deactivate OpenSV\n Page-->>FE: ASP DAY_NUM NP_BACK PARTY_NAME IDEN_TYPE_CODE IDEN_NR\n deactivate Page\n\n FE->>FE: 填充PARTY_NAME IDEN_TYPE_CODE IDEN_NR\n FE->>FE: CHECK_RESULT_CODE = 0\n\n FE->>Page: queryTodayOpenCountAndNotice IDEN_TYPE_CODE IDEN_NR\n activate Page\n Page->>CustSV: queryTodayOpenCountAndNotice\n CustSV-->>Page: NOTICE_TAG NOTICE_MSG\n Page-->>FE: NOTICE_TAG NOTICE_MSG\n deactivate Page\n\n alt NOTICE_TAG == 1\n FE-->>User: 风险提示 NOTICE_MSG\n end\n</div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>调用链详情：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>前端：<code>checkAccessNum()</code> -&gt; 校验集团编码/代理商/号码格式 -&gt; <code>$.ajax.submit(null, &quot;checkAccessNum&quot;, param, &quot;&quot;, ...)</code></li>\n<li>后端接口：<code>NpSubscriberOpen.checkAccessNum(IRequestCycle)</code></li>\n<li>业务层：<code>this.call(&quot;OrderCentre.person.INpSubscriberOpenOperateSV.checkAccessNum&quot;)</code></li>\n<li>数据库：携转用户表（SELECT）、号码资源表（SELECT）</li>\n<li>后续调用：<code>queryTodayOpenCountAndNotice()</code> -&gt; <code>this.call(&quot;OrderCentre.person.ICustInfoOperateSV.queryTodayOpenCountAndNotice&quot;)</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>关键字段：</strong></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>层级</th>\n<th>输入字段</th>\n<th>输出字段</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>前端</td>\n<td>ACCESS_NUM, NP_BACK, AGENT_DEPART_ID, EC_GROUP_ID</td>\n<td>ASP, DAY_NUM, NP_BACK, PARTY_NAME, IDEN_TYPE_CODE, IDEN_NR</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>后端</td>\n<td>ACCESS_NUM, NP_BACK, AGENT_DEPART_ID, EC_GROUP_ID</td>\n<td>ASP(携出运营商), DAY_NUM(携出天数), NP_BACK(快速携回标记), PARTY_NAME, IDEN_TYPE_CODE, IDEN_NR</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>数据库</td>\n<td>ACCESS_NUM</td>\n<td>携转用户记录 号码资源记录</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><strong>异常处理：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>携入号码为空或格式不正确：前端校验拦截</li>\n<li>集团编码为空（OPEN_TYPE==12）：前端提示拦截</li>\n<li>代理商未选择（代理商开户时）：前端提示拦截</li>\n<li>携转号码不存在：后端返回错误</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"32-%E5%AD%90%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%E4%BA%8Csim%E5%8D%A1%E8%AF%BB%E5%86%99%E4%B8%8E%E6%A0%A1%E9%AA%8C\">3.2 子流程二：SIM卡读写与校验</h3>\n<p><strong>业务描述：</strong> 通过读卡器硬件读取SIM卡信息（ICCID），校验SIM卡有效性，写卡时写入个性化数据。支持OCX控件和H5两种模式。</p>\n<p><strong>时序图：</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-mermaid\"><div class=\"mermaid\">sequenceDiagram\n participant User as 工作人员\n participant FE as 前端\n participant Page as NpSubscriberOpen\n participant OpenSV as INpSubscriberOpenOperateSV\n participant HW as 读卡器硬件\n\n Note over User,HW: 读卡流程\n\n User->>FE: 点击 读卡\n FE->>FE: beforeReadCard 校验ACCESS_NUM和CHECK_RESULT_CODE\n FE->>HW: OCX/H5 读卡\n HW-->>FE: ICCID IS_WRITED\n\n alt IS_WRITED == 1 成卡\n FE-->>User: 提示此卡为成卡 请选择白卡\n else IS_WRITED == 100 白卡已读\n FE->>FE: 设置ICC_ID\n FE->>Page: checkIccId ACCESS_NUM ICC_ID\n activate Page\n Page->>OpenSV: checkNpIccId\n activate OpenSV\n OpenSV->>DB: SELECT SIM卡资源表\n OpenSV-->>Page: 校验结果\n deactivate OpenSV\n Page-->>FE: 校验通过\n deactivate Page\n FE->>FE: CHECK_RESULT_CODE = 1\n end\n\n Note over User,HW: 写卡流程\n\n User->>FE: 点击 写卡\n FE->>FE: beforeWriteCard 校验\n FE->>HW: OCX/H5 写卡\n HW-->>FE: ICCID\n FE->>FE: afterWriteCard 设置ICC_ID并调用checkIccId\n</div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>调用链详情：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>读卡前端：<code>beforeReadCard()</code> -&gt; 校验 -&gt; OCX/H5读卡 -&gt; <code>afterReadCard(data)</code> -&gt; 判断IS_WRITED -&gt; <code>checkIccId(data)</code></li>\n<li>写卡前端：<code>beforeWriteCard()</code> -&gt; 校验 -&gt; OCX/H5写卡 -&gt; <code>afterWriteCard(data)</code> -&gt; <code>checkIccId(data)</code></li>\n<li>后端接口：<code>NpSubscriberOpen.checkIccId(IRequestCycle)</code></li>\n<li>业务层：<code>this.call(&quot;OrderCentre.person.INpSubscriberOpenOperateSV.checkNpIccId&quot;)</code></li>\n<li>数据库：SIM卡资源表（SELECT）</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>关键字段：</strong></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>层级</th>\n<th>输入字段</th>\n<th>输出字段</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>前端</td>\n<td>ACCESS_NUM, ICC_ID</td>\n<td>CHECK_RESULT_CODE(0=号码通过 1=SIM卡通过)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>后端</td>\n<td>ACCESS_NUM, ICC_ID</td>\n<td>校验结果</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><strong>异常处理：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>未校验号码就读卡：前端提示&quot;请先校验手机号码&quot;</li>\n<li>铁通号码（0开头）：前端提示&quot;铁通号码不支持白卡开户&quot;</li>\n<li>成卡（IS_WRITED=1）：前端提示&quot;此卡为成卡，请选择白卡并重新读卡&quot;</li>\n<li>号码校验未通过就校验SIM卡：前端提示&quot;手机号码校验未通过&quot;</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"33-%E5%AD%90%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%E4%B8%89%E5%A5%97%E9%A4%90%E5%92%8C%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9\">3.3 子流程三：套餐和活动选择</h3>\n<p><strong>业务描述：</strong> 选择携转用户开户套餐和新入网营销活动，涉及产品中心RPC调用查询活动资费。</p>\n<p><strong>时序图：</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-mermaid\"><div class=\"mermaid\">sequenceDiagram\n participant User as 工作人员\n participant FE as 前端\n participant Handler as OfferHandler\n participant Page as NpSubscriberOpen\n participant ProdSV as IPriceQueryFSV\n\n Note over User,ProdSV: 套餐选择\n\n User->>FE: 点击 选择套餐\n FE->>FE: openOffer 打开OfferListPopup弹窗\n Note over FE: 用户在弹窗中选择套餐 回调getOfferSubmitParams\n FE->>Handler: getOfferSubmitParams submitParam\n FE->>Handler: getOffer OFFER_ID\n activate Handler\n Handler->>Handler: 查询套餐详情\n Handler-->>FE: offerName\n deactivate Handler\n FE->>FE: 存储SELECTED_OFFER_NAME SELECTED_OFFER_VALUE MAIN_OFFER_ID\n FE->>FE: 判断OS_SEL_FLAG 显示国际短信语音提醒\n\n Note over User,ProdSV: 活动选择\n\n User->>FE: 点击 新入网活动\n FE->>FE: openActive 打开OfferListPopup弹窗\n Note over FE: 用户在弹窗中选择活动 回调getActiveSubmitParams\n\n FE->>Page: checkSaleActiveFee OFFER_ID\n activate Page\n Page->>ProdSV: queryPriceFeeByOfferIdForRes OFFER_ID MGMT_DISTRICT\n activate ProdSV\n ProdSV->>ProdSV: 查询活动资费\n ProdSV-->>Page: FEE\n deactivate ProdSV\n Page-->>FE: FEE\n deactivate Page\n\n FE->>Handler: getOffer OFFER_ID\n activate Handler\n Handler-->>FE: offerName\n deactivate Handler\n FE->>FE: 存储SELECTED_ACTIVE_NAME SELECTED_ACTIVE_VALUE\n</div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>调用链详情：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>套餐选择：<code>openOffer()</code> -&gt; <code>$.OfferListPopup.showOfferListPopup(param)</code> -&gt; 用户选择 -&gt; <code>getOfferSubmitParams(submitParam)</code> -&gt; <code>$.httphandler.get(&quot;com.ai.saas.component.offer.handler.OfferHandler&quot;, &quot;getOffer&quot;, ...)</code></li>\n<li>活动选择：<code>openActive()</code> -&gt; <code>$.OfferListPopup.showOfferListPopup(param)</code> -&gt; 用户选择 -&gt; <code>getActiveSubmitParams(submitParam)</code> -&gt; 先调用 <code>checkSaleActiveFee</code> 再调用 <code>OfferHandler.getOffer</code></li>\n<li>资费查询后端：<code>NpSubscriberOpen.checkSaleActiveFee(IRequestCycle)</code> -&gt; <code>this.call(&quot;UnifyProductCentre.offer.IPriceQueryFSV.queryPriceFeeByOfferIdForRes&quot;)</code></li>\n<li><strong>这是本页面调用 UnifyProductCentre 的地方</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>关键字段：</strong></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>层级</th>\n<th>输入字段</th>\n<th>输出字段</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>前端</td>\n<td>OFFER_ID(套餐/活动)</td>\n<td>SELECTED_OFFER_NAME, SELECTED_OFFER_VALUE(JSON), SELECTED_ACTIVE_NAME, SELECTED_ACTIVE_VALUE(JSON), MAIN_OFFER_ID</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>后端(资费查询)</td>\n<td>OFFER_ID, MGMT_DISTRICT</td>\n<td>FEE</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><strong>异常处理：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>活动资费查询失败：前端提示错误信息</li>\n<li>套餐有指定关联活动但未选择：弹窗提示&quot;该套餐有指定的开户营销关联关系&quot;</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"34-%E5%AD%90%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%E5%9B%9B%E7%AD%BE%E8%AE%A2%E6%97%A0%E7%BA%B8%E5%8C%96%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE\">3.4 子流程四：签订无纸化协议</h3>\n<p><strong>业务描述：</strong> 生成无纸化前置协议，获取协议流水号和XML报文，启动电子协议签署流程。</p>\n<p><strong>时序图：</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-mermaid\"><div class=\"mermaid\">sequenceDiagram\n participant User as 工作人员\n participant FE as 前端\n participant Page as NpSubscriberOpen\n participant ElecSV as IElecSV\n\n User->>FE: 点击 签订协议\n FE->>FE: sendEpaperPre 全面校验\n FE->>Page: sendEpaperPre 表单数据\n activate Page\n Page->>Page: 校验CHECK_RESULT_CODE 客户信息 套餐 快速携回等\n Page->>ElecSV: getPreEpaperOper 生成协议\n activate ElecSV\n ElecSV->>ElecSV: 组装协议模板 填充数据\n ElecSV-->>Page: PRE_INTACT_ID EPAPER_XML_PRE\n deactivate ElecSV\n Page-->>FE: PRE_INTACT_ID EPAPER_XML_PRE\n deactivate Page\n\n FE->>FE: 存储EPAPER_PRE_INTACT_ID\n FE->>FE: $.printMgr.startupEpaper 启动电子协议签署\n</div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>调用链详情：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>前端：<code>sendEpaperPre()</code> -&gt; 全面校验（号码校验、SIM卡校验、客户信息、经办人、套餐、用户类型、快速携回、指定活动关联）-&gt; <code>$.ajax.submit(conditionArea, &quot;sendEpaperPre&quot;, params, ...)</code></li>\n<li>后端接口：<code>NpSubscriberOpen.sendEpaperPre(IRequestCycle)</code></li>\n<li>业务层：<code>this.call(&quot;OrderCentre.person.IElecSV.getPreEpaperOper&quot;)</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>关键字段：</strong></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>层级</th>\n<th>输入字段</th>\n<th>输出字段</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>前端</td>\n<td>全部表单数据</td>\n<td>PRE_INTACT_ID, EPAPER_XML_PRE</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><strong>异常处理：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>携入号码校验未通过（CHECK_RESULT_CODE=-1）：前端提示拦截</li>\n<li>SIM卡校验未通过（CHECK_RESULT_CODE=0）：前端提示拦截</li>\n<li>未选择套餐：前端提示&quot;请选择套餐&quot;</li>\n<li>快速携回条件不满足：前端提示&quot;快速携回必须是移动携出号码&quot;或&quot;携出7天内才能办理&quot;</li>\n<li>套餐有指定关联活动：弹窗确认是否返回选择</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"35-%E5%AD%90%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%E4%BA%94%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E5%BC%80%E6%88%B7%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B\">3.5 子流程五：提交开户（核心流程）</h3>\n<p><strong>业务描述：</strong> 提交完整的携转开户业务数据，创建用户、账户、套餐订购、携转关系等记录。</p>\n<p><strong>时序图：</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-mermaid\"><div class=\"mermaid\">sequenceDiagram\n participant User as 工作人员\n participant FE as 前端\n participant Page as NpSubscriberOpen\n participant OpenSV as INpSubscriberOpenOperateSV\n participant CustSV as ICCOutOperateSV\n participant DB as 数据库\n\n User->>FE: 点击 提交\n FE->>FE: submitBeforeCheck 全面校验\n FE->>FE: checkHasActive 校验套餐关联活动\n FE->>FE: $.cssubmit.submitTrade 组装提交数据\n FE->>Page: onTradeSubmit 全部表单数据\n activate Page\n\n Page->>OpenSV: createNpSubscriber 开户核心逻辑\n activate OpenSV\n OpenSV->>DB: INSERT 用户表 账户表 订购表 携转关系表\n DB-->>OpenSV: TRADE_ID\n deactivate OpenSV\n\n alt 开户失败\n Page->>CustSV: cardCampOn 营销活动补偿\n activate CustSV\n CustSV->>CustSV: 回滚/补偿操作\n CustSV-->>Page: 补偿结果\n deactivate CustSV\n Page-->>FE: 开户失败\n else 开户成功\n Page->>CustSV: addOperLog 记录操作日志\n activate CustSV\n CustSV->>DB: INSERT 操作日志表\n CustSV-->>Page: 成功\n deactivate CustSV\n Page-->>FE: 开户成功\n end\n deactivate Page\n</div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>调用链详情：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>前端：<code>submitBeforeCheck()</code> -&gt; 全面校验 -&gt; <code>checkHasActive</code> -&gt; <code>$.cssubmit.submitTrade()</code> -&gt; <code>onTradeSubmit</code></li>\n<li>后端接口：<code>NpSubscriberOpen.onTradeSubmit(IRequestCycle)</code></li>\n<li>业务层：\n<ol>\n<li><code>this.call(&quot;OrderCentre.person.INpSubscriberOpenOperateSV.createNpSubscriber&quot;)</code> - 携转开户核心逻辑</li>\n<li><code>this.call(&quot;CustomerCentre.custmgr.ICCOutOperateSV.cardCampOn&quot;)</code> - 营销活动补偿（失败时）</li>\n<li><code>this.call(&quot;CustomerCentre.common.IOperLogSV.addOperLog&quot;)</code> - 记录操作日志</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>数据库：用户表、账户表、订购表、携转关系表（INSERT）</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>关键字段：</strong></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>层级</th>\n<th>输入字段</th>\n<th>输出字段</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>前端</td>\n<td>全部表单数据 ACCESS_NUM SELECTED_OFFER_VALUE ICC_ID PARTY_NAME IDEN_NR ASP NP_BACK等</td>\n<td>TRADE_ID(开户成功)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>后端</td>\n<td>完整开户数据</td>\n<td>TRADE_ID, bizCode, bizDesc</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"36-%E5%AD%90%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%E5%85%AD%E5%80%BC%E7%8F%AD%E9%95%BF%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81%E7%A0%81%E6%8E%88%E6%9D%83\">3.6 子流程六：值班长验证码授权</h3>\n<p><strong>业务描述：</strong> 对于吉祥号码等特殊场景，需要值班长工号发送验证码并校验通过后才能继续办理。</p>\n<p><strong>时序图：</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-mermaid\"><div class=\"mermaid\">sequenceDiagram\n participant User as 工作人员\n participant FE as 前端\n participant Page as NpSubscriberOpen\n participant OpenSV as ISubscriberOpenSV\n participant DB as 验证码表\n\n Note over User,DB: 发送验证码\n\n User->>FE: 输入值班长工号 点击发送验证码\n FE->>FE: sendYzm 校验工号格式(8位)\n FE->>Page: dealYzm MANAGER_STAFF ACCESS_NUM ACTION=SEND_YZM\n activate Page\n Page->>OpenSV: dealYzm\n activate OpenSV\n OpenSV->>DB: 生成验证码 发送短信\n DB-->>OpenSV: 成功\n OpenSV-->>Page: returnValue returnMsg\n deactivate OpenSV\n Page-->>FE: 发送结果\n deactivate Page\n FE-->>User: 提示发送成功\n\n Note over User,DB: 校验验证码\n\n User->>FE: 输入验证码 点击校验\n FE->>FE: fnValidateYzmInfo 校验验证码\n FE->>Page: dealYzm SMS_NUMBER MANAGER_STAFF ACCESS_NUM ACTION=VALID_YZM\n activate Page\n Page->>OpenSV: dealYzm\n activate OpenSV\n OpenSV->>DB: 校验验证码\n DB-->>OpenSV: smsValidFlag\n OpenSV-->>Page: returnValue returnMsg smsValidFlag\n deactivate OpenSV\n Page-->>FE: 校验结果\n deactivate Page\n\n alt 校验通过\n FE->>FE: yzmValidFlag = 0 解除证件字段禁用\n else 校验失败\n FE-->>User: 提示验证码错误\n end\n</div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>调用链详情：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>前端发送：<code>sendYzm()</code> -&gt; 校验工号8位 -&gt; <code>$.ajax.submit(&quot;&quot;, &quot;dealYzm&quot;, params, &quot;&quot;, ...)</code></li>\n<li>前端校验：<code>fnValidateYzmInfo()</code> -&gt; <code>$.ajax.submit(&quot;&quot;, &quot;dealYzm&quot;, params, &quot;&quot;, ...)</code></li>\n<li>后端接口：<code>NpSubscriberOpen.dealYzm(IRequestCycle)</code></li>\n<li>业务层：<code>ServiceCaller.call(&quot;OrderCentre.person.ISubscriberOpenSV.dealYzm&quot;)</code></li>\n<li>数据库：验证码表（生成/校验）</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>关键字段：</strong></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>层级</th>\n<th>输入字段</th>\n<th>输出字段</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>前端</td>\n<td>MANAGER_STAFF(8位工号), SMS_NUMBER(验证码), ACCESS_NUM</td>\n<td>returnValue, returnMsg, smsValidFlag</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><strong>异常处理：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>值班长工号非8位：前端提示&quot;值班长工号输入错误&quot;</li>\n<li>验证码为空：前端提示&quot;请输入验证码信息&quot;</li>\n<li>验证码错误：后端返回非0的returnValue</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"37-%E5%AD%90%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%E4%B8%83%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B%E6%A0%A1%E9%AA%8C\">3.7 子流程七：智能助手校验</h3>\n<p><strong>业务描述：</strong> 通过AI智能助手对客户证件信息进行智能校验，获取校验结果。</p>\n<p><strong>时序图：</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-mermaid\"><div class=\"mermaid\">sequenceDiagram\n participant FE as 前端\n participant Page as NpSubscriberOpen\n participant AgentSV as IAgentTokenSV\n\n Note over FE,AgentSV: 页面初始化时查询智能助手开关\n\n FE->>Page: queryAssistantSwitch\n activate Page\n Page->>AgentSV: queryAssistantSwitch\n activate AgentSV\n AgentSV-->>Page: SHOW_AGENT_ASSISTANT_BUTTON\n deactivate AgentSV\n Page-->>FE: Y或N\n deactivate Page\n\n alt SHOW_AGENT_ASSISTANT_BUTTON == Y\n FE->>FE: 显示 启动智能助手 按钮\n else\n FE->>FE: 隐藏按钮\n end\n\n Note over FE,AgentSV: 用户点击智能助手\n\n FE->>Page: generateAgentToken CERT_TYPE_ID CERT_ID\n activate Page\n Page->>AgentSV: generate\n activate AgentSV\n AgentSV->>AgentSV: 生成智能助手访问Token和URL\n AgentSV-->>Page: URL MSG\n deactivate AgentSV\n Page-->>FE: URL\n deactivate Page\n\n alt URL 存在\n FE->>FE: openAgentPopup 打开智能助手页面\n else\n FE-->>User: 提示智能体地址获取失败\n end\n</div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>调用链详情：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>开关查询：<code>loadAgentAssistantSwitch()</code> -&gt; <code>$.ajax.submit(null, &quot;queryAssistantSwitch&quot;, &quot;&quot;, ...)</code> -&gt; <code>this.call(&quot;OrderCentre.agent.crm.IAgentTokenSV.queryAssistantSwitch&quot;)</code></li>\n<li>生成Token：<code>openAgentWindow()</code> -&gt; 校验证件信息 -&gt; <code>$.ajax.submit(null, &quot;generateAgentToken&quot;, param, ...)</code> -&gt; <code>this.call(&quot;OrderCentre.agent.crm.IAgentTokenSV.generate&quot;)</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>关键字段：</strong></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>层级</th>\n<th>输入字段</th>\n<th>输出字段</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>前端</td>\n<td>CERT_TYPE_ID, CERT_ID</td>\n<td>URL, MSG</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"38-%E5%AD%90%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%E5%85%AB%E5%90%89%E7%A5%A5%E5%8F%B7%E7%A0%81%E6%9D%83%E9%99%90%E6%A0%A1%E9%AA%8C\">3.8 子流程八：吉祥号码权限校验</h3>\n<p><strong>业务描述：</strong> 对于吉祥号码开户，需要通过值班长验证码授权才能继续办理。</p>\n<p><strong>时序图：</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-mermaid\"><div class=\"mermaid\">sequenceDiagram\n participant FE as 前端\n participant Page as NpSubscriberOpen\n participant NumSV as INumberIntfQuerySV\n participant PrivSV as ISecPrivOperSV\n participant DB as 数据库\n\n FE->>Page: initIMPOWER ACCESS_NUM IS_CHKRULE\n activate Page\n Page->>NumSV: querySingNumInfo ACCESS_NUM\n activate NumSV\n NumSV->>DB: SELECT 号码信息 判断是否吉祥号\n DB-->>NumSV: ISLUCKY\n deactivate NumSV\n\n alt ISLUCKY == 1 吉祥号码\n Page->>PrivSV: insertLuckyNumBusiLog 记录吉祥号操作日志\n activate PrivSV\n PrivSV->>DB: INSERT 吉祥号操作日志表\n PrivSV-->>Page: 成功\n deactivate PrivSV\n Page-->>FE: ISLUCKY=1\n FE->>FE: 显示验证码授权区域 IMPOWER\n else 非吉祥号码\n Page-->>FE: ISLUCKY!=1\n FE->>FE: 隐藏验证码授权区域\n end\n deactivate Page\n</div></code></pre>\n<p><strong>调用链详情：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>前端：<code>$.NpSubscriberOpen.init()</code> -&gt; 获取登录号码 -&gt; <code>$.ajax.submit(&quot;&quot;, &quot;initIMPOWER&quot;, param, &quot;NpSubHiddenPart&quot;, ...)</code></li>\n<li>后端接口：<code>NpSubscriberOpen.initIMPOWER(IRequestCycle)</code></li>\n<li>业务层：\n<ol>\n<li><code>this.call(&quot;ResourceCentre.resource.INumberIntfQuerySV.querySingNumInfo&quot;)</code> - 查询号码是否为吉祥号</li>\n<li><code>this.call(&quot;BusiFrame.priv.ISecPrivOperSV.insertLuckyNumBusiLog&quot;)</code> - 记录吉祥号操作日志</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>数据库：号码信息表（SELECT）、吉祥号操作日志表（INSERT）</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>关键字段：</strong></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>层级</th>\n<th>输入字段</th>\n<th>输出字段</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>前端</td>\n<td>ACCESS_NUM(登录号码)</td>\n<td>ISLUCKY</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"%E5%9B%9B%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E4%BE%9D%E8%B5%96%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E5%9B%BE\">四、数据依赖关系图</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-mermaid\"><div class=\"mermaid\">graph TD\n A[输入携入号码] --> B[checkAccessNum 校验]\n B --> C{校验通过?}\n C -->|否| D[提示错误]\n C -->|是| E[填充客户信息 PARTY_NAME IDEN_NR等]\n E --> F[queryTodayOpenCountAndNotice 风险提醒]\n F --> G{NOTICE_TAG==1?}\n G -->|是| H[风险提示]\n G -->|否| I[继续]\n H --> I\n\n I --> J{需要写卡?}\n J -->|是| K[beforeReadCard 读卡]\n K --> L[afterReadCard 判断IS_WRITED]\n L --> M{IS_WRITED==100?}\n M -->|是| N[checkIccId SIM卡校验]\n M -->|否| O[提示成卡]\n N --> P[CHECK_RESULT_CODE=1]\n P --> Q[beforeWriteCard 写卡]\n Q --> R[afterWriteCard 设置ICC_ID]\n R --> N\n J -->|否| S[CHECK_RESULT_CODE=0]\n\n S --> T[openOffer 选择套餐]\n T --> U[getOfferSubmitParams 保存套餐]\n U --> V[openActive 选择活动]\n V --> W[checkSaleActiveFee 查询资费]\n W --> X[getActiveSubmitParams 保存活动]\n X --> Y[sendEpaperPre 签订协议]\n Y --> Z[EPAPER_PRE_INTACT_ID]\n Z --> AA[submitBeforeCheck 全面校验]\n AA --> AB[checkHasActive 校验关联活动]\n AB --> AC[$.cssubmit.submitTrade 提交]\n AC --> AD[onTradeSubmit 携转开户]\n AD --> AE[createNpSubscriber 创建用户]\n AE --> AF{成功?}\n AF -->|是| AG[addOperLog 记录日志]\n AF -->|否| AH[cardCampOn 营销补偿]\n AG --> AI[开户完成]\n AH --> AJ[开户失败]\n</div></code></pre>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"%E4%BA%94%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E7%B4%A2%E5%BC%95\">五、关键函数索引</h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>函数名</th>\n<th>所在文件</th>\n<th>业务作用</th>\n<th>调用后端接口</th>\n<th>所属流程</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>checkAccessNum</td>\n<td>npsubscriberopen.js / NpSubscriberOpenComp.js</td>\n<td>携入号码校验</td>\n<td>POST ACTION=checkAccessNum -&gt; INpSubscriberOpenOperateSV.checkAccessNum</td>\n<td>主流程-步骤1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>queryTodayOpenCountAndNotice</td>\n<td>npsubscriberopen.js</td>\n<td>开户风险提醒</td>\n<td>POST ACTION=queryTodayOpenCountAndNotice -&gt; ICustInfoOperateSV.queryTodayOpenCountAndNotice</td>\n<td>主流程-步骤2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>beforeReadCard</td>\n<td>npsubscriberopen.js / NpSubscriberOpenComp.js</td>\n<td>读卡前校验</td>\n<td>无</td>\n<td>主流程-步骤3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>afterReadCard</td>\n<td>npsubscriberopen.js / NpSubscriberOpenComp.js</td>\n<td>读卡后处理</td>\n<td>无</td>\n<td>主流程-步骤3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>checkIccId</td>\n<td>npsubscriberopen.js / NpSubscriberOpenComp.js</td>\n<td>SIM卡校验</td>\n<td>POST ACTION=checkIccId -&gt; INpSubscriberOpenOperateSV.checkNpIccId</td>\n<td>主流程-步骤4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>beforeWriteCard</td>\n<td>npsubscriberopen.js / NpSubscriberOpenComp.js</td>\n<td>写卡前校验</td>\n<td>无</td>\n<td>主流程-步骤5</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>afterWriteCard</td>\n<td>npsubscriberopen.js / NpSubscriberOpenComp.js</td>\n<td>写卡后处理</td>\n<td>无</td>\n<td>主流程-步骤5</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>openOffer</td>\n<td>NpSubscriberOpenComp.js</td>\n<td>打开套餐选择弹窗</td>\n<td>$.OfferListPopup.showOfferListPopup</td>\n<td>主流程-步骤6</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>getOfferSubmitParams</td>\n<td>npsubscriberopen.js / NpSubscriberOpenComp.js</td>\n<td>套餐选择回调</td>\n<td>OfferHandler.getOffer</td>\n<td>主流程-步骤6</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>openActive</td>\n<td>npsubscriberopen.js / NpSubscriberOpenComp.js</td>\n<td>打开活动选择弹窗</td>\n<td>$.OfferListPopup.showOfferListPopup</td>\n<td>主流程-步骤7</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>getActiveSubmitParams</td>\n<td>npsubscriberopen.js / NpSubscriberOpenComp.js</td>\n<td>活动选择回调</td>\n<td>POST ACTION=checkSaleActiveFee -&gt; UnifyProductCentre.offer.IPriceQueryFSV.queryPriceFeeByOfferIdForRes + OfferHandler.getOffer</td>\n<td>主流程-步骤7</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>sendEpaperPre</td>\n<td>npsubscriberopen.js / NpSubscriberOpenComp.js</td>\n<td>生成前置协议</td>\n<td>POST ACTION=sendEpaperPre -&gt; IElecSV.getPreEpaperOper</td>\n<td>主流程-步骤8</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>submitBeforeCheck</td>\n<td>npsubscriberopen.js / NpSubscriberOpenComp.js</td>\n<td>提交前全面校验</td>\n<td>POST ACTION=checkHasActive -&gt; StaticUtil</td>\n<td>主流程-步骤9</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>sendYzm</td>\n<td>npsubscriberopen.js / NpSubscriberOpenComp.js</td>\n<td>发送值班长验证码</td>\n<td>POST ACTION=dealYzm -&gt; ISubscriberOpenSV.dealYzm</td>\n<td>子流程-验证码</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>fnValidateYzmInfo</td>\n<td>npsubscriberopen.js / NpSubscriberOpenComp.js</td>\n<td>校验验证码</td>\n<td>POST ACTION=dealYzm -&gt; ISubscriberOpenSV.dealYzm</td>\n<td>子流程-验证码</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>loadAgentAssistantSwitch</td>\n<td>npsubscriberopen.js</td>\n<td>查询智能助手开关</td>\n<td>POST ACTION=queryAssistantSwitch -&gt; IAgentTokenSV.queryAssistantSwitch</td>\n<td>子流程-智能助手</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>openAgentWindow</td>\n<td>npsubscriberopen.js</td>\n<td>打开智能助手</td>\n<td>POST ACTION=generateAgentToken -&gt; IAgentTokenSV.generate</td>\n<td>子流程-智能助手</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>initIMPOWER</td>\n<td>NpSubscriberOpen.java</td>\n<td>吉祥号码权限校验</td>\n<td>POST ACTION=initIMPOWER -&gt; INumberIntfQuerySV.querySingNumInfo + ISecPrivOperSV.insertLuckyNumBusiLog</td>\n<td>子流程-吉祥号</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>onTradeSubmit</td>\n<td>NpSubscriberOpen.java</td>\n<td>提交携转开户</td>\n<td>onTradeSubmit -&gt; INpSubscriberOpenOperateSV.createNpSubscriber</td>\n<td>主流程-步骤9</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>buildSubmitDatas</td>\n<td>NpSubscriberOpen.java</td>\n<td>构建统一鉴权提交参数</td>\n<td>POST ACTION=buildSubmitDatas</td>\n<td>辅助流程</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>checkAgentInfo</td>\n<td>npsubscriberopen.js / NpSubscriberOpenComp.js</td>\n<td>经办人信息校验</td>\n<td>无</td>\n<td>辅助校验</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>checkAge</td>\n<td>npsubscriberopen.js</td>\n<td>年龄校验(18岁以上)</td>\n<td>无</td>\n<td>辅助校验</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>getCompBusiData</td>\n<td>NpSubscriberOpenComp.js</td>\n<td>获取组件业务数据(场景化融合)</td>\n<td>$.FusionUtil.buildBusiData</td>\n<td>场景化流程</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"%E5%85%AD%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E4%BA%8B%E9%A1%B9%E4%B8%8E%E8%BE%B9%E7%95%8C%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6\">六、注意事项与边界条件</h2>\n<h3 id=\"61-%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E9%A1%BA%E5%BA%8F%E4%B8%8E%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81%E4%BE%9D%E8%B5%96\">6.1 操作顺序与状态依赖</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>前置条件</th>\n<th>依赖操作</th>\n<th>标志变量</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>SIM卡校验</td>\n<td>CHECK_RESULT_CODE != -1</td>\n<td>必须先校验携入号码</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>写卡</td>\n<td>CHECK_RESULT_CODE != -1</td>\n<td>必须先校验携入号码</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>签订协议</td>\n<td>CHECK_RESULT_CODE == 1</td>\n<td>必须完成SIM卡校验</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>提交开户</td>\n<td>CHECK_RESULT_CODE == 1</td>\n<td>必须完成SIM卡校验</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>智能助手</td>\n<td>证件信息已填写</td>\n<td>IDEN_TYPE_CODE和IDEN_NR非空</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"62-%E5%BC%80%E6%88%B7%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B-opentype-%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E\">6.2 开户类型 OPEN_TYPE 说明</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>OPEN_TYPE</th>\n<th>类型</th>\n<th>特殊要求</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>12</td>\n<td>携转用户开户</td>\n<td>需填写集团编码(条件显示)</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"63-%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E6%90%BA%E5%9B%9E%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E8%A7%84%E5%88%99\">6.3 快速携回业务规则</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>条件</th>\n<th>规则</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>ASP == 1</td>\n<td>必须是移动携出号码</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>DAY_NUM &lt;= 7</td>\n<td>携出7天内才能办理</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>NP_BACK == 1</td>\n<td>快速携回标记 勾选后生效</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"64-%E5%B9%B6%E5%8F%91%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6\">6.4 并发控制</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>SIM卡选占：</strong> <code>checkNpIccId</code> 通过数据库状态更新实现选占，防止多操作员同时选占同一张SIM卡</li>\n<li><strong>号码预占：</strong> 携入号码校验时可能涉及号码预占 [待补充详细机制]</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"65-%E5%B9%82%E7%AD%89%E6%80%A7\">6.5 幂等性</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>查询操作：</strong> 所有查询类接口天然幂等</li>\n<li><strong>协议生成：</strong> <code>sendEpaperPre</code> 每次调用生成新的 PRE_INTACT_ID，非幂等</li>\n<li><strong>提交开户：</strong> <code>onTradeSubmit</code> 非幂等，重复提交会创建重复用户</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"66-%E5%B7%B2%E7%9F%A5%E5%BC%82%E5%B8%B8%E5%9C%BA%E6%99%AF\">6.6 已知异常场景</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>异常场景</th>\n<th>触发条件</th>\n<th>处理方式</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>携入号码不存在</td>\n<td>输入非携转号码</td>\n<td>后端返回错误</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>快速携回条件不满足</td>\n<td>ASP!=1 或 DAY_NUM&gt;7</td>\n<td>前端提示拦截</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>成卡误用</td>\n<td>IS_WRITED=1</td>\n<td>前端提示&quot;此卡为成卡，请选择白卡&quot;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>铁通号码</td>\n<td>ACCESS_NUM以0开头</td>\n<td>前端提示&quot;铁通号码不支持白卡开户&quot;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>集团后付费备注为空</td>\n<td>SUBSCRIBER_TYPE=w 且 REMARKS为空</td>\n<td>前端提示拦截</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>集团后付费备注非中文</td>\n<td>SUBSCRIBER_TYPE=w 且 REMARKS非中文</td>\n<td>前端提示拦截</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>套餐有指定关联活动</td>\n<td>MAIN_OFFER_ID有值 且 ACTIVE=TRUE</td>\n<td>弹窗确认是否返回选择</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>吉祥号码未授权</td>\n<td>ISLUCKY=1 但未通过验证码校验</td>\n<td>验证码区域显示 必须通过授权</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>18岁以下用户</td>\n<td>身份证计算年龄&lt;18</td>\n<td>前端提示&quot;请到对应场景化菜单办理&quot;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>统一鉴权场景</td>\n<td>$.authUtil.matchAuthScene 匹配成功</td>\n<td>needPrePaper=false 跳过前置协议</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"67-%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E9%A1%B9\">6.7 重要配置项</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>配置项</th>\n<th>位置</th>\n<th>说明</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>PRE_BUSI_MODE_CODE</td>\n<td>页面隐藏域</td>\n<td>无纸化前置模式 1=开启</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>IS_NEED_WRITE_CARD_NEW</td>\n<td>页面隐藏域</td>\n<td>1=使用新版写卡组件 0=使用旧版</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>NEED_PASSWORD</td>\n<td>页面隐藏域</td>\n<td>1=需要手动设置密码 0=短信下发</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>OS_SEL_FLAG</td>\n<td>静态配置</td>\n<td>国际短信语音功能开关</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>DEFAULT_NPSUBOPEN_OFFER_IDS</td>\n<td>页面隐藏域</td>\n<td>默认套餐ID列表</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>DEFAULT_NPSUBOPEN_NEW_ACTIVE_IDS</td>\n<td>页面隐藏域</td>\n<td>默认活动ID列表</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>UNIFY_CFG_ID</td>\n<td>页面隐藏域</td>\n<td>统一鉴权配置ID</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>OPENPRV/OPENPRVEX</td>\n<td>权限配置</td>\n<td>开户证件权限控制</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"68-%E4%B8%8E-unifyproductcentre-%E7%9A%84%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB\">6.8 与 UnifyProductCentre 的调用关系</h3>\n<p>本页面<strong>仅有一处</strong>调用 UnifyProductCentre：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>checkSaleActiveFee()</code> -&gt; <code>UnifyProductCentre.offer.IPriceQueryFSV.queryPriceFeeByOfferIdForRes</code></li>\n<li>用途：查询营销活动的最低预存费用</li>\n<li>调用时机：选择新入网活动时</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"69-%E5%BE%85%E8%A1%A5%E5%85%85%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF\">6.9 待补充信息</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>项目</th>\n<th>说明</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>数据库表结构</td>\n<td>携转用户表、用户表、账户表、订购表、携转关系表的完整DDL</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>createNpSubscriber 服务实现</td>\n<td>携转开户核心逻辑的详细实现</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>checkAccessNum 服务实现</td>\n<td>携入号码校验的详细逻辑</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>checkNpIccId 服务实现</td>\n<td>SIM卡校验的详细逻辑</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>统一鉴权流程</td>\n<td>$.authUtil 组件的完整鉴权流程</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>场景化融合组件</td>\n<td>$.FusionUtil.buildBusiData 的详细实现</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>智能助手系统</td>\n<td>IAgentTokenSV.generate 的接口协议和智能体系统架构</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n</file>"}],"timestamp":1775814057444}}
{"type":"message","id":"7a2f0e08","parentId":"6a131e4e","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:41:23.265Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user sent another file - this is the \"业务逻辑说明文档\" (Business Logic Documentation) for the same 携转用户开户 (NP portability user account opening) system. This is the reference document that was used to generate the security analysis report.\n\nThis document describes:\n1. Overview of the page functionality\n2. Main business flow with Mermaid sequence diagrams\n3. 8 sub-flows detailed:\n   - 携入号码校验 (NP number validation)\n   - SIM卡读写与校验 (SIM card read/write and validation)\n   - 套餐和活动选择 (Package and offer selection)\n   - 签订协议 (Agreement signing)\n   - 提交开户 (Account opening submission - core flow)\n   - 值班长验证码授权 (Supervisor verification code authorization)\n   - 智能助手校验 (AI assistant validation)\n   - 吉祥号码权限校验 (Lucky number permission validation)\n4. Data dependency relationships\n5. Key function index\n6. Notes and boundary conditions\n\nThis is essentially the source document that the security analysis was based on. The user sent this alongside the security report, probably as context or reference material.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到！这是**业务逻辑说明文档**——是安全分析报告的源文档。\n\n可以确认两份文档的关系：\n\n---\n\n## 📄 文档对照\n\n| 文档 | 内容 | 用途 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **业务逻辑说明文档** | 8个子流程的完整时序图 + 代码调用链 + 字段说明 | AI 分析的输入（代码理解） |\n| **安全分析报告** | 11 个漏洞的详细审计（类型/代码/Mermaid/复现/修复建议） | AI 分析的输出 |\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 说明文档结构速览\n\n**8 个子流程：**\n\n| 子流程 | 核心风险点（已在安全报告中覆盖） |\n|--------|---------|\n| ① 携入号码校验 | VUL-002（IBOSS000 硬编码绕过）、VUL-010（一证多名检查不全） |\n| ② SIM卡读写与校验 | 并发选占竞态条件（信息不足，待补充） |\n| ③ 套餐和活动选择 | VUL-005（OPEN_TYPE=11 绕过权限） |\n| ④ 签订无纸化协议 | VUL-008（非幂等，可滥用生成大量协议） |\n| ⑤ **提交开户（核心）** | VUL-001（幂等性缺失）、VUL-004（非原子删除）、VUL-006（预占释放不全）、VUL-007（弱随机数） |\n| ⑥ 值班长验证码授权 | VUL-009（无频率限制 + 暴力破解） |\n| ⑦ 智能助手校验 | （信息不足，未分析） |\n| ⑧ 吉祥号码权限校验 | VUL-003（前端 JS 变量绕过）、VUL-011（日志异常被静默吞没） |\n\n---\n\n## 📌 两份文档关键对应关系\n\n安全报告的 **VUL-003** 对应说明文档的 **子流程⑥+⑧**：\n- 吉祥号校验 → `initIMPOWER` 返回 `ISLUCKY` → 前端显示验证码区\n- 但 `onTradeSubmit`（子流程⑤）**未校验**验证码状态\n\n安全报告的 **VUL-001** 对应说明文档的 **6.5 幂等性**：\n> 文档明确写了：`onTradeSubmit 非幂等，重复提交会创建重复用户`\n\n---\n\n这两份文档构成了完整的**安全审计输入+输出**。如果要用它们测试代码扫描插件，需要我做什么？比如：\n\n1. 把这两份文档打包成 ZIP，用插件扫描生成报告？\n2. 作为**提示词模板**的示例，让插件生成类似格式的安全分析？\n3. 其他用途？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":16837,"output":799,"cacheRead":148731,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":166367,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775814057491,"responseId":"chatcmpl-2f5887f6-b1dc-4696-9554-a4cf577ce031"}}
{"type":"compaction","id":"ead04c0d","parentId":"7a2f0e08","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:41:58.527Z","summary":"## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] 创建 `projects/code-scanner-plugin/` 完整前端项目（Vue 3 + Vite + TypeScript）\n- [x] `src/CodeScanner.vue` — 4步状态机（上传ZIP→提示词→等待→报告展示）\n- [x] `src/scanService.ts` — 核心业务（`buildPromptWithUploadInstruction`/`submitScanTask`/`waitForResult`）\n- [x] `src/mockMinioClient.ts` — Mock MinIO 客户端（浏览器兼容版）\n- [x] `server/mockMinio.ts` — Mock MinIO Server（端口9000/9001，支持seed）\n- [x] `server/index.ts` — Express Mock Backend（端口3001，60s后注入MD到MinIO）\n- [x] `buildPromptWithUploadInstruction` 修正：Mock模式也追加MinIO上传指令（地址10.28.198.153:9010、用户名admin、桶code-scanning、UUID）\n- [x] **Bug修复：`Buffer`浏览器兼容性问题** — `mockMinioClient.ts`中所有`Buffer`替换为`TextDecoder`/`TextEncoder`/`Uint8Array`（浏览器无`Buffer`API）\n- [x] Mock MinIO主服务(9000)增加`/seed?uuid=`端点用于E2E测试\n- [x] Mock后端注释更新为\"模拟大模型按追加指令上传到MinIO\"\n- [x] TypeScript编译通过（`tsc --noEmit` 0错误）\n- [x] Vite生产构建通过（1.83s，92模块）\n- [x] Playwright E2E全链路测试：**11/11全部通过**\n  - S1.Mock MinIO连接+seed ✅\n  - S2.Mock Backend接口 ✅\n  - B1.页面加载 ✅\n  - B2.ZIP上传 ✅\n  - B3.导航Step2 ✅\n  - B4.模板填充 ✅\n  - B5.提交扫描+Step3状态 ✅\n  - S3.轮询逻辑(seed→读到文件) ✅\n  - B6.轮询检测到文件→Step4 ✅\n  - B7.报告展示(724字符HTML,H1+表格) ✅\n  - B8.重新扫描回到Step1 ✅\n- [x] `e2e-test.mjs` — 完整Playwright自动化测试脚本\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] GitHub推送待确认（沙箱网络无法直连github.com，需用户提供本地推送）\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **`Buffer`用`TextDecoder`/`TextEncoder`/`Uint8Array`替代**：浏览器环境无Node.js的`Buffer`API，`downloadTextFile`使用`new TextDecoder().decode(ab)`，`uploadTextFile`使用`new TextEncoder().encode(content)`\n- **Mock seed端点加在9000主服务**：确保轮询端点与seed写入端点一致，避免跨服务文件同步不可靠\n- **`buildPromptWithUploadInstruction`统一追加MinIO指令**：移除Mock模式下的shortcut，保证提示词在真实/模拟场景下一致\n\n## Next Steps\n1. 将修复后的项目代码（`Buffer`兼容版）推送到GitHub：`https://github.com/wangyang962996947/yaxins`\n2. 测试可选择两条路径：\n   - Mock模式：Mock后端60s延迟 + Mock MinIO轮询（`USE_MOCK=true`）\n   - 真实模式：连接真实MinIO 10.28.198.153:9010（`USE_MOCK=false`）\n3. 前端`vite.config.ts`已配置代理（`/api`→3001，`/minio`→10.28.198.153:9010），需部署后验证\n\n## Critical Context\n- **Bug根因**：`waitForResult`轮询`fileExists`返回`true`后调用`downloadTextFile`，但`downloadTextFile`内部`Buffer.from(ab).toString('utf-8')`在浏览器中抛出`ReferenceError: Buffer is not defined`，被catch吞掉，导致Step4永远不出现\n- 调试方法：Playwright监听浏览器console + 网络请求拦截，发现`[waitForResult] 轮询出错: ReferenceError: Buffer is not defined`\n- 真实MinIO地址：`10.28.198.153:9010`，用户名`admin`，密码`A12345678`，桶`code-scanning`\n- Mock MinIO存储目录：`/tmp/code-scanning-mock/`\n- 后端60s延迟模拟LLM生成报告的真实处理时间\n\n## Exact Identifiers\n- MinIO地址：`10.28.198.153:9010`\n- MinIO用户名：`admin`\n- MinIO密码：`A12345678`\n- MinIO桶名：`code-scanning`\n- Mock MinIO端口：9000（主服务）、9001（控制面板）\n- Mock Backend端口：3001\n- Frontend端口：5174\n- 仓库URL：`https://github.com/wangyang962996947/yaxins`\n- Token（已撤销）：`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`\n- 日志文件：`/tmp/mock-minio.log`、`/tmp/mock-backend.log`、`/tmp/vite.log`\n- 测试文件：`/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/projects/code-scanner-plugin/e2e-test.mjs`\n- Mock存储目录：`/tmp/code-scanning-mock/`\n- 核心文件：`src/mockMinioClient.ts`、`src/scanService.ts`、`src/CodeScanner.vue`、`server/index.ts`、`server/mockMinio.ts`\n- USE_MOCK开关：`scanService.ts`第10行\n\n## Recent turns preserved verbatim\n- User: System: [2026-04-10 16:31:09 GMT+8] Exec failed (clear-pr, signal SIGTERM)\nSystem: [2026-04-10 16:33:18 GMT+8] Exec failed (warm-wha, signal SIGTERM)\nSystem: [2026-04-10 16:34:36 GMT+8] Exec completed (wild-rid, code 1) :: 6:34:06] [❌ FAIL] 轮询等待: Step 4 结果页未出现 [16:34:06] [ℹ️ INFO] 测试报告展示和交互 [16:34:06] [❌ FAIL] 报告展示: 下载按钮未显示 [16:34:06] [ℹ️ INFO] 测试重新扫描功能 [16:34:36] [❌ FAIL] 重新扫描: locator.click: Timeo…\nSystem: [2026-04-10 16:39:40 GMT+8] Exec failed (tidal-ne, signal SIGTERM) :: 🔧 Mock MinIO Server 已启动 (端口 9000) 模拟桶: code-scanning 存储目录: /tmp/code-scanning-mock 对象操作: http://localhost:9000/{objec...\n- Assistant: 测试刚通过，立即推送修复到 GitHub：\n[non-text content: thinking, toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): 📋 收集本地文件...\n\n共 20 个文件\n\n🌳 获取当前分支 HEAD commit...\n\n  parent commit: c9fac7d6a