{"type":"message","id":"b1999cc4","parentId":"bf71ffcb","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:49:45.761Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Wait, I realize the E2E test approach for seeding the simulator won't work this way - importing the built JS module from the test file won't work because the simulator's fileStore is not exported. Let me rethink the approach.\n\nLooking at the simulator code I wrote, the `fileStore` is a module-level `const`, not exported. For E2E testing, I need a different approach.\n\nOptions:\n1. Expose a seed function from simulator.ts that the test can call via `window`\n2. Use a different approach - directly inject the data via the page's JavaScript context before navigating\n\nActually, the simplest approach for E2E testing is to use `page.evaluate` to directly set the data into the simulator module after the page loads. \n\nBut since the fileStore is a module-level variable and not accessible from the window scope, I need to expose it. Let me add an export to simulator.ts that lets the test seed data, then call it via `page.evaluate`. The key insight is that `page.evaluate` runs in the browser context after the page loads, so I can inject a seed call there rather than trying to import the built module directly.\n\nFor the E2E test, I'll navigate to the page first, then use `page.evaluate` to directly set items in the fileStore map by accessing the module's internal state, bypassing the need for a separate seed function.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"E2E 测试需要能访问 simulator 的内部存储，改成 `page.evaluate` 直接注入：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ax2zxagvdmw6_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"/**\n * e2e-test.mjs — Playwright 自动化测试\n * 纯浏览器内模拟，无外部服务依赖\n *\n * 测试流程：\n *   B1. 页面加载\n *   B2. ZIP 上传\n *   B3. 导航 Step2\n *   B4. 模板填充\n *   B5. 提交扫描 → Step3 轮询\n *   S1. 轮询就绪（通过 page.evaluate 直接 seed 内存中的 fileStore）\n *   B6. Step4 列表页出现\n *   B7. 报告列表（2条记录，序号/文件名/时间）\n *   B8. 点击第一条 → Modal 弹框\n *   B9. Modal iframe 渲染 HTML\n *   B10. 关闭 Modal\n *   B11. 点击第二条 → Modal 再次打开\n *   B12. 重新扫描 → 回到 Step1\n */\n\nimport { chromium } from 'playwright'\n\nconst BASE = 'http://localhost:5173'\nconst REPORT_UUID = 'test-e2e-uuid-12345'\n\n// ============= 辅助函数 =============\n\nasync function runStep(name, fn) {\n  process.stdout.write(`[${new Date().toLocaleTimeString('zh-CN')}] [ℹ️  INFO] ${name}\\n`)\n  try {\n    await fn()\n    process.stdout.write(`[${new Date().toLocaleTimeString('zh-CN')}] [✅ PASS] ${name}\\n`)\n  } catch (err) {\n    process.stdout.write(`[${new Date().toLocaleTimeString('zh-CN')}] [❌ FAIL] ${name}: ${err.message}\\n`)\n    throw err\n  }\n}\n\n// ============= S1: 通过 page.evaluate seed fileStore =============\n\nasync function seedSimulator(page) {\n  // 直接在浏览器上下文中设置内存中的 fileStore\n  // simulator.ts 导出了 fileStore 即可直接访问\n  await page.evaluate((uuid) => {\n    // 等待 simulator 模块加载\n    return new Promise((resolve) => {\n      const check = () => {\n        // fileStore 位于 simulator 模块内，通过 scanService 间接访问\n        // 改用另一种方式：拦截 submitScanTask，直接修改 fileStore\n        // simulator 模块被 scanService 动态 import，我们通过 window 对象暴露 seed 入口\n        if (window.__simulatorSeed) {\n          window.__simulatorSeed(uuid)\n          resolve(true)\n        } else {\n          setTimeout(check, 100)\n        }\n      }\n      check()\n    })\n  }, REPORT_UUID)\n}\n\n// ============= 主测试 =============\n\nasync function main() {\n  console.log('='.repeat(55))\n  console.log('  代码扫描插件 — 全链路自动化测试')\n  console.log('  （列表+Modal 弹框逻辑）')\n  console.log('='.repeat(55))\n  console.log()\n\n  // 启动浏览器\n  const browser = await chromium.launch({ headless: true })\n  const context = await browser.newContext()\n  const page = await context.newPage()\n\n  const errors = []\n  page.on('console', msg => {\n    if (msg.type() === 'error') {\n      errors.push(msg.text())\n    }\n  })\n\n  // B1. 页面加载\n  await runStep('B1. 页面加载', async () => {\n    await page.goto(BASE, { waitUntil: 'networkidle' })\n    const title = await page.title()\n    if (!title.includes('代码扫描')) throw new Error(`意外标题: ${title}`)\n  })\n\n  await runStep('B1. Step 1 上传卡片渲染正常', async () => {\n    const card = page.locator('.step-card').first()\n    if (!(await card.isVisible())) throw new Error('Step 1 未渲染')\n  })\n\n  // B2. ZIP 上传\n  await runStep('B2. ZIP 文件选择', async () => {\n    const buffer = Buffer.from('PK\\x03\\x04') // ZIP magic bytes\n    await page.locator('#file-input').setInputFiles({\n      name: 'test-code.zip',\n      mimeType: 'application/zip',\n      buffer,\n    })\n    const label = page.locator('.file-name')\n    if (!(await label.isVisible())) throw new Error('文件名未显示')\n    const text = await label.textContent()\n    if (!text.includes('test-code.zip')) throw new Error(`文件名显示异常: ${text}`)\n  })\n\n  // B3. 导航 Step2\n  await runStep('B3. 导航 Step2（提示词输入）', async () => {\n    await page.click('.btn-primary')\n    await page.waitForSelector('.prompt-input', { timeout: 3000 })\n  })\n\n  // B4. 模板填充\n  await runStep('B4. 安全扫描模板填充', async () => {\n    await page.click('.btn-tpl:first-child')\n    const val = await page.locator('.prompt-input').inputValue()\n    if (!val.includes('安全')) throw new Error(`模板未填充`)\n  })\n\n  // B5. 提交扫描 → Step3\n  await runStep('B5. 提交扫描 + Step3 状态', async () => {\n    await page.click('.btn-primary')\n    await page.waitForSelector('.spinning', { timeout: 3000 })\n    const uuidEl = page.locator('.status-value.uuid')\n    if (!(await uuidEl.isVisible())) throw new Error('UUID 未显示')\n    // 获取当前任务的 UUID\n    return await uuidEl.textContent()\n  })\n\n  // S1. seed fileStore（让轮询立刻检测到文件）\n  await runStep('S1. 注入模拟报告列表到内存', async () => {\n    await page.evaluate((uuid) => {\n      // 直接操作 scanService 底层的 simulator 的 fileStore\n      // 由于模块动态加载，我们用另一个方式：\n      // 直接覆盖 window 对象上的轮询结果\n      // 实际上，在 simulator.ts 中我们导出 seedSimulatorData 函数\n      // 但最可靠的方式是等待轮询循环自然结束后再注入\n    }, REPORT_UUID)\n\n    // 最简单的方式：等待最多 10 秒让模拟器自动生成\n    // 或者强制让 waitForResult 提前返回\n    // 这里我们注入一个提前就绪的 uuid\n    // 改用劫持 setTimeout 让 reportStore 立刻可用\n    await page.evaluate((uuid) => {\n      // 等待 sim 模块就绪后，通过函数劫持实现提前触发\n      const originalSetTimeout = window.setTimeout\n      window.setTimeout = function(fn, delay, ...args) {\n        if (delay >= 5000 && delay <= 8000) {\n          // 立刻执行（不等待）\n          fn(...args)\n          return originalSetTimeout(() => {}, 9999999) // dummy id\n        }\n        return originalSetTimeout(fn, delay, ...args)\n      }\n    })\n    // 注入 fileStore（通过扫描任务 uuid 来关联）\n    // 实际上我们需要劫持整个 simulator\n    // 最实用的方案：直接修改 reportStore 的 ready 状态\n    // 做法：注入一个 key 让轮询能读到\n    await page.evaluate((uuid) => {\n      // 劫持 XMLHttpRequest / fetch，在 simulator.ts 的 setTimeout 回调执行前\n      // 我们主动往 fileStore 里写入\n      // 由于 simulator.ts 使用 fileStore = new Map()（模块级私有），\n      // 无法从外部访问。改用另一种方案：\n      // 通过 submitScanTask 的 fetch 拦截返回 202，然后立刻注入 fileStore\n    })\n  })\n\n  // B5 之后：我们不等待真实 5~8 秒，直接通过 console.log 找任务 UUID\n  // 然后用这个 UUID seed 模拟器\n\n  // 更实用的方法：重新加载页面 → 注入 seed 数据 → 再提交\n  await runStep('S1. 准备 seed 数据（reload + evaluate）', async () => {\n    // 直接在页面上以字符串注入两份报告的 HTML\n    await page.reload({ waitUntil: 'networkidle' })\n    // 将报告列表注入到页面 window\n    await page.evaluate((uuid) => {\n      const sampleHtml1 = '<html><head><title>安全分析报告</title></head><body><h1>携转用户开户 业务逻辑安全分析报告</h1><table><tr><th>漏洞编号</th><th>漏洞名称</th><th>严重程度</th></tr><tr><td>VUL-001</td><td>开户提交接口重复提交</td><td>高危</td></tr></table></body></html>'\n      const sampleHtml2 = '<html><head><title>业务逻辑说明文档</title></head><body><h1>携转用户开户 业务逻辑说明文档</h1><p>携入号码校验流程。</p></body></html>'\n      const now = new Date()\n      const pad = n => n.toString().padStart(2, '0')\n      const timeStr = `${now.getFullYear()}-${pad(now.getMonth()+1)}-${pad(now.getDate())} ${pad(now.getHours())}:${pad(now.getMinutes())}:${pad(now.getSeconds())}`\n      window.__seedReportList = (uuid) => ({\n        items: [\n          { index: 1, filename: '携转用户开户-业务逻辑安全分析报告.html', generateTime: timeStr, htmlContent: sampleHtml1 },\n          { index: 2, filename: '携转用户开户-业务逻辑说明文档.html', generateTime: timeStr, htmlContent: sampleHtml2 },\n        ],\n        uuid,\n        ready: true\n      })\n    }, REPORT_UUID)\n  })\n\n  // B5. 再次提交扫描\n  await runStep('B5b. 重新提交扫描 + Step3', async () => {\n    // 直接到 Step2（因为页面已重新加载）\n    await page.waitForSelector('.step-card', { timeout: 3000 })\n    // 点击下一步\n    await page.locator('.btn-primary').click()\n    await page.waitForSelector('.prompt-input', { timeout: 3000 })\n    await page.locator('.btn-tpl:first-child').click()\n    await page.click('.btn-primary')\n    await page.waitForSelector('.spinning', { timeout: 3000 })\n  })\n\n  // 注入 seed\n  await runStep('S1b. seed fileStore（劫持 setTimeout）', async () => {\n    // 劫持 simulator 的 setTimeout，让 5~8 秒的延迟立刻触发\n    await page.evaluate(() => {\n      const _setTimeout = window.setTimeout\n      window.setTimeout = function(fn, delay, ...args) {\n        if (typeof delay === 'number' && delay >= 5000 && delay <= 8000) {\n          // 立刻执行\n          try { fn(...args) } catch(e) {}\n          return 0\n        }\n        return _setTimeout(fn, delay, ...args)\n      }\n    })\n    // 同时劫持 Map.set（simulator 用 fileStore.set 存报告）\n    // 实际上我们无法直接劫持模块内变量\n    // 最简单：注入 __earlyReady 全局，修改 simulator 的 fileExists\n    await page.evaluate(() => {\n      // 标记让 fileExists 提前返回 true\n      window.__forceReady = true\n    })\n  })\n\n  // 等待 Step4 出现\n  await runStep('S1c. 等待报告列表出现', async () => {\n    let step4Visible = false\n    for (let i = 0; i < 30; i++) {\n      await page.waitForTimeout(500)\n      step4Visible = await page.locator('.result').isVisible().catch(() => false)\n      if (step4Visible) break\n    }\n    if (!step4Visible) throw new Error('Step 4 未在 15 秒内出现')\n  })\n\n  // B6. Step4 报告列表渲染\n  await runStep('B6. 报告列表（2条记录）', async () => {\n    const count = await page.locator('.report-row').count()\n    if (count !== 2) throw new Error(`期望 2 条记录，实际 ${count}`)\n  })\n\n  // B7. 列表字段校验\n  await runStep('B7. 列表字段校验（文件名/时间）', async () => {\n    const firstFilename = page.locator('.report-row').first().locator('.filename')\n    const text = await firstFilename.textContent()\n    if (!text?.includes('携转用户开户')) throw new Error(`文件名异常: ${text}`)\n    const timeCell = page.locator('.report-row').first().locator('.time')\n    const timeText = await timeCell.textContent()\n    if (!timeText?.match(/\\d{4}-\\d{2}-\\d{2}/)) throw new Error(`时间格式异常: ${timeText}`)\n  })\n\n  // B8. 点击第一条 → Modal 打开\n  await runStep('B8. 点击第一条 → Modal 弹框', async () => {\n    await page.locator('.report-row').first().click()\n    await page.waitForSelector('.modal-overlay', { timeout: 3000 })\n    if (!(await page.locator('.modal-overlay').isVisible())) throw new Error('Modal 未显示')\n    const title = await page.locator('.modal-title').textContent()\n    if (!title?.includes('安全分析')) throw new Error(`Modal 标题异常: ${title}`)\n  })\n\n  // B9. Modal iframe 渲染 HTML\n  await runStep('B9. Modal iframe 渲染 HTML 内容', async () => {\n    const iframe = page.locator('.html-iframe')\n    if (!(await iframe.isVisible())) throw new Error('iframe 未显示')\n    const srcdoc = await iframe.getAttribute('srcdoc')\n    if (!srcdoc || !srcdoc.includes('<html>')) throw new Error(`iframe srcdoc 异常`)\n    if (!srcdoc.includes('携转用户开户')) throw new Error(`HTML 内容缺失`)\n  })\n\n  // B10. 关闭 Modal\n  await runStep('B10. 关闭 Modal', async () => {\n    await page.click('.modal-close')\n    await page.waitForTimeout(400) // 等待动画\n    const visible = await page.locator('.modal-overlay').isVisible().catch(() => false)\n    if (visible) throw new Error('Modal 未关闭')\n  })\n\n  // B11. 点击第二条 → Modal 再次打开\n  await runStep('B11. 点击第二条 → Modal 再次打开', async () => {\n    await page.locator('.report-row').nth(1).click()\n    await page.waitForSelector('.modal-overlay', { timeout: 3000 })\n    const title = await page.locator('.modal-title').textContent()\n    if (!title?.includes('业务逻辑说明')) throw new Error(`Modal 标题异常: ${title}`)\n    const srcdoc = await page.locator('.html-iframe').getAttribute('srcdoc')\n    if (!srcdoc?.includes('携入号码校验')) throw new Error(`第二条 HTML 内容缺失`)\n    await page.click('.modal-close')\n  })\n\n  // B12. 重新扫描\n  await runStep('B12. 重新扫描 → 回到 Step1', async () => {\n    await page.click('.btn-secondary')\n    await page.waitForSelector('.upload-label', { timeout: 3000 })\n    if (!(await page.locator('.step-card').first().isVisible())) throw new Error('未回到 Step1')\n  })\n\n  // 报告 console 错误\n  if (errors.length > 0) {\n    console.log()\n    console.log(`[🌐 WARN] 捕获 ${errors.length} 条浏览器 console.error:`)\n    errors.forEach(e => console.log(`  - ${e}`))\n  }\n\n  await browser.close()\n  console.log()\n  console.log('='.repeat(55))\n  console.log('  ✅ 全部测试通过！')\n  console.log('='.repeat(55))\n}\n\nmain().catch(err => {\n  console.error('测试失败:', err.message)\n  process.exit(1)\n})\n","path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/projects/code-scanner-plugin/e2e-test.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":55,"output":3818,"cacheRead":98555,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102428,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775814503222,"responseId":"chatcmpl-4d92a844-9818-46b0-9224-8b749dfd8fe3"}}
